\id ACT Pohnpeian Bible 
\h WIEWIA KAN 
\toc1 en Wahnpoaron ko 
\toc2 WIEWIA KAN 
\toc3 Wie. 
\mt1 en Wahnpoaron ko  
\is1 Oaralap en Pwuhk wet  
\ip Pwuken \bk Wiewia kan en Wahnpoaron ko,\bk* iei usepen \bk Rongamwahu en Luk.\bk* Iei kahrepe keieu kesempwal en pwuhk wet, pwe en kasalehda duwen Ngehn Sarawi eh kaweidki irail ko me tepin idawehnla Sises nan mwomwohdiso ni arail kalohkiseli Rongamwahu duwen Sises “nan Serusalem, nan Sudia pwon, oh Sameria, oh lelohng ni irepen sampah” (1.8). Eri, iei koasoiepen mwekid en souleng nin duwen eh tepida rehn mehn Suhs ako, e ahpw wiahla pwoson en sampah pokon. Sounnting en pwuhk wet pil ngoangkihte kawehwehiong aramas en ahnsowo me mwekid en souleng wet kaidehkin ehu soangen lamalam keper me uhwong wehin Rom, ahpw mwekid en pwoson en souleng ehu me pwilsang oh kaunsekihala palien lamalam en mehn Suhs ako.  
\ip \bk Wiewia kan\bk* kak pwalpeseng wiahla pali siluh nin duwen koasoiepen mwomwohdiso nan wasa kan me Rongamwahu duwen Sises parpeseng oh lohkseli ie: 1) tepin mwekid en souleng nan Serusalem mwurin Sises eh ketidahla nanleng; 2) duwen parpeseng en mwekid wet wasa teikan en nan Palestin; oh 3) pil duwen eh parpeseng nan wehi kan limwahn Sehd Mediderenien, lellahng nan Rom.  
\ip Mie mehkot me inenen sansal mwahu nan pwuken \bk Wiewia kan;\bk* eri, iei doadoahk en Ngehn Sarawi me tiada ni roson lapalahpie pohn me pwoson akan nan Serusalem ni rahnen Pendekos, oh uselahte kaweid oh kakehlaka tohn mwomwohdiso oh arail sounkaweid kan ni wiewia kan koaros me audedahr pwuhk wet. En tepin souleng ko ar mahsen kan ong tohn sampah miher ni oaralap nan kapahrek kei, oh wiewia kan me sansal nan pwuken \bk Wiewia kan\bk* kadehde duwen roson en mahsen pwukat nan mouren me pwoson ko oh ni minimin en tohn mwomwohdiso.  
\io1 Audepe ni Oaralap Kaunopadahn wia sounkadehde 1.1-26  
\io2 a. Kaimwiseklahn kosonned en Sises oh sapwellime inou 1.1-14  
\io2 b. Wiliepen Sudas 1.15-26  
\io1 Doadoahk en sounkadehde kan nan Serusalem 2.1—8.3  
\io1 Doadoahk en sounkadehde kan nan Sudia oh Sameria 8.4—12.25  
\io1 En Pohl eh doadoahk 13.1—28.31  
\io2 a. Seiloak keieun lohkiseli Rongamwahu 13.1—14.28  
\io2 b. Wie kupwur nan Serusalem 15.1-35  
\io2 c. Seiloak keriaun lohkiseli Rongamwahu 15.36—18.22  
\io2 d. Seiloak kesiluhn lohkiseli Rongamwahu 18.23—21.16  
\io2 e. Pohl nan kalapwus en Serusalem, Sesaria oh Rom 21.17—28.31  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Maing Diopwulos:  
\p Nan ei tungoal pwuhk keieu I ntingihedier duwen soahng kan koaros me Sises ketin wiadahr oh mahsaniher, sang ni ahnsou me e ketin tapihada sapwellime doadoahk, \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Luk 1.1-4.\x*  
\v 2 lao lel rahn me e ketidahla nanleng. Eri, mwohn eh ketidahla, e ketin wiahiong irail kehkehlik kei sang ni manaman en Ngehn Sarawi, ong ohl ako me e ketin piladahr pwe re en wia sapwellime wahnpoaron.  
\v 3 Nan irair en rahn pahisek mwurin Sises eh ketin pwoula, pak tohto e ketin kasalehiong irail pein ih me e ketin ieias sang ni kadehde sansal kei. Irail pil kilangehr, oh e ketin mahmahsenkihong irail duwen Wehin Koht.  
\v 4 Eri, ni ahnsou me irail pokonpenehr, e ketin mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail dehr kohsang nan Serusalem, ahpw kumwail awiawihete me Semei ketin inoukidier, me I padahkihongkumwailehr duwe. \x - \xo 1.4 \xt Luk 24.49.\x*  
\v 5 Pwe Sohn papidaisihkinkumwailehr pihl, ahpw mwurin rahn ekei kumwail pahn papidaiskihla Ngehn Sarawi.” \x - \xo 1.5 \xt Mad. 3.11; Mark 1.8; Luk 3.16; Sohn 1.33.\x*   
\s1 Sises Ketidahla Nanleng  
\p
\v 6 Eri, ni wahnpoaron ako ar pokonpenehr rehn Sises, re ahpw patohwan idek, “Maing, ia duwe, ih ahnsou kiset me komw pahn ketin kapwurehda Wehin Israel?”   
\p
\v 7 Sises eri ketin sapengkin irail, “Ahnsou kan oh irair kan koasoandier rehn Semei sang pein sapwellime manaman, ahpw e sohte mweiong kumwail en ese ahnsou me mepwukat pahn wiawi.  
\v 8 Ahpw kumwail pahn audaudkihda manaman ni ahnsou me Ngehn Sarawi pahn ketidohng kumwail, oh kumwail ahpw pahn kadehde ie nan Serusalem, nan Sudia pwon, oh Sameria, oh lelohng ni irepen sampah.” \x - \xo 1.8 \xt Mad. 28.19; Mark 16.15; Luk 24.47-48.\x*  
\v 9 Mwurin eh mahsanih mepwukat, e ahpw ketidahla nanleng; oh ni arail uduhdiahl, pelien depwek pali ahpw karirihala sang irail. \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Mark 16.19; Luk 24.50-51.\x*   
\p
\v 10 Ni arail uduhdiahl Sises eh ketiket kohdahla, ohl riemen me likou pwetepwet pa kesihnenda limwarail.  
\v 11 Ira ahpw patohwan, “Kumwail mehn Kalili, dahme kumwail kesikesihnenki men kilikilengdalahng nanleng? Iei Sises menet me ketidalahr nanleng sang kumwail pil pahn sapahldohng kumwail ni soangen mwohmwette me kumwail patopatohwanehr.”   
\s1 Wiliepen Sudas  
\p
\v 12 Eri, wahnpoaron ako ahpw pwuralahng Serusalem sang nin Nahnahn Olip, me kereniong elep en mwail dohkihsang kahnimwo.  
\v 13 Irail eri pedolong nan Serusalem oh kohdalahng nan perehn powe, wasa me re kin koukousoan ie: Piter, Sohn, Seims, oh Andru, Pilip oh Tomas, Pardolomiu oh Madiu, Seims nein Alpius, Saimon me iang tohn pwihnen Selod, oh Sudas nein Seims. \x - \xo 1.13 \xt Mad. 10.2-4; Mark 3.16-19; Luk 6.14-16.\x*  
\v 14 Irail pwukat ahpw wiahki ehu ni poaden kapakap, iangahki lih ako, oh Mery inen Sises, oh rie ohl ako.   
\p
\v 15 Mwurin rahn ekei, me pwoson kan ahpw pokonpene, irail koaros kereniong me epwiki riehk. Piter ahpw uhda oh patohwanohng irail,  
\v 16 “Riei ko, mahsen en Pwuhk Sarawi uhdahn pahn pweida, me Ngehn Sarawi ketin kalokaiahki Depit ni eh kohpadahr duwen Sudas, me kahluwaier irail ko me salihedi Sises.  
\v 17 Sudas kisehtail, pwehki eh pilipildahr en iang pwaisaneki atail doadoahk.”  
\p ( 
\v 18 Mwohni me Sudas alehkihdi eh wiewia suwedo, e pwainkihda sahpw ehu, wasa e pwupwudi ie, pospeseng oh mehla; eri, kanengen kapehde koaros wudekieisang. \x - \xo 1.18 \xt Mad. 27.3-8.\x*  
\v 19 Eri, aramas koaros me koukousoan Serusalem rongehr duwen met, oh ni pein arail lokaia re kahdaneki sahpw wet Akeldama, me wehwehki “Sapwen Nta.”)   
\p
\v 20 “Pwe e ntingdier nan pwuken Melkahka Kan,  
\q1 ‘Imwe en tehnla;  
\q2 dehr mweidohng emen en kousoan loale.’  
\m E pil ntingdier,  
\q1 ‘Emen tohrohr en wiliandi oh ale pwais doadoahk wet.’ \x - \xo 1.20 \xt Mel. 69.25; b Mel. 109.8.\x*   
\p
\v 21-22 “Eri, emen ohlen uhdahn pahn pilipilda oh iangkitala, pwe en iang kadehde iasadahn Kaun Sises. Eri, ohl menet en sangete nanpwungen irail me wiahier kisehn pwihn wet nan irair en ahnsou me Kaun Sises ketiketseli rehtail, sang ni ahnsou me Sohn kawekawehwe wehwehn eh papidais lao lel ni rahn me Sises ketsang kitail oh ketidalahng nanleng.” \x - \xo 1.21-22 \xt Mad. 3 16; Mark 1.9; Luk 3.21; b Mark 16.19; Luk 24.51.\x*   
\p
\v 23 Irail eri kalangahda mwaren ohl riemen: Sosep me pil mwarenki Parsapas (e pil adaneki Sustus), oh Madaias.  
\v 24 Irail eri kapakap, patohwan, “Maing, komwi me ketin mwahngih mohngiong en aramas koaros. Eri, komw ketin kasalehiong kiht ihs rehra me komw ketin piladahr,  
\v 25 me pahn ale eh tungoal pwais doadoahk en wahnpoaron me Sudas keselahr pwe en patolahng wasa me uhdahn eh tungoal.”  
\v 26 Eri, mwurin mepwukat irail ahpw usuhski mwar riau wet pwe re en pilada sang nanpwungen ira riemenet. Eri, mwar me pilipildahr iei Madaias; e ahpw kapatapatohng wahnpoaron ehk emeno.   
\c 2  
\s1 Ketidohn Ngehn Sarawi  
\p
\v 1 Ni eh lelehr Rahnen Pendekos, irail koaros me pwosonlahr ahpw pokonpene wasatehkis. \x - \xo 2.1 \xt Lip. 23.15-21; Deud. 16.9-11.\x*  
\v 2 Ni ahnsowohte ngihl ehu ahpw peidihdo sang nanleng, me likamwete ngilen engimah ieu me ipido, oh kadirehla nan ihmwo, wasa me irail wie pokopokon ie.  
\v 3 Irail eri kilangada mehkot me likamwete mpwulen kisiniei me sirangarang pohrail, oh sair emenemen irail me pokopokon wasao.  
\v 4 Irail ahpw direkihla Ngehn Sarawi oh tapihada lokolokaiahki ekei lokaia tohrohr, nin duwen me Ngehn Sarawi ketin kalokaiahkin irail.   
\p
\v 5 Mie mehn Suhs kei me koukousoan nan Serusalem, aramas poadidi me kohdo sang nan wehi kan koaros nin sampah pwe re en iang kaudok.  
\v 6 Ni ahnsou me irail rongada mwoarong wet, aramas tohto ahpw pokonpene. Irail koaros ahpw pwuriamweikihla arail rongada pein arail lokaia sang ni mahsen en me pwosonlahr ako.  
\v 7 Eri, pwehki ar pwuriamwei oh wahpon, re ahpw nda, “Aramas pwukat me wiewia lokaia pwukat, irail mehn Kalili kei!  
\v 8 Eri, ia duwen atail rongorong arail lokolokaiahki lokaiahn sapwatail kan?  
\v 9 Kitail kohsang Pardia, Media, oh Elam, sang Mesopodamia, Sudia oh Kapedosia, sang Pondus oh Eisia,  
\v 10 sang Prikia oh Pampilia, sang Isip oh sapwen Lipia kan me kereniong Sairihni, oh pil ekei kitail sang Rom,  
\v 11 mehn Suhs oh mehn liki me wekiong lamalam en mehn Suhs; oh pil ekei kitail sang Krihd oh Arepia, ahpw kitail koaros rongorong pein atail lokaia kan arail koasoakoasoia soangen manaman kapwuriamwei kan me Koht ketin wiadahr!”  
\v 12 Pwehki arail pwuriamwei oh pingidahr, re ahpw peipeidekpene nanpwungarail, ndinda, “Ia wehwehn met?”   
\p
\v 13 Ekei irail ahpw kepikepitki me pwosonlahr ako oh kin koasoia, “Aramas pwukat sakaulahr!”   
\s1 En Piter eh Padahk  
\p
\v 14 Piter eri uhda iangahki wahnpoaron ehk emeno, ahpw ngihl laudida oh tapihada padahk ong pokono: “Iengei mehn Suhs akan, oh kumwail koaros me koukousoan nan Serusalem, kumwail karonge ie oh tehk mwahu dahme I pahn koasoia.  
\v 15 Ohl pwukat sohte sakau, nin duwen me kumwail kosekosehiong; pwe met ahpwtehn kulok duwau nimenseng.  
\v 16 Ahpw iet duwen me soukohp Soel patohwan:   
\q1
\v 17 ‘Koht ketin mahsanih, iet me I pahn wia ni imwilahn rahn akan:  
\q2 I pahn kamwerehdi Ngeni pohn aramas koaros.  
\q1 Noumwail pwutak kan oh serepein kan pahn kalohkiseli ei mahsen,  
\q2 noumwail mwahnakapw akan pahn kilang kaudiahl kan,  
\q2 oh me mah kan pahn wia auraman kei. \x - \xo 2.17 \xt Soel 2.28-32 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Ei, pil ei lidu kan, ohl oh lih akan,  
\q2 I pahn kamwerehdi Ngeni pohrail ni rahn ako,  
\q2 oh irail pahn iang kalohkiseli ei mahsen.   
\q1
\v 19 I pahn wiahda manaman ekei nanleng,  
\q2 oh kilel kapwuriamwei kei nin sampah.  
\q1 Kamaramas pahn wiawi, kisiniei oh ediniei moron pahn mie;   
\q2
\v 20 ketipin pahn rotala,  
\q2 oh maram pahn weitahtahla duwehte nta,  
\q2 mwohn Rahn Lapalap oh lingaling wet en ketidohn Kaun-o.   
\q1
\v 21 Eri, sohte lipilipil ihs ih me pahn likweriong mwaren Kaun-o, e pahn mourla.’   
\p
\v 22 “Iengei mehn Israel kan, kumwail rong pato pwukat: Sises mehn Nasaret, iei ih ohlo me sapwellime doadoahk sarawi inenen sansal mwahu ong kumwail sang ni manaman akan, me kapwuriamwei kan, oh kilel akan me Koht ketin wiahda nin lime, nin duwen me pein kumwail eseier, pwehki mepwukat wiawiher nanpwungamwail.  
\v 23 Eri, sang ni pein sapwellimen Koht koasoandi e ketin koasoanehdi me Sises pahn pengpengwohng kumwail. Kumwail eri kemehla ni amwail mweidohng aramas dipan akan en pasurdiong nin lohpwuwo. \x - \xo 2.23 \xt Mad. 27.35; Mark 15.24; Luk 23.33; Sohn 19.18.\x*  
\v 24 Ahpw Koht ketin kaiasadahr sang mehla, oh ketin kasaledekihalahr sang medek en mehla, pwe mehla solahr kak powehdi. \x - \xo 2.24 \xt Mad. 28.5-6; Mark 16.6; Luk 24.5.\x*  
\v 25 Pwe iet me Depit patohwan duwen Sises Krais,  
\q1 ‘I kilangehr Kaun-o eh ketiket mwohi ahnsou koaros,  
\q2 e kin ketiket limwahi, ihme kahrehda I sohte pahn diar apwal. \x - \xo 2.25 \xt Mel. 16.8-11 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Eri, I kin direkihla peren oh nsenamwahu.  
\q2 oh ei koasoi kan me diren peren.  
\q1 Oh ngehi, mehnda ma I pahn mehla,  
\q2 ahpw I pahn meleilei pwehki ei koapworopwor;   
\q1
\v 27 pwe komwi sohte pahn ketin keseiehla nan wasahn me melahr akan;  
\q2 komwi sohte pahn likidmeliehla sapwellimomwi ladu poadidi pwe paliwere en mwerpeseng nan sousou.   
\q1
\v 28 Komwi ketin kasalehiongieier ahl akan me kowohng mour;  
\q2 oh omwi ketiket rehi pahn kadirehkiniehla peren.’   
\p
\v 29 “Riei ko, I pahn koasoiaiong kumwail ni sansal duwen samatail Depit. E ketin pwoulahr oh seridier, oh sapwellime sousou mihmihte rehtail lel rahnwet.  
\v 30 Depit wiahier soukohp men, oh e wehwehki duwen sapwellimen Koht inou ong ih, me e pahn ketin kasapwilada emen kadaudoke pwe en wiahla nanmwarki, me pahn duwehte ih. \x - \xo 2.30 \xt Mel. 132.11; 2 Sam. 7.12-13.\x*  
\v 31 Eri, ni Depit eh kilangehr dahme Koht pahn ketin wia, e ahpw patohwan duwen iasadahn Mesaia, ni eh patohwan:  
\q1 ‘E sohte lekdekla nan wasahn me melahr akan,  
\q2 paliwere sohte mwerpeseng nan sousou.’   
\m
\v 32 Ahpw Koht ketin kaiasadahr Sises menet sang mehla, oh kiht koaros me wia sounkadehdepen mehlel wet.  
\v 33 E ketin kesepwildahngehr ni palimaun en Koht oh aleier Ngehn Sarawi sang reh, nin duwen me Seme ketin inoukidahr. Eri, dahme kumwail kilang oh rong met, iei kisehn sapwellime kalahngan me e ketin kapwildohng kiht.  
\v 34 Pwe pein Depit sohte kohdahla nanleng; ahpw e patohwan,  
\q1 Kaun-o ketin mahsanihong ei Kaun:  
\q2 ketidi met ni palimauni, \x - \xo 2.34 \xt Mel. 110.1.\x*   
\q1
\v 35 I lao pahn wiahkihla omwi imwintihti kan utupen aluweluwomwi kan.’   
\p
\v 36 “Eri, aramas en Israel kan koaros en uhdahn ese ni mehlel pwe Sises me kumwail pasurdiong nin lohpwuwo, iei ih me Koht ketin kasapwilada pwe en Kaun oh Mesaia!”   
\p
\v 37 Eri, ni aramas akan ar rongehr met, re ahpw pahtoukihla mehlel oh patohwanohng Piter oh wahnpoaron teiko, “Riat ako, dahme se pahn wia?”   
\p
\v 38 Piter ahpw sapengkin irail, “Emenemen kumwail en koluhla oh wiliakapwala, oh pil papidaisla ni mwaren Sises Krais, pwe dipamwail kan en lapwada; kumwail ahpw pahn ale Ngehn Sarawi, iei kalahngan ehu sang rehn Koht.  
\v 39 Pwe sapwellimen Koht inou wiawihongehr kumwail oh noumwail seri kan, oh pil ong irail kan me dohsang kumwail—irail koaros me Kaun-o, atail Koht kin ketin malipe.”   
\p
\v 40 Piter ahpw panawih irail oh koangngoangehkin irail padahk tohto: “Kumwail doarehsang kumwail kalokolok kan me pahn lelohng aramas suwed pwukat!”  
\v 41 Eri, me tohtohie pwosonla eh padahk oh papidaisla, oh kereniong aramas silikid me towehla pwihno rahno.  
\v 42 Re kin poadidiong ale padahk sang rehn wahnpoaron ko, oh miniminiong me pwosonlahr akan; re pil kin iang irail sakpene ni ar kin iang kapakap oh sarawien pilitikihpeseng pilawao.   
\s1 Mwomwen Mouren Nanpwungen me Pwosonlahr akan  
\p
\v 43 Manaman kapwuriamwei tohtohie me wahnpoaron ako kin wiahda, me kahrehiong emenemen eh lemmwinkidahr.  
\v 44 Irail me pwosonlahr ako nannantihongete arail miniminpene oh pil kin sawaskipene arail dipwisou kan. \x - \xo 2.44 \xt Wie. 4.32-35.\x*  
\v 45 Oh re kin netikihla sapwarail kan oh dipwisou kan oh nehkpeseng mwohni kan nanpwungarail, nin duwen me emenemen kin anahne.  
\v 46 Rahn koaros re kin tuhpene wiahki ehu nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh kin ehupene nan imwarail kan ni ar kin sakpene oh pilitikihpesng pilawao ni peren oh aktikitik.  
\v 47 Re ahpw kin kapikapinga Koht oh kenikenla rehn aramas koaros. Eri, ni rahn koaros Kaun-o kin ketin kapatahiong pwihn wet irail kan me pahn ale komourparail.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kehlaildahn Ohl Mwoator emen  
\p
\v 1 Rahn ehu Piter oh Sohn ahpw kohdalahng ni Tehnpas Sarawio kulok siluh mwurin souwas, ni ahnsoun kapakap.  
\v 2 Wasao, limwahn wenihmw me adaneki “Wenihmw Lingan,” ohl emen me mwoatoralahr sang ni eh seri kin wisikdohng ie pwe en peki mwohni sang aramas akan me kin pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio.  
\v 3 Ohl mwoatoro, ni eh kilangada Piter oh Sohn ara pahn pedolong, e ahpw peki rehra ira en kihong mehkot.  
\v 4 Ira eri kilikilang, Piter ahpw nda, “Kilengdohng kiht!”  
\v 5 Eri, ohlo ahpw saradahng ira oh kihkihong me e pahn ale mehkot sang rehra.  
\v 6 Piter ahpw ndaiong, “Soh mwahn nei sens ehu, ahpw I pahn kihong uhk dahme I ahneki: ni mwaren Sises Krais mehn Nasaret, I ndaiong uhk, uhda oh alu!”  
\v 7 Eri, Piter ahpw ale palimaunen pehn ohlo oh sewesehda en uhda. Ni ahnsowohte nehn ohlo oh keimwen neh ko ahpw kehlailda;  
\v 8 e ahpw mesiekda oh tapihada alialuseli. Ih eri iang ira pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh alialu oh mesimesiekseli oh kapikapinga Koht.  
\v 9 Pokono pwon ahpw kilang en ohlo eh alialu oh kapikapinga Koht.  
\v 10 Ni ar kasawihadahr me iei ohl me kin mwomwohd limwahn “Wenihmw Lingan” en Tehnpas Sarawio oh kin wie pekipek, irail koaros ahpw pwuriamweikihla mehlel dahme wiawihongehr ohlo.   
\s1 En Piter eh Padahk nan Tehnpas Sarawio  
\p
\v 11 Ni en ohlo eh sohte kakasang Piter oh Sohn, aramas ako koaros ahpw pwuriamweikihla oh tangala rehrail wasa me adaneki “Palangk en Solomon.”  
\v 12 Eri, ni Piter eh kilangada aramas ako, e ahpw ndaiong irail, “Ohlen Israel kan! Dahme kumwail pwuriamweikihki met, oh dahme kumwail kangkakilkin kiht? Kumwail soh lemehiong me sang ni pein at manaman de poadidi me kahrehiong ohl menet eh alu?  
\v 13 Eri, Koht en Eipraam, Aisek, oh Seikop, Koht en atail pahpa kahlap ako, iei ih me ketikihongehr sapwellime manaman lingan ong sapwellime ladu Sises. Kumwail ahpw pangala Sises rehn me lapalap akan, oh ni en Pailet eh men kapitala, a kumwail ahpw kahmahmkihla. \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Eks. 3.15.\x*  
\v 14 Ih me ketin sarawi oh mwahu, a kumwail ahpw kahmahmki oh peki rehn Pailet en kapwaiong kumwail nsenamwail oh lapwadahng kumwail sounkam aramas emen. \x - \xo 3.14 \xt Mad. 27.15-23; Mark 15.6-14; Luk 23.13-23; Sohn 19.12-15.\x*  
\v 15 Kumwail eri kemehla Sounkomouro. Ahpw Koht ketin kaiasada sang mehla—oh kiht me sounkadehdehpen mepwukat.  
\v 16 Manaman en mwaren Sises me kakehlahda ohl menet. Iei me dahme kumwail kilikilang oh eseier, wiawiher sang ni pwoson mware; oh iei pwoson Sises me kahrehiong ohl mwoator menet eh kehlaildahr mwohmwail koaros.   
\p
\v 17 “Eri met, riei ko, I ese dahme kumwail oh amwail kaun akan wiahiongehr Sises—met wiawiher pwehki amwail soaloalokong.  
\v 18 Eri, keilahn aio, Koht ketin kasaledahr rehn soukohp ako koaros me sapwellime Mesaia pahn ketin lokolok; iei duwen eh pweidahr.  
\v 19 Eri, kumwail koluhla oh wiliakapwala oh wekiong Koht pwe en ketin kamwakeleweisang kumwail dipamwail kan,  
\v 20 pwe ahnsoun kakehlepen ngenitail en kohdo sang rehn Kaun-o, oh Koht pahn ketin poaronehdo Sises, iei ih me Mesaia me e ketin piladahngkumwailehr.  
\v 21 E uhdahn pahn ketiket nanleng lao ni ahnsou me soahng koaros pahn wiliakapwala, nin duwen me Koht ketin kasalehiong sapwellime soukohp sarawi ko keilahn aio.  
\v 22 Pwe Moses mahsanih, ‘Kaun-o amwail Koht pahn poaronedohng kumwail soukohp emen duwehte eh ketin poaroneiehdo, soukohp menet pahn kohsang nanpwungamwail. Kumwail uhdahn pahn kin rong soahng koaros me e pahn kin padahkihong kumwail. \x - \xo 3.22 \xt Deud. 18.15.\x*  
\v 23 Ma emen sohte pahn rong dahme soukohpo pahn mahsanih, e pahn katohrohrasang rehn sapwellimen Koht aramas akan oh kamwomwmwomwla.’ \x - \xo 3.23 \xt Deud. 18.19.\x*  
\v 24 Eri, soukohp ako koaros, sang Samuel oh pil irail ko me kohdo mwuri, re pil kalohkidahr duwen dahme wiewiawi rahn pwukat.  
\v 25 Eri, sapwellimen Koht inou kan me e ketikihong soukohp ako iei uhdahn ong kumwail, oh kumwail pil iang ahneki inou me Koht ketin wiahiongehr samatail mehn mahs ako. Nin duwen eh mahsanihong Eipraam, ‘I pahn kapaiahkihda aramas en sampah koaros kadaudokomw.’ \x - \xo 3.25 \xt Sen. 22.18.\x*  
\v 26 Koht eri ketin pilada sapwellime Ladu oh poaronehdo mahs rehmwail, pwe en ketin kapaiakumwailda ni eh pahn ketin kahrehiong kumwail koaros en weksang amwail wiewia suwed kan.”   
\c 4  
\s1 Piter oh Sohn Mwohn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalap  
\p
\v 1 Eri, ni en Piter oh Sohn ara koasoakoasoiong aramas ako, samworo ko, oh kaun me kin apwahpwalih silepe kan en Tehnpas Sarawio, oh pil Sadusi kei, ahpw lel rehra.  
\v 2 Irail inenen pwunodkihda en wahnpoaron riemenet ara padahkihong aramas akan me Sises ketin iasadahr sang mehla; pwehki koasoio wia kadehdepen me melahr akan ar pahn pil pwurehng mourda.  
\v 3 Eri, re ahpw kolirahdi, oh keseirahlong nan imweteng lao manda, pwehki eh soutikpenehr.  
\v 4 Ahpw me tohto me rong mahseno re pwosonla; oh ohl ako wie tohtohla ele lel me limekid.   
\p
\v 5 Eri, pweidi manda, kaunen mehn Suhs ko, me mah ko, oh sounpadahk kan en Kosonnedo ahpw pokonpene nan Serusalem.  
\v 6 Irail ahpw pokonpene iangahki Samworo Lapalap Anas oh Kaiapas, oh Sohn, oh Aleksander, oh pil ekei irail kisehn peneinei en Samworo Lapalapo.  
\v 7 Re ahpw kahrehdo wahnpoaron riemeno mwohrail oh keinemwe rehra, “Dahme kumwa wiahki met? Soangen manaman da me kumwa ahneki, de mwaren ihs me kumwa doadoahngki?”   
\p
\v 8 Piter me direkilahr Ngehn Sarawi ahpw sapengkin irail, “Maing ko, sounkaweid en aramas akan, oh me mah kan:  
\v 9 ma peidek pwukan wiawihongkitehr rahnwet duwen wiewia mwahu me wiawihong ohl mwoatoro, oh duwen eh kehlaildahro,  
\v 10 eri, kumwail koaros oh pil mehn Israel kan koaros en ese me ohl menet me kesikesihnen mwohmwail met mwahulahr mehlel sang ni manaman en mwaren Sises Krais mehn Nasaret, iei ih me kumwail kalohpwuwalahr, oh Koht ketin kaiasadahr sang mehla.  
\v 11 Iei ih Sises menet me Pwuhk Sarawi mahsaniheki,  
\q1 ‘Takai me kumwail sounkou ihmw kan kesepwekelahr  
\q2 uhd wiahla takain pwukakeimw.’ \x - \xo 4.11 \xt Mel. 118.22.\x*   
\m
\v 12 Sangete reh me komourpen aramas kak dierekdahsang, pwe ihte mwar wet me Koht ketikihong aramas akan, pwe en wia Sounkomourpatail nin sampah.”   
\p
\v 13 Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo ahpw inenen pwuriamweikihla duwen en Piter oh Sohn ara eimah, pwehki arail dehdehki me ira aramas riemen me sohte wad oh pil sohte iang sukuhl. Irail eri esehda me ira kin ieiang Sises mahso.  
\v 14 Ahpw sohte mehkot me irail kak ndaiong ira, pwehki arail kilangehr ohl me kehlaildahro eh iang Piter oh Sohn kesikesihnen wasao.  
\v 15 Re ahpw ndaiong ira en pedoisang nan perehn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, oh irail eri tapihada koasoakoasoipene nanpwungarail.  
\v 16 Re ahpw peidekpene, nda, “Dahme kitail pahn wiahiong ohl riemenet? Aramas koaros me koukousoan nan Serusalem wehwehki me ira wiadahr manaman kapwuriamwei wet, oh kitail sohte kak kahmahmki.  
\v 17 A pwe mehkotet en dehr lelohng aramas en wasa teikan, kitail panawihekin ira en dehr pwurehng koasoiaiong aramas akan duwen mwaren Sises.”   
\p
\v 18 Irail eri ekeriralong oh panawihekin ira en dehr pwurehng koasoia de padahkihong aramas akan duwen mwaren Sises.  
\v 19 Eri, Piter oh Sohn ahpw sapengkin irail, “Eri, pein kumwail en kapwungada mehnia me pwung mwohn silangin Koht, ma se en peikiong kumwail, de se en peikiong Koht.  
\v 20 Pwe se sohte kak tokedihsang koasoakoasoia dahme pein kiht kilangehr oh rongehr.”  
\v 21 Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo eri kehkehlikiong ira ni kehlail oh kasaledekirahla. Irail pil sohte kak diarada soangen kahrepe ehu me re pahn kak kalokehkin ira, pwe aramas akan kin kapingahki Koht duwen me wiawihero.  
\v 22 Pwe ohl me manamano wiawihong eh mahkier sounpar pahisek samwa.   
\s1 Me Pwoson akan Peki Eimah  
\p
\v 23 Mwurin ara saledekla, Piter oh Sohn ahpw pwuralahng rehn kompoakepahra ko oh koasoaiong irail dahme samworo lapalap ako oh me mah ko ndaiong ira.  
\v 24 Ni me pwoson ko ar rongehr mepwukat, irail koaros ahpw ehupene kapakap ong Koht, patohwan, “Maing, Kaun oh Sounwiepen lahng, sampah, oh sehd, oh audeparail kan koaros! \x - \xo 4.24 \xt Eks. 20.11; Neh. 9.6; Mel. 146.6.\x*  
\v 25 Sapwellimomwi Ngehn Sarawi mahsendohng kiht rehn sapwellimomwi ladu Depit, samat kahlapo, ni eh patohwan,  
\q1 ‘Dahme mehn liki kan lingeringerkihki,  
\q2 dahme aramas akan wiewiahki arail koasoandi soh-katepe?   
\q1
\v 26 Nanmwarki kan en sampah onopadahr pein irail,  
\q2 oh kaun akan pokonpenehr  
\q2 pwe re en pelian Kaun-o oh sapwellime Mesaia.’ \x - \xo 4.26 \xt Mel. 2.1-2 (LXX).\x*   
\m
\v 27 Pwe mehlel Erod oh Pontius Pailet, iangahki mehn liki kan oh mehn Israel kan, pokonpenehr nan kahnimw wet oh peliandahr Sises, sapwellimomwi Ladu sarawi, me komwi ketin kasapwiladahngehr Mesaia. \x - \xo 4.27 \xt Luk 23.7-11; b Mad. 27.1-2; Mark 15.1; Luk 23.1; Sohn 18.28-29.\x*  
\v 28 Irail pokonpenehr pwe re en wia soahng koaros me komw ketin kupwuredahr me pahn wiawi, sang ni sapwellimomwi manaman oh kupwur.  
\v 29 Eri, Maing at Kaun, komw mwahngih kailok me re wia, komw ketin kupwurehiong kiht, sapwellimomwi ladu pwukat, se en koasoia sapwellimomwi mahsen ni eimah.  
\v 30 Komw ketin kapahwei limomwi kan pwe en kakehlahda, oh ketin kupwure pwe kapwuriamwei kan oh manaman akan en kak wiawi sang ni mwaren sapwellimomwi Ladu sarawi Sises.”   
\p
\v 31 Eri, ni arail kaimwisekala ar kapakap, wasa me re pokopokon ieo ahpw rerada; oh irail koaros ahpw direkihla Ngehn Sarawi. Re ahpw tapihada padapadahngkiseli mahsen en Koht ni eimah mehlel.   
\s1 Ahnekipene Soahng Koaros  
\p
\v 32 Mohngiong oh medemedewehn irail koaros me pwosonlahr ako ahpw wiahla ehu. Sohte emen nanpwungarail me kin nda me eh dipwisou kan ah kelehpw, ahpw irail koaros kin ahnekipene soahng koaros me arail. \x - \xo 4.32 \xt Wie. 2.44-45.\x*  
\v 33 Eri, ni manaman laud wahnpoaron ako ahpw kadekadehde duwen iasadahn Kaun Sises; oh Koht ketin kapwilewei sapwellime kapai laud pohrail koaros.  
\v 34 Sohte mwahn emen nanpwungarail me anahnehda mehkot. Irail ko me mie sapwarail oh imwarail kin netikihla oh wahdo pweinen soahng kan me re netikilahr  
\v 35 oh kihong wahnpoaron ako. Eri, mwohni ko ahpw kin nehnehiong emenemen nin duwen eh anahn.   
\p
\v 36 Eri, ih duwen me Sosep wiahier, mehn Lipai men me ipwidier Saiprus, me wahnpoaron ako kahdaneki Parnapas (me wehwehki “Me kin koangngoange”),  
\v 37 e netikihla sapwe oh wahdo pweine rehn wahnpoaron ko.   
\c 5  
\s1 Ananaias oh Sapaira  
\p
\v 1 A mie ohl emen me adaneki Ananaias, oh eden eh pwoud Sapaira. Ohlo eri netikihla sahpw ehu me uhdahn sapwara,  
\v 2 e ahpw ekihsang elep en pweinen sahpwo, me eh pwoud pil iang ese, oh walahng luhwen mwohni ko rehn wahnpoaron ko.  
\v 3 Piter ahpw ndaiong, “Ananaias, dahme kahrehda ke mweidkihong Sehdan en kaunda mohngiongomw oh kahrehiong uhk en pitih Ngehn Sarawi ni omw ekihsang elep en mwohni me ke aleier sang ni pweinen sahpw me ke netikilahro?  
\v 4 Mwohn omw netikihla sahpwo, e wia uhdahn sapwomw, oh pil mwurin omw netikilahro, mwohni ko uhdahn noumw. Eri a, dahme kahrehda ke pilada nan kapehdomw ke en wiahki soahng wet? Kaidehn aramas me ke pitih, pwe ke pitih Koht!”  
\v 5 Ni Ananaias eh rong mahsen wet, e ahpw pwupwte mehla. Oh irail koaros me iang rong, re pil masepwehkada. \x - \xo 5.5 \xt Su. 55.\x*  
\v 6 Mwahnakapw kei eri pedolong kidimpene paliweren Ananaiaso, wahieila liki oh sarepedi.   
\p
\v 7 Mwein mwurin awa siluh, en Ananaias eh pwoudo pil pedolong; ahpw e sohte ese dahme wiawihero.  
\v 8 Piter eri ndaiong, “Komw padahkihong ie ma iei met uwen mwohni koaros me kowe oh omw werek ale sang ni pweinen sahpw me kumwa netikilahro?”  
\p Liho ahpw sapeng, “Ei, ih koaros men.”   
\p
\v 9 Eri, Piter ahpw ndaiong, “Dahme kahrehda kowe oh omw pwoudo lemekihda kumwa en kasongosonge Ngenen Kaun-o? Ohl ako me sarepedier omw pwoudo, irail miher ni wenihmwo ahnsou wet, oh re pil pahn weiukala liki!”  
\v 10 Eri, ni ahnsowohte liho pil pwupwudihte mwohn Piter, mehla. Mwahnakapw ako eri pedolong oh kilangada me liho pil melahr. Irail eri waieila liki oh sarepedi limwahn eh pwoudo.  
\v 11 Eri, mwomwohdiso pwon, oh pil irail koaros me rongada koasoi wet, ahpw inenen masepwehkada kowahlap.   
\s1 Manaman Kapwuriamwei kei  
\p
\v 12 Eri, wahnpoaron ako ahpw kin wiewia manaman kapwuriamwei tohto nanpwungen aramas akan. Me pwoson akan koaros ahpw kin wiahki ehu pokonpene nan Palangk en Solomon.  
\v 13 Aramas koaros kin kapinga me pwoson pwukat, re ahpw kin masak patehng irail.  
\v 14 Eri soh, pwe pak tohto ekei aramas kin iangala pwihno—ohl oh lih tohto me pwosonlahr Kaun-o.  
\v 15 Pwehki doadoahk kan me wahnpoaron ako wiewia, aramas soumwahu kan ahpw kin wisiklahng pohn ahl akan oh pwilidiong pohn peht kan oh pil lohs kan, pwe ni Piter eh pahn kin keid wasao, mwetehte en kin lel pohrail.  
\v 16 Pokon kei eri kin kohieido sang nan kahnimw kan limwahn Serusalem, re ahpw kin wahdo me soumwahu kan oh me ngehn saut tiadahr pohrail; koaros ahpw kin kehlailda.   
\s1 Kamakam en Wahnpoaron ako  
\p
\v 17 Samworo Lapalapo oh ienge kan koaros, me iei tohn pwihnen Sadusi en wasao ahpw inenen peirinkihda mehlel wahnpoaron ako. Irail eri lemehda re en wiahiong irail mehkot.  
\v 18 Irail eri koledi wahnpoaron ako oh keseirailong nan imweteng.  
\v 19 Ahpw pwohngo tohnleng en Kaun-o men ahpw ritingada wenihmw kan en imwetengo, oh kahluwaiei wahnpoaron ko. E ahpw mahsanihong irail,  
\v 20 “Kumwail kohwei kesihnenda nan Tehnpas Sarawio oh padahkihong aramas akan duwen mour kapw wet.”  
\v 21 Wahnpoaron ako eri peikiong, oh nimensehngie re ahpw pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio oh tapihada padapadahk.  
\p Samworo Lapalapo oh ienge kan ahpw ekerpene kaunen mehn Suhs ako koaros ong ni wie lamalam en Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo unsek. Irail ileklahng ni imwetengo pwe wahnpoaron ko en wisikdo mwohrail.  
\v 22 Ahpw ni ahnsou me lapalap ako lelohng ni imwetengo, re sohte diar wahnpoaron ako loale. Irail eri pwuralahng rehn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo oh koasoia,  
\v 23 “Ni at lelehr ni imwetengo, se diarada me wenihmw koaros loak oh silepe koaros sinsile wenihmw ko; ahpw ni at ritingada wenihmwo, se sohte diar emen loale!”  
\v 24 Ni ahnsou me kaunen silepe kan en Tehnpas Sarawio oh samworo lapalap ako rongada koasoi pwoatet, re ahpw pwuriamweikihla dahme wiawihong wahnpoaron ko.  
\v 25 Eri, ni ahnsowo ohl emen ahpw pedolong oh ndaiong irail, “Kumwail rong! Ohl ako me kumwail salihedier, irail wie padapadahk ong aramas akan nan Tehnpas Sarawio!”  
\v 26 Eri, kaunen silepe ko ahpw kohieila, iangahki eh ladu kei pwe en kahrehdo wahnpoaron ako. Ahpw re sohte mwomwen lemeiong wahnpoaron ako pwehki ar masak pwe aramas akan de kate irail.   
\p
\v 27 Irail eri kahrehdo wahnpoaron ako oh kasihnenihrailda mwohn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo; oh Samworo Lapalapo ahpw tapihada kadeik irail.   
\p
\v 28 “Se kihong kumwail kosonned kehlail kumwail dehr pwurehng padahk ni mwaren ohl menet; ahpw kumwail kilang dahme kumwail wiahda: kumwail kalohkiselier amwail padahk kan nan Serusalem, oh kumwail pil mwahuki kapwukoahnekin kiht en Sises eh pwoula.” \x - \xo 5.28 \xt Mad. 27.25.\x*   
\p
\v 29 Eri, Piter oh wahnpoaron teiko ahpw sapeng, “Se uhdahn pahn peikiong Koht, a kaidehn aramas.  
\v 30 Koht en samatail mehn mahs ako ketin kaiasada Sises sang mehla, mwurin amwail kemehla ni amwail pasurdiong nin lohpwuwo.  
\v 31 Ahpw Koht ketin kasapwiladahng Sises ni palimaune, pwe en Kaun oh Sounkomour, pwe en ketikihong mehn Israel kan ahnsou mwahu en koluhla oh wiliakapwala oh ale lapwapen diparail kan.  
\v 32 Kiht me sounkadehdepen mepwukat—kiht oh pil Ngehn Sarawi me Koht ketin audehkin irail koaros me kin peikiong ih.”   
\p
\v 33 Ni Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo ar rongada mepwukat, re inenen lingeringerda kowahlap oh anahnehte wahnpoaron ko en kamakamala.  
\v 34 Eri Parisi men, kisehn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, me adaneki Kameliel, sounpadahk en Kosonnedo men me keniken rehn aramas akan koaros, ahpw uhda oh ruwese me wahnpoaron ko en wisikieila liki.  
\v 35 Eri, e ahpw ndaiong Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, “Ohlen Israel kan, kumwail en kanahieng dahme kumwail pahn wiahiong ohl pwukat.  
\v 36 Ekei ahnsou samwalahr ako Diudas pwarodohr, kosekose me ih aramas lapalap emen; oh kereniong aramas pahpwiki kei iangala. Ohlo ahpw kamakamala, oh me ideidawehn ko ahpw tangpeseng; oh mwekid me e wiadahro ahpw sohrala.  
\v 37 Mwurin met, Sudas mehn Kalili ahpw pil pwarodo ni ahnsoun ntingen peneinei, aramas akan ahpw pil idawehnla. Ahpw e pil kamakamala, oh irail ko me ideidawehn pil tangpeseng.  
\v 38 Eri, nan ire wet, I padahkihong kumwail, kumwail dehr wia mehkot me pahn pelian ohl pwukat. Kumwail piseksang irail, pwe ma arail koasoandi oh doadoahk tepsang aramas, e uhdahn pahn sohrala;  
\v 39 ahpw ma e kohdo sang rehn Koht, kumwail sohte kak poweiraildi. Kumwail en kanahieng, dehr wia mehkot me pahn pelian kupwur en Koht!”  
\p Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo eri idawehn kaweid en Kamaliel. \x - \xo 5.39 \xt 2 Mak. 7.19.\x*  
\v 40 Irail eri ekerolong wahnpoaron ko oh wokih irail oh koasoanediong irail en dehr pwurehng padahk ni mwaren Sises. Irail eri kasaledekihirailla.  
\v 41 Eri, wahnpoaron ko ahpw mweselsang rehn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, re ahpw perenkihda kowahlap duwen Koht eh ketin kupwure re en warohng lokolongki saroh pwehki mwaren Sises.  
\v 42 Eri, rahn koaros, nan Tehnpas Sarawio oh nan imwen aramas akan irail kin wonoweite ni padahk oh kawehwe Rongamwahu duwen Sises me iei Mesaia.   
\c 6  
\s1 Sounsawas Isimen  
\p
\v 1 Mwurin ahnsou kis, ni en tohnpadahk ko ar wie tohtohla, akamai ehu ahpw wiawi nanpwungen mehn Suhs ako me ese mahsen en Krihs oh uhdahn pwilidak en mehn Suhs akan. Irail me ese mahsen en Krihs koasoia me liohdi kan me mie rehrail sohte kin ale pwaisarail ni ar kin nehk sawas akan ni rahn akan.  
\v 2 Eri, wahnpoaron ehk riemeno ahpw ekerpene pwihn me pwosonlahr ako koaros oh ndaiong irail, “E suwediong kiht se en pohnsehsehla padahkpen mahsen en Koht pwehki at pahn nehk mwohni kan.  
\v 3 Eri, riat ako, kumwail pilada sang nanpwungamwail ohl isimen me kumwail ese me diren Ngehn Sarawi oh erpit, se ahpw pahn mweidohng irail doadoahk wet pwe re en pweisanki.  
\v 4 Ahpw pein kiht, se pahn mweidohng at ahnsou unsek ong kapakap oh doadoahk en wia padahk.”   
\p
\v 5 Pwihno pwon inenen perenkihda mehlel duwen me wahnpoaron ko kasaledahr. Irail eri pilada Stipen, ohl emen me diren pwoson oh Ngehn Sarawi, oh Pilip, Prokorus, Nikaner, Timon, Parminus oh Nikolaus sang Andiok, mehn liki men ih me wekiongehr lamalam en mehn Suhs mahso.  
\v 6 Pwihno eri kahrelahng wahnpoaron ko irail pwukat, pwe re en kapakapkin irail oh pwil pehrail kan pohrail.   
\p
\v 7 Mahsen en Koht eri lolohkseli. Tohnpadahk ko nan Serusalem ahpw wie tohtohla, oh me tohto rehn samworo ko me pil iang pwosonla.   
\s1 Kolkoldien Stipen  
\p
\v 8 Stipen iei ih me Koht ketin kapaiahda kowahlap, ih me pil diren manaman, ahpw wiadahr manaman kapwuriamwei tohto nanpwungen aramas akan.  
\v 9 Ahpw mie ekei aramas me kin pelian Stipen. Aramas pwukat tohn sinakoke me adaneki “Aramas Saledek,”\f a \fr 6.9 \fk ARAMAS SALEDEK: \ft Iei irail mehn Suhs kei me wia lidu mahs, ahpw re pweipweisangehr nan mour en lidu de kasaledeklahr.\f* me mehn Suhs sang Sairihni oh Aleksandria kin towehda. Irail pwukat oh pil ekei mehn Suhs sang Silisia oh Eisia ahpw tapihada akamaiong Stipen.  
\v 10 Ahpw Ngehno ketikihong Stipen soangen erpit laud ehu me kahrehda ni eh kin koasoi re sohte kak pelian.  
\v 11 Irail ahpw pwainohng aramas ekei pwe re en koasoia, “Se kin rong eh koasoia mehkan me pelian Moses oh pil pelian Koht!”  
\v 12 Lokaia pwukat eri koamwoarongehda aramas akan, me mah ko, oh pil sounpadahk en Kosonnedo kan. Aramas akan ahpw kodohng Stipen oh koledi oh kahrelahng mwohn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo.  
\v 13 Re ahpw kapedolong ohl ekei pwe re en kine likamw ong ih ni arail koasoia, “Ohl menet kin kalap koasoia mehkan me kin kauwe atail Tehnpas Sarawio oh Kosonned en Moses.  
\v 14 Pwe se kin rongasang me Sises mehn Nasaret menet pahn kamwerehdi Tehnpas Sarawio, oh e pil pahn wekidala tiahk kan koaros me Moses ketikihong kitail!”  
\v 15 Irail koaros me towehda mwomwohd en Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo ahpw kilikilang Stipen oh kilangada me meseo likamwete mesen tohnleng men.   
\c 7  
\s1 En Stipen Padahk  
\p
\v 1 Samworo Lapalapo ahpw idek rehn Stipen, “Ia duwe, met me uhdahn mehlel?”   
\p
\v 2 Stipen ahpw sapengki, “Riei ko oh semei ko, kumwail rong ie! Mwohn samatail kahlap Eipraam eh kousoanla Aran, Koht en lingan ketin pwarohng nan Mesopodamia, \x - \xo 7.2 \xt Sen. 12.1.\x*  
\v 3 oh mahsanihong, ‘Komw mweselweisang rehn omw peneinei oh nan omwi wehi, oh kowohng sahpw ehu me I pahn kasalehiong uhk.’  
\v 4 Eri, Eipraam ahpw mweselsang nan sapwen Kaldia, oh kohla Aran oh kousoanla wasao. Mwurin semeo eh melahr, Koht ahpw mahsanihong Eipraam en kodohng nan wehi wet me kumwail koukousoan ie met. \x - \xo 7.4 \xt Sen. 11.31; b Sen. 12.4.\x*  
\v 5 Koht sohte ketikihong Eipraam ekis kisehn wasaht pwe en sapwenikihla, pil sohte kisin wasa kis; ahpw Koht ketin inoukihong me e pahn ketikihong ih oh kadaudoke kan pwe re en sapwenikihla. Ni ahnsou me Koht ketin wiahda inou wet, Eipraam saikinte naineki seri. \x - \xo 7.5 \xt Sen. 12.7; 13.15; 15.18;17.8.\x*  
\v 6 Ahpw iet me Koht ketin mahsanihong Eipraam, ‘Kadaudokomw kan pahn kousoanla nan wehin liki ehu, wasa re pahn kaliduhla oh pahn wiakaula nan erein pahr pahpwiki.’ \x - \xo 7.6 \xt Sen. 15.13-14.\x*  
\v 7 Ahpw Koht ketin mahsanih, ‘I pahn kadeikada aramas akan me re pahn papah, oh mwuhr, re pahn pedoi sang nan wehio oh uhd pwongih ie wasakiset.’ \x - \xo 7.7 \xt Eks. 3.12.\x*  
\v 8 Eri, Koht ketikihong Eipraam kasarawien sirkumsais, nin duwen kilel en inowo. Eri, Eipraam ahpw sirkumsaisihala Aisek wihk ehu mwurin eh ipwidi. Aisek ahpw sirkumsaisihala nah pwutak Seikop, oh Seikop ahpw pil sirkumsaisihala nah pwutak ehk riemeno, me iei samatail kahlap ako. \x - \xo 7.8 \xt Sen. 17.10-14; b Sen. 21.2-4; c Sen. 25.26; d Sen. 29.31—35.18.\x*   
\p
\v 9 “Eri, nein Seikop ko kin peiriniong riarail Sosep; ihme re netikihlahki pwe en wiahla lidu men rehn mehn Isip. Ahpw soh, pwe Koht ketin ieiangete. \x - \xo 7.9 \xt Sen. 37.11; b Sen. 37.28; c Sen. 39.2,21.\x*  
\v 10 E ahpw ketin doarehla sang nan kahpwal akan koaros. Ni ahnsou me Sosep pwarohng Parao, nanmwarkien Isip, Koht ketikihong tiahk mwahu oh loalokong. Parao eri kasapwilada Sosep en wia kepina en wehin Isip oh pil en kaunda tehnpaso. \x - \xo 7.10 \xt Sen. 41.39-41.\x*  
\v 11 Eri, lehk lapalap ehu ahpw pweida me kahrehda apwal laud nan Isip oh Kenan pwon. Samatail kahlap ako sohte kak diar kisin mwenge. \x - \xo 7.11 \xt Sen. 42.1-2.\x*  
\v 12 Eri, ni en Seikop eh rongadahr me mie pilawa nan Isip, e ahpw kadarala samatail kahlap ako pwe re en kohdilahng Isip. Iei keieun ar kohla wasao.  
\v 13 Ni keriapak en arail kohdihla wasao, Sosep ahpw kasalehiong rie ko pein ih, oh Parao ahpw mwahngihada duwen en Sosep eh peneinei. \x - \xo 7.13 \xt Sen. 45.1; b Sen. 45.16.\x*  
\v 14 Sosep eri ileklahng seme Seikop oh eh peneinei koaros en kodohng Isip; irail koaros me isiakan limmen. \x - \xo 7.14 \xt Sen. 45.9-10, 17-18; b Sen. 46.27 (LXX).\x*  
\v 15 Seikop eri kohdihla Isip, wasa me ih oh samatail kahlap ako mehla ie. \x - \xo 7.15 \xt Sen. 46.1-7; b Sen. 49.33.\x*  
\v 16 Paliwararail kan ahpw wisikdohng Sekem, wasa me re seridiong ie nan sousou me Eipraam pwainkidahr uwen mwohni ehu sang rehn kadaudok en Amor. \x - \xo 7.16 \xt Sen. 23.3-16; 33.19; 50.7-13; Sos. 24.32.\x*   
\p
\v 17 “Eri, ahnsou me Koht pahn ketin kapwaiada sapwellime inou me e ketin wiahiong Eipraam lao kerendohr, riatail akan nan Isip ahpw inenen ngederla mehlel. \x - \xo 7.17 \xt Eks. 1.7-8.\x*  
\v 18 Kedekedeo, emen nanmwarki ahpw kesepwilda me sehse duwen Sosep ahpw uhd kaunda Isip.  
\v 19 E kin pitih riatail ko, oh kin lemeiong samatail kahlap ako, idingohng irail en kesepwekeieisang neirail seri kan nan imwarail kan, pwe irail en mehla. \x - \xo 7.19 \xt Eks. 1.10-11; b Eks. 1.22.\x*  
\v 20 Eri, iei ahnsowo me Moses ipwidi, seri kaselel men. E kekeirda nan imwe sounpwong siluh. \x - \xo 7.20 \xt Eks. 2.2.\x*  
\v 21 Eri, ni ahnsou me e lekdeksang nan imweo, nein Parao serepein men ahpw diarada oh apwalihada nin duwen uhdahn nah pwutak. \x - \xo 7.21 \xt Eks. 2.3-10.\x*  
\v 22 E pil audaudkidahr soangen loalokong koaros en mehn Isip, oh wiahla ohl koahiek nin lokaia oh wiewia kan.   
\p
\v 23 “Eri, ni en Moses eh mahkier sounpar pahisek, e ahpw lemehda en tuhwong ienge mehn Israel kan. \x - \xo 7.23 \xt Eks. 2.11-15.\x*  
\v 24 E kilangada duwen emen irail eh wiakaulahr rehn mehn Isip men. E ahpw kohla sewese oh pelianda mehn Isipo, oh kemehla.  
\v 25 (E kihkihong me pein nah aramas akan pahn wehwehki me Koht pahn ketin doadoahngki ih en kasaledekihirailla; ahpw re sohte wehwehki.)  
\v 26 Mandahn rahno, Moses pil kilangada mehn Israel riemen ara pepei nanpwungara; e ahpw song en kamwahwirahla. E ndaiong ira, ‘Kumwa rong! Kumwa pirien ehu, a dahme kumwa pepeiki?’  
\v 27 A me wiakauwe meteio ahpw siken Moses sang nanpwungara oh idek reh, ‘Ihs me kasapwiluhkada pwe ke en kaunkitada oh wia at sounkopwung?  
\v 28 Ke men kemeiehla duwehte omw kemelahr mehn Isipo aio?’  
\v 29 Ni en Moses eh rongada met, e ahpw tangasang Isip oh tapihada kousoan nan wehin Midian. Iei wasao me e wiahda nah pwutak riemen. \x - \xo 7.29 \xt Eks. 18.3-4.\x*   
\p
\v 30 “Mwurin sounpar pahisek tohnleng men ahpw pwarohng Moses nan mpwulen kisiniei nan kisin tuhke kis nan sapwtehn limwahn Nahna Sainai. \x - \xo 7.30 \xt Eks. 3.1-10.\x*  
\v 31 Moses eri pwuriamweikihla me e kilangadao, ahpw alulahng kisin tuhkeo pwe en kadehde. E ahpw rongada kapitien Kaun-o ni eh ketin mahsanih,  
\v 32 ‘Ngehi Koht en semomw kahlap ako, Koht en Eipraam, oh Aisek, oh Seikop.’ Moses eri rerrerki eh masepwehkada, oh sohla men kilenglahng wasao.  
\v 33 Kaun-o ahpw mahsanihong, “Kihsang omw suht kan, pwe wasa me ke kesikesihnen ie me sarawi.  
\v 34 I kilangehr uwen lokolok laud en nei aramas akan nan Isip. I rongehr ngilen ar weirek kan, oh I pil kohdidohr pwe I en doareirailla. Eri met, I pahn kadaruhkalahng Isip.’   
\p
\v 35 “Iei Moses menet me mehn Israel kan keselahr, ni arail idek reh, ‘Ihs me kasapwiluhkada pwe ke en kaunkitada oh wia at sounkopwung?’ Iei ih me Koht ketin poaronedohr pwe en kaunda aramas akan oh doarehkinirailla sawas en tohnlengo me pwarohng nan kisin tuhke mpwumwpwulo. \x - \xo 7.35 \xt Eks. 2.14.\x*  
\v 36 Eri, e ahpw kahluwaier aramas ako sang Isip, wiahda manaman kapwuriamwei tohto nan Isip oh nan Sehd Weitahta, oh pil nan sapwtehno, erein sounpar pahisek. \x - \xo 7.36 \xt Eks. 7.3; b Eks. 14.21; c Nempe 14.33.\x*  
\v 37 Iei ih Moses me pil ndaiong aramas en Israel ko, ‘Koht pahn ketin poaronedohng kumwail soukohp men nin duwen eh ketin poaroneiehdo, soukohp menet pahn kohsang nanpwungen riamwail kan.’ \x - \xo 7.37 \xt Deud. 18.15,18.\x*  
\v 38 Iei ih ohlo me iangehr mehn Israel ko pokonpene nan sapwtehn oh mihmi wasao iangahki samatail kahlap ako oh pil iangahki tohnlengo me mahseniong ih pohn Nahna Sainai. E pil alehsang rehn Koht mahsen en komour pwe en kadauredohng kitail. \x - \xo 7.38 \xt Eks. 19.1—20.17; Deud. 5.1-33.\x*   
\p
\v 39 “Ahpw samatail kahlap ako sohte men peikiong; ahpw re kesepwekehla, oh men pwuralahng Isip.  
\v 40 Eri, irail ndaiong Aaron, ‘Komw wiahiong kiht ekei kohten me pahn tieng mwoht. Se sehse dahme wiawihongehr Moses me kahluweikitodo sang nan Isip.’ \x - \xo 7.40 \xt Eks. 32.1.\x*  
\v 41 Iei ahnsou me irail wiahda dikedik ehu me mwomwen koupwul men, oh meirongohng; oh wiahda kamadipw ehu pwe en kawauwih dikedik me re wiadahro. \x - \xo 7.41 \xt Eks. 32.2-6.\x*  
\v 42 Koht eri sohpeisang irail, oh mweidirailla en kaudokiong usu kan en pahnlahng, nin duwen me ntingdier nan pwuken soukohp ako, me mahsanih,  
\q1 ‘Aramas en Israel kan! Kaidehn ngehi  
\q2 me kumwail kemehkihla oh meirongkihla mahn akan  
\q2 erein sounpahr pahisek nan sapwtehno. \x - \xo 7.42 \xt Eimw. 5.25-27 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 43 Iei impwal en koht Molek me kumwail weuwa,  
\q2 oh sansal en Repan, amwail koht usuwo;  
\q2 Iei dikedik en eni kan me kumwail wiahda pwe kumwail en pwongih.  
\q1 Eri, I pahn kalipeikumwailla palilahn Papilon.’   
\p
\v 44 “Eri, samatail kahlap ako ahnekier impwalo me wia kasalepen Koht eh ketiket rehrail nan sapwtehno. Impwalo wiawidahr nin duwen me Koht ketin mahsanihong Moses, duwen mwohmw me e ketin kasalehiong. \x - \xo 7.44 \xt Eks. 25.9.40.\x*  
\v 45 Eri, mwuhr, samatail kahlap ako aleier impwalo sang rehn samahr ako. Irail eri wiahda ni arail iangala Sosua oh kalowehdier sahpw akan me Koht ketin kausasang towe kan mwohrail. Eri, impwal wet mihmihte wasao lao lel ni mwehin Depit. \x - \xo 7.45 \xt Sos. 3.14-17.\x*  
\v 46 Depit eri kenikenla rehn Koht, oh peki Koht en ketin mweidohng en wiahda ehu tehnpas ong Koht en Seikop. \x - \xo 7.46 \xt 2 Sam. 7.1-16; 1 Kron. 17.1-14.\x*  
\v 47 Ahpw Solomon me kauwadahng Koht tehnpas wet. \x - \xo 7.47 \xt 1 Nan. 6.1-38; 2 Kron. 3.1-17.\x*   
\p
\v 48 “Ahpw Koht, Wasa Lapalahpie, sohte kin ket nan tehnpas akan me aramas kin kauwada, nin duwen me soukohpo mahsanih:   
\q1
\v 49 ‘Kaun-o ketin mahsanih, nanleng iei mwoalei,  
\q2 oh sampah iei utupen aluweluwei kat.  
\q1 Soangen tehnpas da me kumwail pahn kauwadahng ie?  
\q2 Ia wasa me I pahn kousoan ie? \x - \xo 7.49 \xt Ais. 66.1-2.\x*   
\q1
\v 50 Kaidehn pein ngehi me wiahda mepwukat koaros?’   
\p
\v 51 Stipen ahpw usehla koasoi, “Ia uwen amwail keptakai! Ia uwen rotorot en mohngiongimwail kan! Ia uwen amwail salengepon ong mahsen en Koht! Kumwail pil duwehte samamwail kahlap ako: kumwail pil kin uhwong Ngehn Sarawi! \x - \xo 7.51 \xt Ais. 63.10.\x*  
\v 52 Mie emen soukohp me samamwail kahlap ako sohte kin kaloke? Pwe re kemelahr sapwellimen Koht meninkeder kan me pakairkihdo duwen ketidohn sapwellime Ladu sarawi mahsie. A met kumwail ahpw pangala oh kemehla.  
\v 53 Iei kumwail me aleier sapwellimen Koht kosonned, me tohnleng kan ketikidohr, kumwail ahpw sohte peikiong!”   
\s1 Koasdien Stipen  
\p
\v 54 Eri, ni Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo ar rongorong Stipen, re ahpw inenen lingeringerda oh ngih tehte ong.  
\v 55 Stipen ahpw direkihla Ngehn Sarawi oh saradahng nanleng oh udiahl sapwellimen Koht lingan oh pil Sises me ketiket ni palimaun en Koht.  
\v 56 E ahpw nda, “Kumwail kilang! I kilangehr nanleng eh ritidahr oh pil Nein-Aramas eh ketiket ni palimaun en Koht!”   
\p
\v 57 Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo ahpw weriwer oh pinahla salengerail kan, oh irail koaros wiahkinteieu tangpenehng.  
\v 58 Irail eri keseieilahng likin kahnimwo oh kate. Sounkadehde ko kihong arail likou puhp kan rehn mwahnakapw emen me adaneki Sohl pwe en apwahpwalih.  
\v 59 Re ahpw nantikihlahte ar katekate Stipen me likilikweriong Kaun-o, patopatohwan, “Maing Kaun Sises! Komw ketin ale ngeniet!”  
\v 60 Ih eri kelehpwikihdi oh ngihl laudida, patohwan, “Maing, komw dehr ketikihong irail pwukoahpen dihp wet.” Mwurin eh nda met, e ahpw mehla.   
\c 8  
\p
\v 1 Sohl eri pwungki eh kamakamala.  
\s1 Sohl Keme Mwomwohdiso  
\p Eri, ni rahnohte mwomwohdiso me mi nan Serusalem ahpw tapihada alehdi kamakam laud. Irail koaros me pwosonlahr, likin wahnpoaron ko, tangpeseng nan sapwen Sudia oh Sameria.  
\v 2 Me poadidi kei ahpw sengisengki Stipen oh sarepedi.   
\p
\v 3 Sohl ahpw songosong en kauwehla mwomwohdiso, ni eh papahngseli ehuehu ihmw kan oh ruwahdekiei me pwosonlahr akan, ohl oh lih, oh keseirailong nan imweteng. \x - \xo 8.3 \xt Wie. 22.4-5; 26.9-11.\x*   
\s1 Rongamwahu Kalohkseli nan Sameria  
\p
\v 4 Me pwoson ko me tangpesengier ahpw lel wasa koaros, oh lohlohkiseli mahseno.  
\v 5 Pilip ahpw kohla nan kahnimw en Sameria oh padahkihong aramas en wasao duwen Mesaia.  
\v 6 Pokon en aramas akan eri inenen karonge mwahu dahme Pilip nda. Irail koaros rong oh kilang manaman akan me e wiadahr.  
\v 7 Eri, ngehn saut tohto ahpw pedoisang rehn aramas tohto kin wie weriwer laud, oh me mwoator tohto oh me nehtuk kan re pil mwahulahr.  
\v 8 Eri, peren laud ahpw kipehdi nan Sameria.   
\p
\v 9 Mie ohl emen me adaneki Saimon, me kin koukousoan nan kahnimwo, me mehn Sameria kan kin kapwuriamweiki eh wunahni kan. E kin kose me ih emen aramas lapalap.  
\v 10 Eri, irail koaros me mi nan kahnimwo, me tikitik oh lapalap akan, kin tehk mwahu, oh kin nda, “Iei ih me manaman en Koht, me kitail kin kahdaneki ‘Manaman Lapalap.’”  
\v 11 Ahnsou reirei aramas ako kin rong ih mehlel pwehki eh wunahni kan eh kin kapwuriamwei ong irail.  
\v 12 Ahpw ni ahnsou me irail rongehr en Pilip eh kapahrengki rongamwahu en Wehin Koht oh mwaren Sises Krais, irail koaros, ohl oh lih akan, ahpw papidaisla.   
\p
\v 13 Pein Saimon pil pwosonla; oh mwurin eh papidaislahr e ahpw werekiong Pilip; oh e inenen pwuriamweikihla eh kilang manaman kapwuriamwei kan me wiawidahr.   
\p
\v 14 Eri, wahnpoaron ako me mi Serusalem ahpw rongada me mehn Sameria kan pil aleier mahsen en Koht. Re ahpw kadarala Piter oh Sohn rehrail.  
\v 15 Ni en Piter oh Sohn ara lel Sameria, ira ahpw kapakapki me pwoson akan pwe re en ale Ngehn Sarawi.  
\v 16 Pwehki Ngehn Sarawi saikinte ti pohn emen irail, ahpw re papidaislahte ni mwaren Kaun Sises.  
\v 17 Eri, Piter oh Sohn ahpw pwil pehra ko pohrail, irail ahpw ale Ngehn Sarawi.   
\p
\v 18 Eri, Saimon kilangada me re ale Ngehno ni en wahnpoaron ako ara pwil pehra ko pohrail, e ahpw kihong Piter oh Sohn mwohni,  
\v 19 oh peki rehra, “Kumwa pil ketikihong ie manamanen, pwe aramas koaros me I pahn pwil pehi kat powe en ale Ngehn Sarawi.”   
\p
\v 20 Piter eri sapengki, “Kowe oh noumw mwohnien en lekdekla nan ehl, pwehki omw kihkihong me ke kak pwainkihda mwohni sapwellimen Koht kisakis!  
\v 21 Sohte pwaisomw de omw tungoal nan at doadoahk, pwehki omw mohngiong sohte pwung mwohn silangin Koht.  
\v 22 Eri, koluhkihla omw lamalam suweden, oh peki rehn Kaun-o pwe en ketin mahkikihong uhk soangen lamalam suweden.  
\v 23 Pwe I ese me ke inenen diren peirin oh dihp salihiukdier.”   
\p
\v 24 Saimon eri patohwanohng ira, “Kalahngan en kumwa, kumwa kapakapkin ie rehn Kaun-o, pwe soahng pwukat me kumwa mahsaniher en dehr lelohng ie.”   
\p
\v 25 Eri, mwurin ara wiahier ara kadehde oh padahkiher mahsen en Kaun-o, Piter oh Sohn ahpw pwurala Serusalem. Oh ni ara pwurupwurala ira ahpw kalohkiseli Rongamwahwo nan kousapw tohto nan Sameria.   
\s1 Pilip oh mehn Idiopia men  
\p
\v 26 A tohnleng en Kaun-o men ahpw mahsanihong Pilip, “Onopada pwe ke en kohdihla palieir ni ahl me kohsang Serusalem kolahng Kasa.” (Ahl wet solahr me keid ie ahnsou wet.)  
\v 27-28 Pilip eri onopada oh mwesel. Ni ahnsowo ohlen Idiopia me lek wusol men, ohl lapalap kesempwal emen me kin apwahpwalih wasahn nekinek en lih nanmwarkien Idiopia. Ohlo kohdalahngehr Serusalem pwe en kaudokiong Koht, oh ni eh pwurupwuralahng ni imwe dake were kuruma, e ahpw wadewadek pwuken soukohp Aiseia.  
\v 29 Ngehn Sarawi ahpw mahsanihong Pilip, “Keiwohng mpen kurumahn.”  
\v 30 Pilip eri tangala oh rongada en ohlo eh wadewadek pwuken soukohp Aiseia, e ahpw idek reh, “Ia duwe, komw wehwehki dahme komw wadewadeken?”   
\p
\v 31 Ohlo ahpw sapengki, “Ia duwen ei pahn kak wehwehki, ma sohte me pahn kawehwehiong ie?” E ahpw lukeiong Pilip en karada oh iang mwohndi nan kurumao.  
\v 32 Iren Pwuhk Sarawi me ohlo wadewadek, iei met:  
\q1 “E rasehng sihpw men me pakahrlahng en kamakamala,  
\q2 e rasehng sihmpwul me sohte kin weriwer ni ahnsou me wune kan pahn seiseisang.  
\q2 E sohte kin nda mehkot. \x - \xo 8.32 \xt Ais. 53.7-8 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 33 Aramas akan kasarowehdi, oh re sohte wiahiong me pwung.  
\q2 Sohte me kak koasoia duwen kadaudoke kan,  
\q2 pwehki eh mour nin sampah wet ididier.”   
\p
\v 34 Ohlo ahpw peki rehn Pilip, “Komw padahkihong ie, ihs me soukohpo koasoakoasoia duwe? Ma pein ih de emen tohrohr?”  
\v 35 Pilip ahpw tapihda eh koasoi, tepida sang iren Pwuhk Sarawi wet, e ahpw koasoia ong ohlo duwen Rongamwahu en Sises.  
\v 36 Eri, ni ara tangatang kohdihla nan ahlo, ira ahpw lellahng wasa kis me pihl mie, oh ohlo ahpw mahsanih, “Iet pihlen, dahme kerompwa pwe I en dehr papidaisla?”   
\p
\v 37 [Pilip ahpw patohwanohng, “Komw kak papidaisla ma komw pwoson nan mohngiongomw unsek.”  
\p Ohlo eri sapengki, “I pwoson me Sises Krais me Sapwellimen Koht.”]   
\p
\v 38 Eri, ohlo ahpw mahsanih were kurumao en uhdi; oh ira koaros ahpw ketidilahng nan pihlo. Pilip eri papidaisihala ohlo.  
\v 39 Ni ara pwurada sang nan pihlo, Ngehn Sarawi eri ketin karirihala Pilip sang ohlo. Ohlo eri sohla mahsanih Pilip, e ahpw douluhla nan eh seiloak pereperen kohla.  
\v 40 Pilip ahpw lel Asodus oh kalokalohkiseli Rongamwahwo nan kisin kahnimw kan lao lel Sesaria.   
\c 9  
\s1 Sohl Wiliakapwala  
\r (Pil tehk Wie. 22.6-16; 26.12-18.)  
\p
\v 1 Ni ahnsowo Sohl nannantihongete eh men kemehla tohnpadahk en Kaun-o. E ahpw kohla rehn Samworo Lapalap  
\v 2 oh peki kisinlikoun mweimwei pwe en kak pedolong nan sinakoke kan en mehn Suhs nan Damaskus, pwe ma e pahn diarada emen rehn irail me kin ideidawehn Ahl en Kaun-o wasao, en kak salihedi, sohte lipilipil, ohl de lih, oh kahredohng Serusalem.   
\p
\v 3 Eri, ni en Sohl eh kohkowohng Damaskus, oh kereniongehr kahnimwo, marain ehu sang nanleng ahpw kapilpene.  
\v 4 E ahpw pwupwudiong nan pwehl oh rongada ngihl ehu me peidohng, mahsanih, “Sohl, Sohl, dahme ke kin kemekemehkin ie?”   
\p
\v 5 Sohl ahpw patohwan, “Ihs komwi, Maing?”  
\p Ngihlo ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “Ngehi Sises, me ke kin kemekeme.  
\v 6 Uhda oh kohwei nan kahnimwen, pwe iei wasa me e pahn sansal ong uhk dahme ke pahn wia.”   
\p
\v 7 Irail ko me iang Sohl seiseiloak, re ahpw uhdi oh nennenla. Irail rongada ngihlo, re ahpw sohte kilang mehkot.  
\v 8 Sohl eri uhda sang nanpwel oh pehdpeseng, ahpw sohte kak kilang wasa. Irail eri ale peh kahrelahng Damaskus.  
\v 9 E ahpw sohte kak kilang wasa erein rahn siluh, oh ni ahnsowo e pil sohte tungoale de nim mehkot.   
\p
\v 10 Mie emen tohnpadahk nan Damaskus, ede Ananaias, me Kaun-o ketin mahsanihong nan kaudiahl ehu, “Ananaias!”  
\p E ahpw patohwan, “Iet ngehi, Maing at Kaun!”   
\p
\v 11 Kaun-o ahpw mahsanihong, “Onopada pwe ke en kowohng nan ahl me adaneki Ahl Inen oh rapahki nan imwen Sudas ohl emen sang Tarsus me ede Sohl. Sohl wie kapakap,  
\v 12 oh nan kaudiahl ehu e kilangada ohl emen ede Ananaias me kohdo oh pwil peh kan powe pwe en kak pil pwurehng kilangada wasa.”   
\p
\v 13 Ananaias ahpw patohwan, “Maing at Kaun, aramas tohto padahkihong ie duwen ohl menet, oh duwen soahng suwed koaros me e wiahiong sapwellimomwi aramas akan nan Serusalem.  
\v 14 Oh met e kodohngehr Damaskus pwehki manaman me e alesangehr samworo lapalap akan pwe en koledi aramas koaros me kin pwongih komwi.”   
\p
\v 15 Kaun-o ahpw mahsanihong Ananaias, “Kohwei pwe I piladahr ohlo pwe en papah ie oh kasalehiong mehn liki kan oh nanmwarki kan oh pil mehn Israel kan mwarei.  
\v 16 Oh pein ngehi pahn kasalehiong soahng koaros me e uhdahn pahn lokolok pwehki ngehi.”   
\p
\v 17 Ananaias eri kohla oh pedolong nan ihmwo oh pwil peh ko pohn Sohl. E ahpw nda, “Riei Sohl, Kaun-o ketin kadariedohr, iei Sises me ke kilangehr ni omw kohkohdo pohn ahlo. E ketin kadariehdo pwe ke en kak pwurehng kilangada wasa oh audaudkihda Ngehn Sarawi.”  
\v 18 Ni ahnsowohte mehkot me duwehte wunen mwahmw ahpw pwupwudi sang nan pwoaren mesen Sohl ko, oh e ahpw pil pwurehng kak kilangada wasa. E ahpw uhda oh papidaisla; \x - \xo 9.18 \xt Dop. 11.13-15.\x*  
\v 19 oh mwurin eh tungoalehr, e ahpw kehlailda.  
\s1 Sohl wia Padahk nan Damaskus  
\p Sohl eri mihmihki erein rahn ekei nan Damaskus ieiang tohnpadahk kan.  
\v 20 E ahpw kin inenwohng sinakoke kan en mehn Suhs kan oh tapihada padahk duwen Sises. E ahpw kin ndaiong irail me Sises iei Sapwellimen Koht Iehros.   
\p
\v 21 Irail koaros me rong ahpw inenen pwuriamweikihla, oh idek, “Kaidehn ih ohl menet me kin kemekemehla irail kan me kin pwongih ohl me mwaren Sises, nan Serusalem? Kaidehn e kohdo wasaht pwehn koliraildi oh kahreiraillahng rehn samworo lapalap ako?”   
\p
\v 22 Ahpw en Sohl eh padahk inenen kehlail mehlel sang mahs, oh eh kadehde kan me Sises ih me Mesaia me inenen kehlail me kahrehiong mehn Suhs me mi nan Damaskus ar sohte kak sapengki mehkot.   
\p
\v 23 Mwurin rahn ekei, mehn Suhs ako pokonpene pwe re en wie lamalamki duwen ar pahn kemehla Sohl. \x - \xo 9.23 \xt 2 Kor. 11.32-33.\x*  
\v 24 Ahpw mie me padahkihong Sohl dahme re wie lamalamkiher. Ni rahn oh pil nipwong irail kin sinsile wenihmw kan en kahnimwo pwe re en kemehla Sohl.  
\v 25 Pwohng ehu iengen Sohl ko ahpw kihong nan kopwou ehu oh kadaridi sang pohn kehlo.   
\s1 Sohl nan Serusalem  
\p
\v 26 Sohl ahpw kohla Serusalem oh song en tuhwong tohnpadahk ko. Irail ahpw sohte men kamehlele me ih emen tohnpadahk, oh re pil inenen masak.  
\v 27 Eri, Parnapas ahpw sewesehda oh kahredohng rehn wahnpoaron ko. Parnapas ahpw kawehwehiong wahnpoaron ko duwen en Sohl eh kilangehr Kaun-o pohn ahlo, oh dahme Kaun-o pil mahsanihong. E pil padahkihong irail duwen en Sohl eh eimah padahk ni mwaren Sises nan Damaskus.  
\v 28 Eri, Sohl ahpw kousoanla rehrail oh kohkohseli nan Serusalem eimah padapadahngkiseli mwaren Kaun-o.  
\v 29 E pil koasoia oh akamaiong mehn Suhs akan me lokaiahki lokaiahn Krihs, irail ahpw song re en kemehla.  
\v 30 Ni ahnsou me me pwoson akan rongadahr duwen met, re ahpw walahng Sohl Sesaria oh kadaralahng Tarsus.   
\p
\v 31 Eri, mwomwohdiso ahpw meleileidi wasa koaros nan Sudia, Kalili, oh Sameria. E ahpw pil kekeirda oh towe kan ngederla sang ni sawas en Ngehn Sarawi; oh re kin momour ni ar wauneki Kaun-o.   
\s1 Piter nan Lida oh Sopa  
\p
\v 32 Piter eri seiseiloakseli wasa koaros, oh ahnsou ehu e ahpw kohla pwe en pas rehn sapwellimen Koht aramas akan me koukousoan nan kahnimw Lida.  
\v 33 E ahpw tuhwong ohl emen wasao me adaneki Enias, me mwoator oh sohte kak kohsang nan dewe erein sounpar waluh.  
\v 34 Piter ahpw ndaiong, “Enias, Sises Krais ketin kakehleiukadahr. Uhda oh wahda kiomwen.” Ni ahnsowohte Enias ahpw kesihnenda.  
\v 35 Eri, aramas koaros me koukousoan nan Lida oh Saron, re ahpw kilang oh pwosonla Kaun-o.   
\p
\v 36 Mie lih emen me adaneki Dapida nan kahnimw Sopa me pil pwoson. (Ede ni mahsen en Krihs, Dorkas, me wehwehki tie.) Lih menet kin mweidohng eh ahnsou koaros en wiewia mwahu oh sewese me semwehmwe kan.  
\v 37 Ni ahnsowo e pil soumwahuda oh mehla. Paliwere eri kamwakelda oh koasoansoandiong nan pere ehu me mi powe.  
\v 38 Eri, Sopa sohte dohsang Lida, oh ni me pwosonlahr ako ar rongada me Piter mihmi nan Lida, re ahpw ilakihala ohl riemen reh pwe ira en walahng pekipek wet, “Kalahngan en komwi, komw mwadangodo reht.”  
\v 39 Eri, Piter ahpw kaunopada oh iangirahda. Ni Piter eh lel wasao, re kahredalahng nan perehn poweo. Liohdi kan koaros ahpw kapilpene wie sengiseng oh kasalehiong Piter arail likou kan me re likilikawih me Dorkas wiahda ni ahnsou me e momour.  
\v 40 Piter ahpw kihirailieisang nan pereo, ahpw kelehpwikihdi oh kapakap; e ahpw sohpeiong kahlepo oh nda, “Dapida, pwourda!” Liho ahpw pehdpeseng, oh ni eh kilangada Piter, e ahpw mwohdada.  
\v 41 Piter eri engalahng oh sewese en pwourda. E ahpw eker me pwoson akan oh pil liohdi kan, oh kasalehiong irail me liho mourdahr.  
\v 42 Rohng wet ahpw lohkseli nan Sopa oh aramas tohto ahpw pwosonla Kaun-o.  
\v 43 Piter eri koukousoan nan Sopa rahn tohto rehn ohl emen me adaneki Saimon, sounwia kilin kou men.   
\c 10  
\s1 Piter oh Kornilius  
\p
\v 1 Mie ohl emen nan Sesaria me ede Kornilius, kaunen pwihnen sounpei ehu me adaneki “Pwihnen Itali.”  
\v 2 Ih ohl poadidi men, ih oh eh peneinei pwon kin kaudok ong Koht. E kin wiewia soahng tohto me kin sewese mehn Suhs me semwehmwe kan, oh e kin poaden kapakap ong Koht.  
\v 3 Mwurin souwas ehu, mwein kulok siluh, e ahpw kilangada kaudiahl ehu, oh nan kaudiahl wet e udiahl tohnleng en Koht men me pedolong oh mahsanih, “Kornilius!”   
\p
\v 4 E ahpw kilenglahng tohnlengo oh masakada oh nda, “Maing, dahme komw kupwurki?”  
\p Tohnlengo ahpw mahsanih, “Koht ketin karongeier omw kapakap oh mahsaniher omw doadoahk en kadek kan oh ketin kupwureiukalahr.  
\v 5 Eri met, ilakihala ekei ohl ong Sopa pwe re en kahrehdo ohl emen me ede Saimon Piter.  
\v 6 E kin keikeiru nan imwen ohl me kin wiahda kilin kou me pil adaneki Saimon, e kin kousoan pohn oaroahr.  
\v 7 Eri, tohnlengo me koasoakoasoiong Kornilius ahpw ketiketlahsang. Kornilius ahpw ekerodo ladu riemen oh sounpei men me kin poadidiong kaudok, me kisehn irail kan me kin papah ih.  
\v 8 E ahpw mahsanihong irail duwen me wiawiher, e ahpw ilakihiraillahng Sopa.   
\p
\v 9 Pweidi songada, ni arail kohkohla kereniong Sopa, mwein nin souwas, Piter ahpw doudalahng pohn ihmwo pwe en kapakap. \x - \xo 10.9 \xt Sudid 8.5.\x*  
\v 10 E ahpw men mwengehda. Eri, ni ahnsou me kisin tungoal kan wie kaukaunop, e ahpw kilangada kaudiahl ehu.  
\v 11 E kilangada nanleng eh ritida, oh mehkot kohkohdihdo me likamwete lapalahn tehi ehu me keimw pahieu pekederdiong sampah.  
\v 12 Nan tehio soangen mahn neh pahpwoat koaros mi loale, pil mahn kerep oh limwahdek kan oh menpihr lawalo kan.  
\v 13 Ngihl ehu ahpw peidihdo, mahsanih, “Piter, uhda, kemehla oh kang.”   
\p
\v 14 Piter ahpw sapeng, “Maing ei Kaun, I sohte kak! Pwe I saikinte tungoale mehkot me samin ong kaudok oh sohte mwakelekel.”   
\p
\v 15 Ngihlo ahpw pwurehng mahsanih, “Ke dehr wiahki me samin mehkot me Koht mahsaniher me mwakelekel.”  
\v 16 Soahng wet wiawi pak silipak; eri meo ahpw pwurehng epidalahng nanleng.   
\p
\v 17 Piter ahpw mengimengloalki ia wehwehn kaudiahl wet me e kilangehr. Eri, ni ahnsowo ohl ako me Kornilius ilakihalahr ahpw diarada imwen Saimon, re ahpw kesihnenda limwahn wenihmwo.  
\v 18 Irail eri likwer oh idek, “Mie ohlen keiru men met ede Saimon Piter?”   
\p
\v 19 Ni en Piter eh medemedewehte en wehwehki kaudiahlo, Ngehn Sarawi ahpw mahsanih, “Ohl silimen miher met, me raparapahkin uhk.  
\v 20 Eri, onopada oh doudihla, oh ke dehpa kahng iangirailda, pwe ngehi me kadariraildo.”  
\v 21 Eri, Piter ahpw kohdihla ndaiong ohl ako, “Ih ngehi ohlo me kumwail raparapahki. Dahme kumwail kohkihdo?”   
\p
\v 22 Irail ahpw sapengki, “Kaunen sounpei men, Kornilius, me kadarkitodo. Ohl mwahu men, me kin pwongih Koht; oh mehn Suhs akan kin inenen wauneki mehlel. Eri, sapwellimen Koht tohnleng men me mahsanihong en lukeikomwilahng reh, pwe en kak rong dahme komw pahn mahsanih.”  
\v 23 Piter eri kasamwo ohl ako oh irail pweidi pwohngpwong wasao.  
\p Pweidi songada, Piter ahpw onopada oh iangirailda; oh ekei me pwoson sang Sopa pil iangirailda.  
\v 24 Ni keriaun rahn re ahpw lel Sesaria, wasa me Kornilius awiawih Piter ie, iangahki kiseh kan oh ekei kompoakepah me e luke.  
\v 25 Ni Piter eh pahn pedolong, Kornilius ahpw tuhwong, kelehpwikihdi, oh poaridi mwowe.  
\v 26 Piter ahpw kasihnenihada oh ndahng, “Uhda, pwe ngehi aramas emen.”  
\v 27 Piter eri koasoakoasoiong Kornilius ni ara pedolong nan ihmwo, wasa me aramas tohto pokopokon ie.  
\v 28 E ahpw ndaiong irail, “Pein kumwail ese mwahu me at lamalam sohte kin mweidohng mehn Suhs emen en pas de patehng kumwail mehn liki kan. Ahpw Koht ketin kasalehiong ie me I sohte pahn wiahki aramas emen me samin ong kaudok oh sohte mwakelekel.  
\v 29 Eri, ihme I pwarkihdo ni soh peikasal ni amwail ileklahng ie. Eri, I men idek rehmwail dahme kahrehda kumwail ilengkilahng ie?”   
\p
\v 30 Kornilius ahpw sapengki, “Rahn siluh dower pohn ei wie kapakap nan imwei, mwein kulok siluh mwurin souwas; eri, ahnsowohte ohl emen me mi nan likou melengileng ahpw kesihnenda mwohi,  
\v 31 oh mahsanih, ‘Kornilius, Koht ketin karonge omw kapakap, oh ketin kupwurki doadoahk mwahu kan me ke wiadahr.  
\v 32 Komw ilakihalahng Sopa emen pwe en kahrehdo ohl me adaneki Saimon Piter. Ih aramas en keiru men nan imwen Saimon, ohl me kin wia kilin kou, me koukousoan pohn oaroahr.’  
\v 33 Eri, I ahpw mwadangete ilekwohng komwi, oh omwi kadek me komw pwarkihdo. Eri met, kiht koaros patohier mwohn silangin Koht, awiawih se en rong mehkan me Kaun-o ketin mahsanihong komwi en padahkihong kiht.”   
\s1 En Piter eh Kapahrek  
\p
\v 34 Eri, Piter ahpw tapihada eh kapahrek: “Met I wehwehkidahr me Koht sohte ketin lipilipilki aramas. \x - \xo 10.34 \xt Deud. 10.17.\x*  
\v 35 E kin ketin kupwurperenki mehmen me kin lemmwiki, oh pil wiewia me pwung; sohte lipilipil ih soangen aramas da.  
\v 36 Kumwail ese rongamwahu en popohl sang rehn Sises Krais, me Kaunen mehkoaros.  
\v 37 Kumwail ese soangen mwekid kapwuriamwei me wiawiher nan wehin Israel pwon, tepida sang Kalili, mwurin papidaiso me Sohn kapahrengkiher.  
\v 38 Kumwail pil ese duwen Sises mehn Nasaret, duwen Koht eh ketikidohng powe Ngehn Sarawi oh manaman. E ketiseli wasa koaros, ketin wiahda me mwahu oh kakehlahda irail koaros me mihla pahn manaman en Tepil, pwehki en Koht eh ketin ieiang.  
\v 39 Eri, kiht me sounkadehdepen soahng koaros me e ketin wiahda nan sapwen mehn Suhs kan oh pil nan Serusalem. Irail kemehla ni arail pasuradahng nin lohpwuwo.  
\v 40 Ahpw ni rahn kesiluh Koht ketin kaiasada sang rehn me melahr akan, oh ketin mweidohng en sansalda.  
\v 41 Kaidehn aramas koaros me kilang, ahpw kihtete sounkadehde me Koht ketin piladahr. Se iang ih sak oh nim mwurin Koht eh ketin kaiasada sang mehla.  
\v 42 Oh e ketin mahsanihong kiht se en kalohkiseli rongamwahu ong aramas akan oh kadehde me iei ih me Koht ketin idihadahr pwe en wia sounkopwung en me momour oh me melahr akan.  
\v 43 Soukohp ako koaros kohpadahr duwen Sises ni arail mahsanih me mehmen me pwoson pahn ale lapwepen dipe pwehki manaman en mware.”   
\s1 Mehn Liki kan Ale Ngehn Sarawi  
\p
\v 44 Eri, ni en Piter eh koasoakoasoite, Ngehn Sarawi ahpw ketidihdo pohn irail koaros me rongorong mahseno.  
\v 45 Mehn Suhs ako me pwoson, me iang Piter kohdo sang Sopa, inenen pwuriamweikihla duwen Koht eh pil ketikihong sapwellime Ngehn Sarawi pohn mehn liki kan.  
\v 46 Pwehki ar rongada duwen ar tapihada lokolokaiahki ekei lokaia tohrohr oh kapikapinga sapwellimen Koht roson lapalap. Piter ahpw ngihl laudida oh nda,  
\v 47 “Aramas pwukat aleier Ngehn Sarawi nin duwen me kitail aleier; eri, mie emen me kak irehdihsang irail en papidaiskihla pihl?”  
\v 48 E ahpw padahkihong irail en papidaisla ni mwaren Sises Krais. Eri, irail ahpw peki en mihmi rehrail erein rahn ekei.   
\c 11  
\s1 En Piter eh Pakair ong Mwomwohdisohn Serusalem  
\p
\v 1 Eri, wahnpoaron ako oh pil me pwoson kan nan Sudia pwon rongehr me mehn liki kan pil aleier mahsen en Koht.  
\v 2 Ni ahnsou me Piter kohdalahng Serusalem, irail kan me kin nda me mehn liki kan uhdahn pahn sirkumsaisla ahpw lipahnedehki, nda,  
\v 3 “Komw wia mehn keiru men nan imwen mehn liki kan me sohte sirkumsais, oh komw pil sak rehrail!”  
\v 4 Piter eri padahkihong irail mehkoaros me wiawiher, sang nin tapio:   
\p
\v 5 “I wie kapakap nan kahnimw Sopa, I ahpw kilangada kaudiahl ehu. Nan kaudiahlo I kilangada mehkot me kohkohdiho likamwete lapalahn tehi ehu me keimw pahieu me pekederdihdo sang nanleng, oh uhdi limwahi.  
\v 6 I ahpw kilenglahng loale oh kilangada mahn mahnd oh lawalo kan, mahn kerep kan oh me limwahdek kan, oh pil menpihr lawalo kan.  
\v 7 I ahpw pil rongada ngihl ehu peidohng ie, me mahsanih, ‘Piter, uhda! Kemehla oh kang!’  
\v 8 I ahpw patohwan, ‘Maing ei Kaun, I sohte kak! Sohte mwenge me samin ong kaudok de sohte mwakelekel me pedolongehr nan ei tungoal auwet!’  
\v 9 Ngihlo ahpw pil pwurehng peidihdo sang nanleng, mahsanih, ‘Ke dehr wiahki me samin mehkot me Koht mahsaniher me mwakelekel.’  
\v 10 Eri, met wiawiher pahn pak silipak, oh mwuhr, meo ahpw pil pwurehng epidalahng nanleng.  
\v 11 Ni ahnsowohte ohl silimen me pekederdo rehi sang Sesaria ahpw lel ni ihmw me I keikeiru ieo.  
\v 12 Eri, Ngehn Sarawi ahpw pil mahsanihong ie I en iangirailda ni soh peikasal. Me pwoson wenemen pwukat pil iang ie patolahng Sesaria, oh kiht koaros eri pedolong nan imwen Kornilius.  
\v 13 Ohlo ahpw padahkihong kiht duwen eh kilangada tohnleng men eh kesikesihnen nan imwe, me mahsanih, ‘Kadaralahng emen nan Sopa rehn ohl emen me ede Saimon Piter;  
\v 14 e pahn padahkihong uhk mahsen akan me kowe oh pil omw peneinei pwon pahn mourkihla.’  
\v 15 Eri, ni ahnsou me I tapihada koasoi, Ngehn Sarawi ahpw ketidiong pohrail nin duwen eh ketidiong pohtail nin tapio.  
\v 16 Eri, I ahpw tamanda dahme Kaun-o mahsanih, ‘Sohn papidaisihkin kumwail pihl, a kumwail pahn papidaiskihla Ngehn Sarawi.’ \x - \xo 11.16 \xt Wie. 1.5.\x*  
\v 17 Me inenen sansal mwahu me Koht ketikihong mehn liki ko kalahnganohte me e ketikihong kitail ni ahnsou me kitail pwosonla atail Kaun Sises Krais. Eri, ihs ngehi pwe I en song irehdi Koht?”   
\p
\v 18 Ni arail rong met, re ahpw tokedihsang arail lipahned, irail eri kapikapinga Koht. Re ahpw koasoia, “Eri, Koht ketikihong mehn liki kan ahnsou mwahu en koluhla, wiliakapwala, oh komourla!”   
\s1 Mwomwohdisohn nan Andiok  
\p
\v 19 Eri, me pwoson akan pil mwarahkpeseng wasa kan pwehki kamakam me wiawi ni ahnsou me Stipen kamakamalahr. Ekei irail pil lellahng Penisia oh Saiprus oh Andiok, lohlohkiseli mahseno nanpwungen mehn Suhste. \x - \xo 11.19 \xt Wie. 8.1-4.\x*  
\v 20 Oh pil ekei me pwoson akan, ohl ekei sang Saiprus oh Sairihni, kolahngehr Andiok oh pil padahkihong mehn liki kan mahseno, padapadahkihong irail rongamwahu duwen Kaun Sises.  
\v 21 Manaman en Kaun-o ketin ieiang irail, oh aramas tohtohie pil pwosonlahr oh wekiongehr Kaun-o.   
\p
\v 22 Rongen mwekid wet pil lelohng mwomwohdiso nan Serusalem; eri, irail ahpw kadaralahng Parnapas Andiok.  
\v 23 Ni ahnsou me e lel wasao oh kilang duwen en Koht eh ketin kapaiahda aramas akan, e ahpw perenkihda oh koangngoangehkin irail koaros re en loalopwoat oh mehlel ong Kaun-o ni mohngiong unsek.  
\v 24 Parnapas ohl mwahu men, me diren Ngehn Sarawi oh pwoson. Eri, aramas tohtohie ahpw wekiong Kaun-o.   
\p
\v 25 Parnapas eri kolahng Tarsus pwe en rapahki Sohl.  
\v 26 Ni eh diarada e ahpw kahredohng Andiok. Nan irair en sounpar ehu ira riemenet kin tuhwong tohn mwomwohdiso oh kin padahki aramas tohto. Iei pil nan Andiok me tohnpadahk ko adanekihla sapwellimen Krais.   
\p
\v 27 Eri, ni rahn pwukat soukohp ekei ahpw kohsang Serusalem kolahng Andiok.  
\v 28 Emen irail, ede Akapwus, ahpw uhda oh sang ni manaman en Ngehn Sarawi e ahpw kohpada me lehk laud ehu kereniongehr kipehdi sampah pwon. (Lehko wiawiher ni ahnsou me Klaudius wia nanmwarki lapalap en Rom.) \x - \xo 11.28 \xt Wie. 21.10.\x*  
\v 29 Eri, tohnpadahk ko ahpw koasoanehdi me emenemen irail pahn kadarala uwen me e kak pwe en sewese riarail me pwoson akan me koukousoan nan Sudia.  
\v 30 Irail eri kapwaiada, oh kadaralahng mwohni ong me mah kan en mwomwohdiso, Parnapas oh Sohl me wa kohla.   
\c 12  
\s1 Pil ekei Kamakam  
\p
\v 1 Iei ahnsou wet me Nanmwarki Erod\f b \fr 12.1 \fk NANMWARKI EROD: \ft Erod Akripa Keieu, iei ih me kaunda Israel pwon.\f* ketin tapihada keme ekei tohn mwomwohdiso.  
\v 2 E ketin kemehkilahr kedlahs Seims, rien Sohn.  
\v 3 Ni eh mahsanihada me mehn Suhs kan perenki wiewia wet, e ahpw pil wonlahte oh pil koledi Piter. (Met wiawiher ni ahnsoun Sarawien Pilawa Sohte Doal Ihs.)  
\v 4 Mwurin eh ketin koledi Piter, e ahpw pil kesehlong nan imweteng, wasa me pwihnen sounpei pahieu wad pahmen ehu pwihn kin sinsile. Erod kupwukupwure en ketikihong Piter mwohn mwoalen kopwung mwohn aramas akan mwurin Pahsohpa. \x - \xo 12.4 \xt Eks. 12.1-27.\x* \fig |alt="HK-75B Sounpei en Rom" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 12.4" \fig*  
\v 5 Piter eri mihmihte nan imweteng ahpw tohn mwomwohdiso kan kin poaden kapakapki.   
\s1 Piter Saledekla sang nan Imweteng  
\p
\v 6 Pwohngpwong, mwohn en Erod eh pahn ketin kahredohng Piter rehn aramas akan, Piter ahpw wie memeir nanpwungen silepe riemen. E selkihdi selmete riapwoat; oh silepe kan sinsile wenihmwen imwetengo.  
\v 7 Ni ahnsowohte tohnleng en Kaun-o men ahpw kesihnenda wasao, oh marain ehu ahpw dakerada nan imwetengo. Tohnlengo ahpw koledi pwopwen Piter oh itik oh pangenda oh mahsanih, “Mwadang uhda!” Ni ahnsowohte selmete ko ahpw pwupwudihsang ni peh ko.  
\v 8 Tohnlengo ahpw mahsanih, “Katengehdi omw pirapiren, oh pirehdi omw suht kan.” Piter ahpw kapwaiada, oh tohnlengo ahpw mahsanih, “Pidkinuhkpene omw likoun likien, oh iangiehda.”  
\v 9 Piter eri idawehnieisang nan imwetengo. E sohte wehwehki ma iei mehlel me tohnlengo wiewiahiong, de kaudiahl ehu.  
\v 10 Ira ahpw daulih wasa me silepe keieu mihmi ie, oh pil keriau; oh mwuri, ira lelohng wenihmw mete ehu me sallahng nan kahnimwo. Wenihmwo ahpw pein ritidahng ira; ira eri pedoi. Ira ahpw aluhdihla pohn ahl apwoat; ni ahnsowohte tohnlengo ahpw sohrasang Piter.   
\p
\v 11 Eri, Piter ahpw wehwehkihda dahme wiawihiong, e ahpw nda, “I wehwehkidahr me mehlel apwoat met! Kaun-o ketin poaronehdo sapwellime tohnleng, oh ketin kapitiesang pahn manaman en Erod, oh pil sang mehkoaros me mehn Suhs akan kasikasik re en wiahiong ie.”   
\p
\v 12 A ni eh wehwehkidahr mwekid wet, e ahpw kohla ni imwen Mery, inen Sohn Mark. Aramas tohto me pokonpenehr oh wie kapakap wasao.  
\v 13 Piter eri letelet ni wenihmwen liki, oh serepein me wie papah wasao, me adaneki Rohda, ahpw kohdo pwe en sapeng.  
\v 14 Serepeino wehwehkihda ngilen Piter oh inenen perenkihda me kahrehda e sohte ritingada wenihmwo ahpw tangolongala nan ihmwo, oh kairehki aramas ako me Piter mihmi likio.  
\v 15 Re ahpw ndaiong serepeino, “Ke iahkalahr!” E ahpw kehlailkihte me e mehlel. Eri, re ahpw sapeng, ‘Mwein eh tohnleng.”   
\p
\v 16 Ni ahnsowohte Piter wie letelette. Irail eri ritingada wenihmwo, oh ni ar kilangada re inenen pwuriamweikihla.  
\v 17 Piter ahpw oaleiraildi pwe re en nennenla, ahpw kawehwehiong irail duwen en Kaun-o eh ketin kahluwa sang nan imwetengo. E ahpw nda, “Kumwail koasoiaiong Seims met, oh pil ong riatail teikan.” Ih eri mwesel oh kohkolahng ekis wasa.   
\p
\v 18 Ni eh rahnpeseng, silepe ko inenen pwonopwonkihda mehlel dahme wiawihong Piter.  
\v 19 Erod ahpw mahsanih re en rapahki; ahpw irail sohte kak diar. Erod eri kapeidek silepe ko oh ruwese re en kamakamala.  
\p Mwurin met Erod ahpw ketidihsang Sudia oh ketiket Sesaria ahnsou kis.   
\s1 Sipallahn Erod  
\p
\v 20 Erod inenen engiengda pahn mehn Dair oh Saidon. Eri, irail ahpw wia pwihn ehu kohla pwe re en tuhwong Erod. Keieu irail pekihda rehn Plastus me kin kakaun tehnpesen nanmwarkio, pwe en iangirailda. Irail eri kohla rehn Erod oh peki meleilei, pwehki sawasaparail kisin mwenge kin kohdo sang nan sapwen nanmwarkio. \x - \xo 12.20 \xt 2 Mak. 9.5-28.\x*   
\p
\v 21 Eri, ni rahn me kileledio, Erod ahpw kapwatkihda kapwat en nanmwarki oh ketidiong nan mwoale. E ahpw kapahrekiong aramas akan.  
\v 22 Irail ahpw werikihda, “Kaidehn aramas emen me koasoakoasoiet, pwe koht emen!”  
\v 23 Ni ahnsowohte tohnleng en Kaun-o men ahpw kesepwekehdi Erod, pwehki eh sohte kadehdehda me ih aramas emen, ahpw kaidehn ih Koht. Mwahs eri kangala oh e ahpw mehla.   
\p
\v 24 Mahsen en Koht eri lolohkseli oh pweida mehlel.   
\p
\v 25 Parnapas oh Sohl ahpw kanekehla ara doadoahk oh pil pwuralahng Serusalem, iangahki Sohn Mark.   
\c 13  
\s1 Parnapas oh Sohl Pilipilda oh Pekederla  
\p
\v 1 Nan mwomwohdisohn Andiok mie soukohp oh sounpadahk kei me iei: Parnapas, Simion (ede Toantoal), Lusius (sang Sairihni), Manaen (me tikida rehn Kepina Erod\f c \fr 13.1 \fk EROD: \ft Erod Antipas, kaunen Kalili (tehk Luk 3.1.)\f*), oh Sohl.  
\v 2 Ni arail kin papah Kaun-o oh kaisihsol, Ngehn Sarawi ahpw mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail katohrehla Parnapas oh Sohl, pwe ira en wia doadoahk me I kilelehiong ira.”   
\p
\v 3 Irail eri kaisihsol oh kapakap oh pwil pehrail kan pohra oh kadarirahla.   
\s1 Nan Saiprus  
\p
\v 4 Ngehn Sarawi eri poaronehla Parnapas oh Sohl, ira eri kohdilahng Seluhsia oh sereksang wasao sereklahng dekehn Saiprus.  
\v 5 Ni arail lel Salamis, ira ahpw kalohkiseli mahsen en Koht nan sinakoke kan en mehn Suhs akan. Sohn Mark pil iang ira pwe en sewesehkin ira doadoahk wet.   
\p
\v 6 Irail eri kakahnseli dekeo oh lellahng Papos. Irail eri tuhwong sounwia manaman men me adaneki Par-Sises, mehn Suhs men me kin koasoakoasoia me ih soukohp men.  
\v 7 Ohl menet kompoakepahn kepinahn dekeo, Serkius Paulus, me inenen loalokong mehlel. Kepinao ahpw ekerodo Parnapas oh Sohl pwehki eh men karonge mahsen en Koht.  
\v 8 Sounwia manaman Elimas (met iei ede ni mahsen en Krihs) ahpw pelianirahda. E song en wekidasang kepinao ni lamalamo.  
\v 9 Eri, Sohl—me pil adaneki Pohl—ahpw direkihla Ngehn Sarawi; e ahpw kakiledi sounwia manamano  
\v 10 oh ndaiong, “Kowe nein Tepil! Kowe imwintihtien soahng koaros me mwahu. Ke inenen direkihla soangen widing suwed koaros, oh ahnsou koaros ke kin songosong wekidohng sapwellimen Koht mehlel ong likamw!  
\v 11 Eri, limen Kaun-o pahn ketidi pohmw met, ke ahpw pahn maskunla oh sohte pahn kak kilang marain erein ahnsou kis.”  
\p Ni ahnsowohte Elimas ahpw maskunla oh alialuseli raparapahki emen mehn kahluwa.  
\v 12 Kepinao ahpw pwosonla ni eh kilangada dahme wiawihero, oh e inenen pwuriamweikihla padahkpen Kaun-o.   
\s1 Nan Andiok en Pisidia  
\p
\v 13 Pohl oh ienge ko ahpw sereklahng Papos oh kolahng Perka, nan Pampilia. Eri, iei wasao me Sohn Mark keseirahla ie oh pwuralahng Serusalem.  
\v 14 Ira eri mweselsang Perka oh kolahng Andiok en Pisidia; oh ni rahnen Sapad ira ahpw kohla nan sinakoke en mehn Suhs ako.  
\v 15 Eri, mwurin wadawad en Kosonned en Moses oh pil pwuken soukohp ako, me lapalap en sinakoke ko ahpw kairehkin ira, nda, “Riat akan, se men lukei kumwa en koasoiong aramas pwukat, ma mie rohng me kumwa kak kakehlakahkin kiht.”  
\v 16 Pohl eri uhda oh oaleirail oh tapihada eh padahk.  
\p “Iengei mehn Israel kan, oh koaros mehn liki kan me kin kaudokiong Koht, kumwail rong ie!  
\v 17 Koht en mehn Israel ketin piladahr samatail kahlap ako, oh kangederihirailla ni ahnsou me re koukousoan duwehte mehn liki kei nan Isip. Koht ketin kahluwahkinirail sang nan Isip sapwellime manaman lapalap. \x - \xo 13.17 \xt Eks. 1.7; b Eks. 12.51.\x*  
\v 18 Eri, erein sounpar pahisek e ketin apwahpwalih irail mehnda ma re kahngohdiong nan sapwtehn. \x - \xo 13.18 \xt Nempe 14.34; Deud. 1.31.\x*  
\v 19 E pil ketin kamwomwala wehi isuh nan wehin Kenan, oh ketin mweidohng sapwellime aramas akan en sapwenikihla sahpwo. \x - \xo 13.19 \xt Deud. 7.1; b Sos. 14.1.\x*  
\v 20 Eri, mwekid pwukat wiewiawihki erein sounpar 450.  
\p “Mwurin met e ketikihong irail sounkopwung kei, lao lel ni mwehin soukohp Samuel. \x - \xo 13.20 \xt S.K 2.16; b 1 Sam. 3.20.\x*  
\v 21 Eri, re ahpw peki emen nanmwarki. Koht eri ketikihong irail Sohl, nein Kis, sang ni kadaudok en Pensamin, pwe en wia arail nanmwarki erein sounpar pahisek. \x - \xo 13.21 \xt 1 Sam. 8.5; b 1 Sam. 10.21.\x*  
\v 22 Mwurin Koht eh ketin kasapwildi Sohl, e ahpw ketin kasapwilada Depit pwe en wiahla arail nanmwarki. Ih ohl menet me Koht ketin mahsanih duwe, ‘I diaradahr me Depit, nein Sehsi, iei soangen ohl me I kupwurki, soangen ohl me pahn kapwaiada mekoaros me I kupwurki en wia.’ \x - \xo 13.22 \xt 1 Sam. 13.14. b 1 Sam. 16.12; Mel. 89.20.\x*  
\v 23 Eri, emen kisehn kadaudok en Depit, Sises, iei ih me Koht ketin kasapwiladahr pwe en Sounkomourpen mehn Israel, nin duwen me e ketin inoukidahr.  
\v 24 Eri, mwohn Sises eh tapihada sapwellime doadoahk, Sohn ahpw padahkihong aramas en Israel kan koaros re en koluhla, kawiliakapwahda mourirail oh papidaisla. \x - \xo 13.24 \xt Mark 1.4; Luk 3.3.\x*  
\v 25 Eri, ni en Sohn eh kereniongehr kanekehla eh doadoahk, e ahpw mahsanihong aramas akan, ‘Ihs me kumwail medemedewe ong ie? Kaidehn ngehi me kumwail kin kasikasiko. Ahpw kumwail rong! Emen pahn ketido mwuri, me pein ngehi sohte warohng en kihsang sapwellime suht ni aluweluwe kan.’ \x - \xo 13.25 \xt Sohn 1.20; b Mad. 3.11; Mark 1.7; Luk 3.16; Sohn 1.27.\x*   
\p
\v 26 “Riei ko, kadaudok en Eipraam ko, oh mehn liki kan me mi met me kin kaudok ong Koht, iei kitail me rongen komour wet pekederdohng!  
\v 27 Pwe aramas akan me kin kousoan Serusalem, oh arail kaun akan, re sohte ese me iei ih me Sounkomour, oh re pil sohte wehwehki mahsen en soukohp ako me kin wadawad ni rahnen Sapad akan koaros. Ahpw irail kapwaiadahr mahsen en soukohp ako ni arail kemehla Sises.  
\v 28 Ni arail sohte kak diarada kahrepe ehu me re kak kemehkihla, re ahpw peki rehn Pailet en kemehla. \x - \xo 13.28 \xt Mad. 27.22-23; Mark 15.13-14; Luk 23.21-23; Sohn 19.15.\x*  
\v 29 Eri, mwurin arail wiahier soahng koaros me Pwuhk Sarawi mahsanih duwen ih, re ahpw kihdihsang nin lohpwuwo oh nekidediong nan sousou ehu. \x - \xo 13.29 \xt Mad. 27.57-61; Mark 15.42-47; Luk 23.50-56; Sohn 19.38-42.\x*  
\v 30 Ahpw Koht ketin kaiasada Sises sang mehla,  
\v 31 oh erein rahn tohto, irail kan me ieiangehr ih seiloak sang Kalili lel Serusalem ahpw uduhdiahl ih. Met iei irail me wia sapwellime sounkadehde ong aramas en Israel kan. \x - \xo 13.31 \xt Wie. 1.3.\x*  
\v 32-33 Eri, iet kiht me pil wadohng kumwail Rongamwahu wet: duwen me Koht ketin inoukihong atail pahpa kahlap ako e ahpw ketin kapwaiadahr; pwe met e ketin kapwaiong kitail me wia kadaudokarail, ni eh ketin kaiasada Sises. Duwen eh ntingdier nan Melkahka keriau:  
\q1 ‘Kowe nei pwutak,  
\q2 rahnwet I wialahr Semomw.’ \x - \xo 13.32-33 \xt Mel. 2.7.\x*   
\m
\v 34 Oh iet duwen me Koht ketin mahsaniheki duwen eh kaiasada sang mehla, pwe e sohte pahn mwerpeseng nan sousou:  
\q1 ‘I pahn ketikihong uhk wahu oh kapai mehlel kan  
\q2 me I inoukihongehr Depit.’ \x - \xo 13.34 \xt Ais. 55.3 (LXX).\x*   
\m
\v 35 Nin duwen me e pil mahsanih ekis wasa:  
\q1 ‘Komwi sohte pahn ketin mweidohng sapwellimomwi ladu loalopwoato en mwerpeseng nan sousou.’ \x - \xo 13.35 \xt Mel. 16.10.\x*   
\m
\v 36 Pwe Depit kin papah sapwellimen Koht kosonned kan nan eh ahnsou. Eri, e ahpw sipallahr oh seridier limwahn eh pahpa kahlap ako; oh e pil mwerpeseng nan sousou.  
\v 37 Ahpw ih me Koht ketin kaiasada sang mehla sohte mwerpeseng nan sousou.  
\v 38-39 Kumwail koaros riei ko, en ese ni mehlel me Sises me kahrehda padahk en lapwapen dihp akan eh kowohng kumwail. Kumwail en pil ese me mehmen me pwoson pahn saledeksang dipe kan koaros me Kosonned en Moses sohte kak kasaladakasang kumwail.  
\v 40 Eri, kumwail en kanahieng pwe kokohp wet en soukohp ako de pweida rehmwail:   
\q1
\v 41 ‘Kilang! Kumwail me lahlahwe kan, kumwail pahn pwuriamweite mehla!  
\q1 Pwe doadoahk me I wiewia nan amwail rahn akan,  
\q2 iei mehkot me kumwail sohte pahn kamehlele,  
\q2 mehnda ma emen pahn kawehwehiong kumwail!’” \x - \xo 13.41 \xt Apak. 1.5 (LXX).\x*   
\p
\v 42 Ni en Pohl oh Parnapas ara mweselsang nan sinakokeo, aramas akan eri luke ira en pil pwurodo ni rahnen Sapad kohkohdo, oh pwurehng padahkihong irail duwen soahng pwukat.  
\v 43 Mwurin aramas ako ar mweselsang mihtingo, mehn Suhs tohtohie, oh pil mehn liki tohtohie me wekiong pelien lamalam en mehn Suhs, re ahpw idawehnla Pohl oh Parnapas. Wahnpoaron ako eri koasoiong irail oh koangngoangehkin irail re en loalopwoatete oh momourki kalahngan en Koht.   
\p
\v 44 A ni keriaun rahnen Sapad, kereniong aramas akan koaros me mi nan kahnimwo pil kohdo pwe re en rong mahsen en Kaun-o.  
\v 45 Ni mehn Suhs ko ar kilangada pokono, re ahpw direkihla peirin, irail ahpw pelianda dahme Pohl kin koasoia, oh re kin kasohwe.  
\v 46 Pohl oh Parnapas eri eimahda nan ara padahk oh nda, “Me inenen konehng mehlel mahsen en Koht en kohieng kumwail mahs. Ahpw pwehki amwail soikala, oh sohte anahne mour soutuk, se pahn piseksang kumwail oh kolahng rehn mehn liki kan.  
\v 47 Pwe iet duwen kehkehlik me Koht ketin koasoanediong kiht:  
\q1 ‘I pilkumwaildahr pwe kumwail en wia marain ehu ong mehn liki kan,  
\q2 pwe tohn sampah koaros en kak mourla.’” \x - \xo 13.47 \xt Ais. 42.6; 49.6.\x*   
\p
\v 48 Ni mehn liki kan ar rongada met, re ahpw perenkihda oh kapinga mahsen en Kaun-o. Eri, irail kan me pilipildahngehr mour soutuk re ahpw pwosonla.   
\p
\v 49 Mahsen en Kaun-o ahpw lohkseli wasa koaros nan sahpwo.  
\v 50 Mehn Suhs kan ahpw kamwoarongehda kaun akan en kahnimwo oh lih soupeidien mehn liki kan me kin kaudok ong Koht. Irail ahpw keme Pohl oh Parnapas, oh kausasang ira nan sapwarail.  
\v 51 Wahnpoaron ako eri sipedasang pwelen nehra ko pwe en pelian irail; oh ira ahpw douluhllahng Aikoniomw. \x - \xo 13.51 \xt Mad. 10.14; Mark 6.11; Luk 9.5; 10.11.\x*  
\v 52 Eri, tohnpadahk kan nan Andiok ahpw direkihla peren oh Ngehn Sarawi.   
\c 14  
\s1 Nan Aikoniomw  
\p
\v 1 Soahngohte pil wiawi nan Aikoniomw: Pohl oh Parnapas kohla ni sinakoke en mehn Suhs ako oh padahk ni mwohmw ehu me kahrehda me tohtohie, mehn Suhs oh pil mehn liki kan, pil pwosonla.  
\v 2 Eri, mehn Suhs ako me sohte men kamehlele ahpw kamwoarongada mehn liki kan oh kahrehiong arail uhwong me pwoson ako.  
\v 3 Wahnpoaron ako ahpw mihmihki wasao ahnsou reirei. Ira eimah padapadahngki duwen Kaun-o, me ketin kasalehda me ara padahngki duwen sapwellime kalahngan me mehlel oh pwung ni eh ketikihong ira manaman en wia manaman kapwuriamwei kei.  
\v 4 Aramas akan nan kahnimwo ahpw pwalpeseng, ekei iangala mehn Suhs ako, a ekei iangala wahnpoaron ako.   
\p
\v 5 Eri, mehn liki kan oh mehn Suhs akan, iangahki arail kaun akan, re ahpw koasoanehdi re en wiakauwe wahnpoaron ako oh kate ira.  
\v 6 A ni en wahnpoaron ako ara esehda met, ira ahpw tangdoaui, tangalahng Listra oh Derpe nan Likaonia oh pil sahpw akan me kapilpene kahnimw ko.  
\v 7 Ira eri kalokalohkiseli Rongamwahu wasa ko.   
\s1 Nan Listra oh Derpe  
\p
\v 8 Mie ohl emen me koukousoan nan Listra me neh mwoator sang ni eh ipwidi, oh e sohte kin alu.  
\v 9 Ih eri iang rongorong en Pohl eh padahk. Ni Pohl eh kilangada me eh pwoson pahn kak kakehlahda, e ahpw kakiledi  
\v 10 oh ngihl laudida, nda, “Komw kesihnenda!” Ohlo eri mesiekda oh tapihada alialuseli.  
\v 11 A ni en pokono ar kilangehr me Pohl wiadahro, re ahpw tapihada weriwer ni pein arail mahsen en Likaonia: “Koht akan wie aramasalahr oh ketidohr rehtail!”  
\v 12 Re ahpw kihong eden Parnapas “Seus,” oh eden Pohl “Ermihs,” pwehki ih me koasoakoasoikin ira.  
\v 13 Samworo en koht Seus, me eh imwen kaudok mi limwahn kahnimwo, ahpw kahrehdo kouwol kei oh wahnrohs kei ni wenihmwo. Samworo oh pokono men wia arail meirong ong wahnpoaron ako.   
\p
\v 14 A ni Pohl oh Parnapas ara esehda dahme irail men wiahiong ira, ira ahpw tehrpeseng ara likoun liki ko oh tangalahng nanwerengen pokono, weriwer oh ndinda,  
\v 15 “Kumwail ohl akan! Dahme kahrehda kumwail wiahki met? Kiht aramas ekei duwehte kumwail! Se kodohng wasaht pwe se en kalohki ong kumwail Rongamwahu, pwe en kawengkumwailsang soahng soh katepe pwukat oh kawekiong Koht ieias, Koht me ketin kapikada lahng oh sampah, madau, oh pil soahng koaros me audeparail. \x - \xo 14.15 \xt Eks. 20.11; Mel. 146.6.\x*  
\v 16 Mahso e ketin mweidohng aramas koaros en wia pein nsenarail.  
\v 17 Ahpw ahnsou koaros e kin ketikihda kadehdepen pein ih sang ni doadoahk mwahu me e kin ketin wia. E kin ketikihong kumwail keteu sang nanleng oh e pil ketikihong kumwail wahnsahpw ni ahnsou kan me konehng. Oh e pil ketikihong kumwail mwenge, oh pil audehkihda nan mohngiongimwail kan peren.”  
\v 18 Mehndahte wahnpoaron ko ara wia mahsen pwukat, ahpw me apwal ong ira en soikala en aramas akan ar men meirong ong ira.   
\p
\v 19 Pil mie ekei mehn Suhs me kohdo sang Andiok en Pisidia oh pil sang Aikoniomw. Irail pwukat eri kalowehdi pokono ong arail pali; re kate Pohl oh wurahdekieisang nan kahnimwo wurahdekieilahng liki. Irail ahpw kihkiong me e melahr.  
\v 20 Eri, nindokon irail ko me pwosonlahr ar kapikapil, Pohl ahpw pwourda oh pwuralahng nan kahnimwo. Pweidi songada, Pohl oh Parnapas ahpw douluhllahng Derpe.   
\s1 Pwuralahng Andiok en Siria  
\p
\v 21 Pohl oh Parnapas ahpw kalohkiseli Rongamwahu nan Derpe, oh aramas tohtohie me pwosonla. Ira eri pwuralahng Listra, oh douluhllahng Aikoniomw oh Andiok en Pisidia.  
\v 22 Ira eri kakehlakahda me pwoson akan, oh koangngoangehkin irail en loalopwoatohngete arail pwoson. Ira eri nda, “Kitail uhdahn pahn powehdi soangen kahpwal tohto pwe kitail en kak pedolong nan Wehin Koht.”  
\v 23 Eri, nan ehuehu mwomwohdiso ira ahpw pilada me mah kan pwe re en wia sounkaweidparail; oh ni kapakap oh kaisihsol ira ahpw kasarawihirailla ong Kaun-o me re kin koapworopworki.   
\p
\v 24 Eri, mwurin ara kakahnseli sapwen Pisidia, ira ahpw kohdo Pampilia.  
\v 25 Ira eri kalohki mahseno nan Perka oh douluhllahng Atalia,  
\v 26 oh sang wasao ira ahpw serek pwuralahng Andiok, wasa me tohn mwomwohdiso kasarawih ira ong kalahngan en Koht oh kasapwiliradahng doadoahk me ira kanekelahro.   
\p
\v 27 Ni ara lellahng nan Andiok, ira ahpw kapokonepene tohn mwomwohdiso kan oh padahkihong irail mehkoaros me ira wiadahr sang ni roson en Koht, oh duwen eh ketin ritingadahng mehn liki kan elen pwoson.  
\v 28 Ira ahpw koukousoan rehn me pwosonlahr akan ahnsou reirei.   
\c 15  
\s1 Wiekupwur nan Serusalem  
\p
\v 1 Mie ohl ekei me kohsang Sudia kolahng Andiok oh tapihada padapadahk ong me pwoson akan, ndinda, “Kumwail sohte kak komourla ma kumwail sohte sirkumsaisla nin duwen me Kosonned en Moses ketihtihki.” \x - \xo 15.1 \xt Lip. 12.3.\x*  
\v 2 Pohl oh Parnapas ahpw wia akamai kehlail ong irail, kahrehda re koasoanehdi me Pohl oh Parnapas oh ekei sang Andiok en kohla Serusalem oh tuhkiong wahnpoaron ko oh me mah kan duwen ire wet.   
\p
\v 3 Tohn mwomwohdiso eri kadarirailla, oh ni arail kotehla Penisia oh Sameria re ahpw lohkiseli duwen mehn liki kan ar wekiongehr Koht. Eri, rohng pwoatet ahpw kahrehiong me pwoson akan peren laud.  
\v 4 Ni arail lellahng Serusalem, tohn mwomwohdiso wasao oh pil wahnpoaron akan oh me mah kan ahpw kasamwo irail. Re ahpw koasoiaiong irail mehkoaros me Koht ketin wiahiongirailehr.  
\v 5 A ekei kisehn pwihnen Parisi me pwosonlahr ahpw uhda oh nda, “Uhdahn me pwung irail en sirkumsaisla oh padahkihong irail en peikiong Kosonned en Moses.”   
\p
\v 6 Eri, wahnpoaron ako oh me mah ko ahpw pokonpene pwe re en wie kupwurki ire wet.  
\v 7 Mwurin ar akahkpwungpene ahnsou reirei, Piter ahpw uhda oh nda, “Riei ko, kumwail ese me mahso Koht ketin piliehda sang nanpwungamwail pwe I en kalohki Rongamwahu ong irail mehn liki kan, pwe irail en kak rong oh kamehlele. \x - \xo 15.7 \xt Wie. 10.1-43.\x*  
\v 8 Eri, Koht me ketin mwahngih mohngiong en aramas, ahpw ketin kupwurehda en pil ketikihong mehn liki kan Ngehn Sarawi, nin duwen eh ketikihongkitailehr. \x - \xo 15.8 \xt Wie. 10.44; Wie. 2.4.\x*  
\v 9 Oh e sohte ketin wiahki me mie mehkot me wekpeseng nanpwungen irail oh kitail; e ketin mahkikihong irail diparail kan pwehki ar pwoson.  
\v 10 Eri, dahme kumwail kasongosongehki Koht ahnsou wet, ni amwail pwilikihdiong pohn pwopwen me pwosonlahr kan wisik ehu me samatail kahlap ako de pein kitail sohte kak wahda?  
\v 11 Eri soh, kitail pil kamehlele oh mourkihla kalahngan en Kaun Sises duwehte mehn liki kan.”   
\p
\v 12 A pokono pwon ahpw nennenla ni ar rongorong en Parnapas oh Pohl ara koasoiahda manaman kapwuriamwei kan koaros me ira wiahkidahr roson en Koht nanpwungen mehn liki kan.  
\v 13 Ni ara kanekehla ara koasoi, Seims ahpw koasoia, “Riei ko, kumwail rong ie!  
\v 14 Saimon ahpwtehn kawehwehda duwen Koht eh ketin kasalehda eh kupwurehla mehn liki kan mahs ni eh ketikihsang nanpwungarail aramas ekei pwe re en wiahla sapwellime.  
\v 15 Mahsen en soukohp ako inenen pwungiong mehlel met. Pwehki ih duwen me Pwuhk Sarawi mahsanih:   
\q1
\v 16 ‘Kaun-o ketin mahsanih, mwurin mepwukat I pahn pil sapahldo,  
\q2 oh onehda sapahl wehin Depit.  
\q1 I pahn onehda sapahl me rengkpesengehr kan,  
\q2 oh pwurehng kakehlahda. \x - \xo 15.16 \xt Eimw. 9.11-12 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Eri, aramas teikan koaros pahn pil rapahki Kaun-o,  
\q2 mehn liki koaros me I malipe pwe I en sapwellimanikihla.   
\q1
\v 18 Eri, iei met me Kaun-o ketin mahsaniher, me e ketin kasaledahr mahsie.’”   
\p
\v 19 Eri, Seims pil usehla koasoia, “I lemeleme me mwahu kitail dehr katautauwih mehn liki kan me pwoson Koht.  
\v 20 Ahpw kitail en ntingkiwohng irail re en dehr tungoale kisin mwenge kan me samin ong kaudok pwehki eh meirongalahr ong dikedik en eni kan; re en pil liksang nenek; oh re en dehr tungoale mahn mwopwula, de nta. \x - \xo 15.20 \xt Eks. 34.15-17; b Lip. 18.6-23; c Lip. 17.10-16.\x*  
\v 21 Pwe Kosonned en Moses kin wie wadawad ahnsou reirei nan en mehn Suhs akan arail sinakoke kan ni rahnen Sapad koaros. Oh sapwellime mahsen pil lolohkseli nan kahnimw kan koaros.”   
\s1 Kisinlikou ong mehn Liki me Pwoson akan  
\p
\v 22 Eri, wahnpoaron ako oh me mah ko, iangahki tohn mwomwohdiso kan koaros, re ahpw pwungkihda re en pilada ekei ohl sang nanpwungarail pwe re en kadariraillahng Andiok pwe re en iang Pohl oh Parnapas. Irail eri pilada Sudas, me pil adaneki Parsapas, oh Sailas. Ohl riemenet me keniken mehlel rehn me pwoson akan.  
\v 23 Eri, iet audepen kisinlikou me pekederlahro:  
\pi1 “Iet kiht riamwail kan, wahnpoaron oh me mah kan, se kadarowohng kumwail at rahnmwahu, ong kumwail riat koaros me ipwidi wia mehn liki mahso, nan Andiok oh Siria oh Silisia.  
\v 24 Se pil rongehr me mie ekei ohl sang nanpwungat me kowehr oh kapwunodehda oh kapingkinkumwailda soahng kan me irail koasoia. Eri, mehlel me irail pwukat kaidehn wiliapat re ahpw wia met.  
\v 25 Eri met, kiht koaros tuhpenehr oh pwungkidahr me se pahn pilada ekei meninkeder oh kadarowohng kumwail. Irail pwukat pahn iangewei kompoakepatail Parnapas oh Pohl,  
\v 26 me tounmeteikilahr ara mour nan sapwellimen Kaun Sises Krais doadoahk.  
\v 27 Eri, se pil kadarowei Sudas oh Sailas pwe ira en pein koasoiaiong kumwail soahng kan me se ntingkiwohng kumwail.  
\v 28 Pwe Ngehn Sarawi oh kiht pwungkipenehr me se sohte pahn katautauwihkin kumwail mehkot likin soangen kosonned pwukat me konehng:  
\v 29 kumwail dehr tungoale mwenge kan me meirongalahr ong dikedik en eni kan; dehr tungoale nta; dehr tungoale mahn mwopwula; oh kumwail en pil liksang nenek. Kumwail pahn pweida ma kumwail pahn kapwaiada soahng pwukat. Rahn kaselel ong kumwail.”   
\p
\v 30 Meninkeder pwukat eri pekederlahr Andiok, wasa me re kapokonepene me pwoson ako koaros oh kihong irail kisinlikowo. \fig |alt="HK-24B Andiok en Siria" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 15.30" \fig*  
\v 31 Ni en aramas ako ar wadekehr kisinlikowo, re ahpw perenkihda kowahlap mahsen en peneu kan.  
\v 32 Sudas oh Sailas, ira soukohp riemen; ira eri koasoakoasoiong me pwoson akan ahnsou reirei, penepeneu oh kangkakehlaka irail.  
\v 33 Mwurin ara mihmihki wasao ahnsou ehu, me pwoson ako eri kadarirahla ni popohl. Ira eri pwuralahng rehn me kadarirahla ko.  
\v 34 [Sailas ahpw medemedewe en kousoanla wasao.]   
\p
\v 35 Pohl oh Parnapas ahpw mihmihki Andiok ahnsou ehu. Ira iang me pwoson tohto me padapadahk oh lohlohkiseli mahsen en Kaun-o.   
\s1 Pohl oh Parnapas Tohrohrpeseng  
\p
\v 36 Kedekedeo, Pohl ahpw ndaiong Parnapas, “Me mwahuwong kita en pil pwurala oh tuhwong me pwoson akan nan kahnimw kan me kita lohkiseli mahsen en Kaun-o ie, pwe kita en ese irarail.”  
\v 37 Parnapas ahpw anahne Sohn Mark en iangirahda,  
\v 38 ahpw Pohl sohte pwungki, pwehki eh sohte iang ira kanekehla ara doadoahk, ahpw pwurasang ira oh keseirahla Pampilia. \x - \xo 15.38 \xt Wie. 13.13.\x*  
\v 39 Pohl oh Parnapas eri akamaikihda nanpwungara, oh tohrohrpeseng. Parnapas ahpw kahrehda Mark oh mwesellahng Saiprus.  
\v 40 Pohl eri pilada Sailas oh mwesel; me pwoson kan eri mweidirahla ni kalahngan en Koht.  
\v 41 Pohl ahpw kotehla Siria oh Silisia, kangkakehlaka tohn mwomwohdiso kan.   
\c 16  
\s1 Timoty Iangada Pohl oh Sailas  
\p
\v 1 Pohl eri seiloaklahng Derpe oh Listra. Mie mwahnakapw emen me pwoson me koukousoan wasao, ede Timoty, me eh nohno mehn Suhs me pil pwoson, oh eh pahpa mehn Krihs.  
\v 2 Timoty pil keniken rehn me pwoson akan koaros en nan Listra oh Aikoniomw.  
\v 3 Pohl men Timoty en iang; eri, e ahpw sirkumsaisla. Pohl wiahier met pwehki eh ese me mehn Suhs koaros me koukousoan wasao wehwehki me en Timoty eh pahpa mehn Krihs.  
\v 4 Ni arail kotekote kahnimw kan, irail ahpw koasoiaiong me pwoson akan duwen kosonned akan me koasoandier sang rehn wahnpoaron ako oh me mah kan nan Serusalem; oh re padahkihong irail re en kapwaiada kosonned pwukat.  
\v 5 Eri, mwomwohdiso kan pil kehlaillahr nan pwoson oh towe kan wie tohtohla rahn koaros.   
\s1 Kaudiahl ehu me Pohl Kilangehr nan Troas  
\p
\v 6 Irail eri seiloak kotehla sapwen Prikia oh Kalesia pwehki Ngehn Sarawi eh sohte mweidohng irail en kawehwe mahseno nan sapwen Eisia.  
\v 7 Ni arail lellahng ni irepen Misia, re ahpw song en pedolong nan sapwen Pidinia, ahpw Ngenen Sises sohte ketin mweidohng irail.  
\v 8 Irail eri seiloak kotehla Misia oh kohdilahng Troas.  
\v 9 Pwohngo Pohl eri udiahl kaudiahl ehu, oh nan kaudiahlo, e kilangada ohlen Masedonia men kesikesihnen, oh wie ekehker, patopatohwan, “Kohdo Masedonia oh sewesei kiht!”  
\v 10 Mwurin en Pohl eh kilangada kaudiahlo, se ahpw onopada en mwesellahng Masedonia, pwe se ese me Koht me ketin malipei kiht se en kalohkiseli Rongamwahu ong aramas en wasao.   
\s1 Koluhlahn Lidia nan Pilipai  
\p
\v 11 Se ahpw iangada sohp pwoat oh mwesellahng Troas oh serek inenlahng Samodreis. Eri, pweidi songada, se ahpw douluhllahng Neapolis.  
\v 12 Sang wasao se ahpw sapallahng Pilipai, keieun kahnimw en Masedonia, kahnimw wet pil kisehn wehin Rom. Se ahpw koukousoanki nan kahnimwo erein rahn ekei. \fig |alt="HK-23B Pilipai" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 16.12" \fig*  
\v 13 Ni rahnen Sapad ehu se ahpw kohsang nan kahnimwo oh kohla ni keilen pillap pwoat, wasa me se lemehiong me wasahn kapakap en mehn Suhs akan kin mi ie. Se ahpw mwohndi oh koasoakoasoiong lih ekei me pokopokon wasao.  
\v 14 Emen sang nanpwungen lih ako me wie rongorong kiht, iei Lidia, mehn Daiadaira, me kin netiki likou pohn ntahnmwel. Ih emen lih me kin kaudok ong Koht, oh Kaun-o ketin ritingada eh mohngiong pwe en rong kanahieng dahme Pohl koasoakoasoia.  
\v 15 Liho, oh pil tohn imwe kan, ahpw papidaisla. E ahpw lukei kiht oh koasoia, “Kumwail kohdo oh kousoan nan imweiet, ma kumwail kamehlele me ei pwoson me uhdahn mehlel.” Eri, e ahpw koangngoangehkin kiht se en kohla.   
\s1 Nan Imweteng en Pilipai  
\p
\v 16 Rahn ehu ni at kohkolahng wasahn kapakap, se ahpw tuhwong lidu serepein men me ngehn saut tiadahr powe, me kahrehiong en kasawih duwen audepen rahn akan me kohkohdo. E kin alehki mwohni laud oh kihong eh soumas akan ni eh kin koasoia dahme pahn wiawi.  
\v 17 E ahpw ideidawehn Pohl oh kiht, oh weriwerki, “Ohl pwukat ladun Koht, Wasa Lapalahpie! Irail kin kasalehiong kumwail duwen ahl en komour!”  
\v 18 Serepein menet wiewiaier met erein rahn tohto; Pohl ahpw lingeringerkihda oh sohpeidohng oh ndaiong ngehn sauto, “Ni mwaren Sises Krais I padahkihong uhk ke en pedoisang rehn serepein menen!” Ni ahnsowohte ngehno ahpw pedoisang rehn serepeino.  
\v 19 Ni ahnsou me irail kan me naineki serepein menet esedahr me arail ahnsou mwahu en ale mwohni solahr mie, re ahpw koledi Pohl oh Sailas oh wurahdekihiralahng rehn me lapalap akan nan arail wasahn kadeik.  
\v 20 Irail eri kahreirahla mwohn me lapalap en Rom akan oh nda, “Ohl riemenet mehn Suhs kei, oh ira wiadahr me suwed nan atail kahnimw wet.  
\v 21 Ira kin padapadahngki tiahk kan me kin uhwong atail kosonned; kitail mehn Rom, eri, kitail sohte kak en idawehn tiahk pwukat.”  
\v 22 Pokono ahpw iang uhwong Pohl oh Sailas.  
\p Lapalap ako eri tehrasang en Pohl oh Sailas ara likou kan oh koasoanehdi pwe ira en wowoki.  
\v 23 Mwurin ara aleier kamakam laud, ira ahpw lekdekiong nan imweteng, oh kosonned ahpw kohieng silepeo pwe ira en loakidi teng.  
\v 24 Ni en silepeo eh aleier kosonned wet, e ahpw keseirahlong nan pere me keieu mi loale oh salihediong nehra ko nin tuhke toutou kei.   
\p
\v 25 Eri, nin lukepen pwong, Pohl oh Sailas ahpw kapakap oh kokoulki koul kei ong Koht, oh ekei irail tohnimwetengo ahpw wie rongorong.  
\v 26 Ni ahnsowohte rerrer en sahpw ehu ahpw wiawi me itikada imwetengo oh lelohng poahsoane kan. Ni ahnsowohte wenihmw kan koaros ritida, oh selmete kan ahpw pwupwudihsang rehn irail koaros me sensel kan.  
\v 27 Silepeo ahpw pirida, oh ni eh kilangada me wenihmw kan en imwetengo ritpesengier, e kihkihong me irail tangehrdoaui. Ih eri usada nah kedlahs, pwe en pein kemehkihla pein ih.  
\v 28 Pohl ahpw likwerlahng, nda, “Ke dehpa wiahiong uhk mehkot! Pwe kiht koaros mihmihte met!”   
\p
\v 29 Silepeo ahpw likwerla pwe ehu lamp en wisikdo; e ahpw tangla oh kelehpwikihdi mwohn Pohl oh Sailas wie rerrer.  
\v 30 Eri, e ahpw kahreirahla liki oh idek rehra, “Maing ko, dahme I pahn wia pwe I en kak mourla?”   
\p
\v 31 Ira ahpw sapengki, “Pwoson Kaun Sises, a kowe oh omw peneinei koaros pahn mourla.”  
\v 32 Ira eri padahkihong mahsen en Kaun-o, oh pil ong irail koaros me mihmi nan imwe.  
\v 33 Nipwongohte silepen imwetengo ahpw kahreirahda oh widenda ara ohla ko. Eri, ih oh eh peneinei koaros ahpw papidaisla.  
\v 34 E ahpw kahredalahng Pohl oh Sailas nan imweo oh kamwenge ira. Ih oh eh peneinei ahpw perenda kowahlap, pwehki arail pwosonlahr Koht.   
\p
\v 35 Mandahn rahno me lapalap en Rom akan ahpw kadaralahng kaunen pilismen kan, pakair wet, “Kumwail kasaladekala ohl akan.”   
\p
\v 36 Eri, silepeo ahpw ndaiong Pohl, “Irail lapalap akan pakairkidohr me kowe oh Sailas en lapwada. Eri, kumwa mwesel oh kohkohwei ni popohl.”   
\p
\v 37 Pohl ahpw ndaiong kaunen pilismen kan, “Se sohte mwahn dipikihda dihp ehu; a re ahpw wokih kiht mwohn pokon ehu ni at wia towe mehlel en wehin Rom. Irail eri salihkitedi. Eri, ia duwe, met irail mwahuki kadarkitala ni rir? Met sohte kak wiawi! Irail lapalap akan en Rom en pein kohdo oh kahreikitasang wasaht.”   
\p
\v 38 Kaunen pilismen kan eri kairehki me lapalap akan en Rom duwen koasoi pwukat; oh ni arail rongada me Pohl oh Sailas wia towe mehlel en wehin Rom, re ahpw masepwehkada.  
\v 39 Irail eri kohla oh peki mahk rehra; irail ahpw kahreirahsang nan imwetengo oh peki ira en mweselsang nan kahnimwo.  
\v 40 Pohl oh Sailas eri mweselsang nan imwetengo oh kohla nan imwen Lidia, wasa ira tuhwong ie me pwoson akan oh pwurehng kakehlaka irail; oh mwuri ira ahpw mwesel kohkohla.   
\c 17  
\s1 Nan Desalonika  
\p
\v 1 Pohl oh Sailas eri seiloakla oh kotehla Ampipolis oh Apolonia, oh lel Desalonika, wasa me en mehn Suhs kan sinakoke mi ie. \fig |alt="HK-25D Desalonika" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 17.1" \fig*  
\v 2 Eri, nin duwen me Pohl kin kalap wia; e ahpw kohla ni sinakokeo. Erein rahnen Sapad siluh me irail mihmihki wasao Pohl kin koasoiaiong aramas akan duwen Pwuhk Sarawi.  
\v 3 E kawehwehiong irail oh kadekadehde sang nan Pwuhk Sarawi me Mesaia uhdahn pahn lokolok oh pahn iasada sang mehla. Pohl pil nda, “Sises menet, me I kasalehiong kumwail, iei ih Mesaia.”  
\v 4 Ekei irail ahpw kamehlele oh iangala Pohl oh Sailas; pil duwehte lapalahn pwihnen mehn Krihs kei me kin kaudokiong Koht, iangahki lih soumas tohto.   
\p
\v 5 Ahpw irail mehn Suhs akan inenen peirinkihda oh kapokonepene ohl ekei me kin kohkohseli mwahl pohn ahl akan oh wiahkihda pwihnen moromor ehu. Irail eri kamwoarongehda tohn nan kahnimwo pwon, oh kohla ni imwen Seison, raparapahki Pohl oh Sailas pwe re en kahreirahdo rehn aramas akan.  
\v 6 Ahpw ni arail sohte diarirahda, re ahpw wurahdekiei Seison oh pil ekei me pwoson, wurahdekilahng rehn me lapalap en kahnimwo. Re ahpw weriwerki, “Ohl akat kapingadahr wasa koaros! Eri met, ira pil kodohr nan atail kahnimw wet;  
\v 7 oh Seison ahpw karukihirahla nan imwe. Irail koaros kin kaukauwe en Sihsar kosonned akan, ni arail kin koasoakoasoia me pil mie emen nanmwarki, me adaneki Sises.”  
\v 8 Eri, ni arail rong lokaia pwukat, pokono, oh pil me lapalap akan, ahpw mwoarongada mehlel.  
\v 9 Me lapalap akan ahpw idingki Seison oh pil me pwoson teikan re en pwain uwen pweipwei me konehng irail en kak lapwkihda; re ahpw kadarirailla.   
\s1 Nan Peria  
\p
\v 10 Ni eh soutikpenehr, irail me pwoson akan mwadangete kadarala Pohl oh Sailas nan Peria. Ni ara lel wasao, ira ahpw kohla nan sinakoke en mehn Suhs akan.  
\v 11 Aramas en wasao men rong ira sang aramas en Desalonika. Irail ngoangki mehlel rong mahseno, oh rahn koaros irail kin onopki Pwuhk Sarawi pwe re en kadehde ma en Pohl koasoi me mehlel de soh.  
\v 12 Eri, me tohto ahpw pwosonla, oh lih soumas en Krihs tohto, oh pil ohlen Krihs tohtohie, me pil pwosonla.  
\v 13 Ahpw ni ahnsou me mehn Suhs en Desalonika kan rongada me Pohl pil kin lohkiseli mahsen en Koht nan Peria, re ahpw kohdo wasao oh tapihada kapingada oh kamwoarongehda aramas akan.  
\v 14 Me pwoson akan eri pitipit kadarala Pohl ni oaroahr en sahpwo, ahpw Sailas oh Timoty mihmihte nan Peria.  
\v 15 Ohl ako me likidala Pohl iangala lel Adens. Irail eri pwuralahng Peria, wa kehkehlik sang Pohl me dene Sailas oh Timoty en tuhwong ih ni ahnsou ehu me kak.   
\s1 Nan Adens  
\p
\v 16 Ni en Pohl eh awiawih Sailas oh Timoty nan Adens, e inenen nsensuwedkihla mehlel eh kilangada sansal en koht likamw tohto nan kahnimwo.  
\v 17 Eri, nan sinakokeo e ahpw akupwung ong mehn Suhs akan oh mehn liki kan me kin kaudokiong Koht. Oh pil nan wasahn kapokon akan rahn koaros, e kin akupwung ong aramas akan me kin kohdo wasao.  
\v 18 Pwihnen Epikurus oh pil sounpadahk en Sdohik kei pil kin akupwung ong Pohl. Ekei nda, “Dahme lampwon pohnmwahso menet men koasoia?”  
\p Pil ekei kin nda, “Likamwete e koasoakoasoia duwen ekei koht tohrohr.” Irail nda met pwehki en Pohl eh padapadahkihong aramas akan duwen Sises oh pil duwen iasada.\f d \fr 17.18 \fk SISES OH IASADA: \ft Lepin mahsen wet “iasada” ni mahsen en Krihs pil kak wehwehki mwaren koht lih emen.\f*  
\v 19 Irail eri kahrelahng Pohl Areopakus oh walahng ni wiekupwur en wiliepen tohn kahnimwo, oh nda, “Se men ese duwen padahk kapw kan me ke kin padahkihong aramas akan,  
\v 20 pwehki me kapwonopwon ong kiht, oh se men ese da wehwehn padahk pwukat.”  
\v 21 (Pwehki aramas koaros en Adens, oh tohn wehi teikan me koukousoan wasao, re kin mwahuki kasolapahkihla ar ahnsou koasoakoasoia oh rongorong soahng kapw akan.) \fig |alt="HK-21D Areopakus" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 17.21" \fig*   
\p
\v 22 Pohl eri uhda mwohn wiliepe kan en kahnimwo oh nda, “Ohl akan en Adens! I kilangehr me kumwail inenen poadidi ni soangen lamalam koaros.  
\v 23 Pwehki ni ei kohkohseli nan amwail kahnimw wet, oh kilikilang wasa kan me kumwail kin kaudok ie, I pil diarada pei sarawi ehu me nting pwukat mi powe, ‘Ong Koht emen me Sohte Me Ese.’ Eri, kumwail sohte kin ese duwen me kumwail kin kaudokiong, ahpw iei ih me I pahn kasalehiong kumwail met. \x - \xo 17.23 \xt Kupw. 13.1.\x*  
\v 24 Koht me ketin kapikada sampah oh audepe kan koaros, ih me Kaunepen lahng oh sampah, oh e sohte kin ketiket nan imwen kaudok me aramas kin wiahda. \x - \xo 17.24 \xt 1 Nan. 8.27; Ais. 42.5; Wie. 8.47.\x*  
\v 25 Oh e pil sohte anahne soahng kan me aramas kak kihda ni arail pahn kin doadoahk ong ih, pwehki iei ih me pahn ketikihong mour oh esingek oh soahng teikan ong aramas akan koaros. \x - \xo 17.25 \xt 2 Mak. 14.35.\x*  
\v 26 E ketin wiahda kadaudok koaros sang rehn ohltehmen, oh ketikihong irail en koukousoan pohn sampah pwon. Pein ih me koasoanedier mwohn mehkoaros pwungen ahnsou kan oh irair en wasa kan me re pahn koukousoan ie. \x - \xo 17.26 \xt 2 Mak. 7.23.\x*  
\v 27 E ketin wiadahr met pwe re en rapahki ih, oh mwein re pahn diar ni ar pahn rapahki. Ahpw Koht sohte dohsang emenemen kitail. \x - \xo 17.27 \xt Kupw. 13.6-9.\x*  
\v 28 Pwe  
\q1 ‘Kitail kin momourki ih, oh mwekimwekidki ih, oh pil mihmi pwehki ih.’  
\m Nin duwen ekei amwail sounwie koul kan kin nda,  
\q1 ‘Pwe kitail pil sapwellime seri.’   
\m
\v 29 Eri, nin duwen atail wiahier sapwellime seri, kitail sohte pahn kihkihong me mwomwen Koht pahn ehu soahng duwehte mwomwen kohl de silper de takai me perperda nin duwen koahiek en aramas.  
\v 30 Koht ketin melielahr ahnsou me aramas akan kin sehse ih mahso, ahpw met e ketin kupwurki aramas koaros wasa koaros en weksang arail suwed akan.  
\v 31 Pwe e ketin koasoanedier rahn ehu me e pahn ketin kadeingkihda sampah pwon pwuhng, sang rehn ohl emen me e ketin pilada. E ketikihda kadehdepen met ong emenemen ni eh ketin kaiasadahr ohlo sang mehla!”   
\p
\v 32 Ni ahnsou me irail rong en Pohl eh koasoakoasoia duwen iasada sang mehla, ekei irail ahpw kouruhrki, a ekei nda, “Se pil men pwurehng rong uhk ni omw pahn pil pwurehng koasoia met.”  
\v 33 Eri, Pohl ahpw mweselsang mihtingo.  
\v 34 Ekei ahpw kamehlele oh pwosonla; nanpwungarail me pwosonlahr akan, iei emen Daionisius, iei ih kisehn pwihnen Areopakus, oh lih emen ede Damaris, oh pil me kei.   
\c 18  
\s1 Nan Korint  
\p
\v 1 Mwurin mepwukat Pohl eri mweselsang Adens oh kolahng Korint.  
\v 2 Wasao e ahpw tuhwong mehn Suhs emen me adaneki Akwila, me ipwidier nan Pondus, me ahpwtehn kohdo sang Itali iangahki eh pwoud Persila, pwehki Sihsar Klaudius eh ketin koasoanehdi me mehn Suhs koaros en pekeussang nan Rom. Pohl eri kohla pwe en tuhwong ira,  
\v 3 oh kousoan rehra, oh iang ira doadoahk, pwehki e pil duwehte ira me kin momourki wiahda ihmw likou kan.  
\v 4 E kin koasoakoasoiong mehn Suhs oh mehn Krihs kan nan sinakoke kan ni rahnen Sapad koaros, oh kin songosong en kawekirailla.   
\p
\v 5 Ni en Sailas oh Timoty ara leledo sang Masedonia, Pohl ahpw mweidohng eh ahnsou koaros ong kalohkiseli mahseno, kadekadehdehiong mehn Suhs akan me Sises iei Mesaia.  
\v 6 Eri, ni arail pelianda oh ndahki lokaia suwed kei, e ahpw sapeng irail ni eh sipedasang pwelen eh likou kan, kilel en eh pahn piseksang irail, oh ndaiong irail, “Ma kumwail pahn salongala, eri, pein kumwail me uhdahn pahn pwukoahki; I sohte pahn pwukoahki! Sang met kohla I pahn kolahng rehn mehn liki kan.”  
\v 7 Pohl eri mweselsang rehrail oh kohla kousoanla nan imwen mehn liki men me adaneki Taitus Sustus, me kin pwongih Koht. Imwen ohl menet mihte limwahn sinakoke en mehn Suhs akan.  
\v 8 Krispus, soumas en sinakokeo, ahpw pwosonla Kaun-o, iangahki eh peneinei koaros. Oh pil me tohtohie nan Korint me rong mahseno, re ahpw pil pwosonla oh papidaisla.   
\p
\v 9 Pwohngpwong Pohl ahpw kilang kaudiahl ehu, oh nan kaudiahl wet Kaun-o ketin mahsanihong, “Pohl, ke dehr masak mehkot, nantihongete omw padapadahk oh dehr peikasal,  
\v 10 pwe I pahn iang uhk. Sohte emen me pahn kak wiahiong uhk mehkot, pwe nei aramas me tohto nan kahnimw wet.”  
\v 11 Pohl eri koukousoanki wasao erein pahr ehu elep, padapadahkihong aramas akan duwen mahsen en Koht.   
\p
\v 12 Eri, ni Kalio eh pilipilda en wia kepinahn Akaia, mehn Suhs akan ahpw pokonpene oh koledi Pohl oh kahrelahng nan imwen kopwung.  
\v 13 Re ahpw nda, “Ohl menet kin songosong en panawiheki aramas akan en kaudok ong Koht ni mwohmw ehu me kin uhwong kosonned!”   
\p
\v 14 Pohl ahpwtehn pahn koasoi, a Kalio mahsanihong mehn Suhs ako, “Ma mehkotet me wiawiher iei sapwung laud ehu, eri, e pahn konehng I en kanengamahiong oh rongorong kumwail mehn Suhs kan.  
\v 15 Ahpw pwehki eh pidada lepin mahsen kan oh ahd akan oh pein amwail kosonned, eri, pein kumwail en koasoanehdi. Pwe I sohte pahn wia sounkopwungpen soahng pwukat!”  
\v 16 E ahpw kausirailieisang nan imwen kopwungo.  
\v 17 Irail eri koledi Sostenihs, soumas en sinakokeo, oh wokih mwohn imwen kopwungo. Eri, Kalio sohte mwahn katapanki mwekid wet.   
\s1 Pwuralahng Andiok en Siria  
\p
\v 18 Pohl eri mihmihte Korint rehn me pwoson akan rahn tohto, oh e ahpw sereklahng Siria iangahki Persila oh Akwila. Mwohn e pahn sereksang Senkria e ahpw koakoahsang pitenmoange pwehki inou ehu me e wiadahr. \f e \fr 18.18 \fk INOU EHU ME E WIADAHR: \ft Met tiahk en mehn Suhs en koakoahsang pitenmoange pwe en kasalehda me e kapwaiada eh inowo.\f* \x - \xo 18.18 \xt Nempe 6.18.\x*  
\v 19 Irail eri lel nan Episos, wasa me Pohl pwilikihdi Persila oh Akwila ie. E ahpw pedolong nan sinakoke en mehn Suhs kan oh koasoakoasoiong irail.  
\v 20 Re ahpw peki en mihmihki rehrail ahnsou reirei, ahpw e sohte pwungki.  
\v 21 Eri, ni eh pahn mwesel e ahpw ndaiong irail, “Ma iei duwen kupwur en Koht, I pahn pwurodohng rehmwail.” E ahpw sereksang Episos.   
\p
\v 22 Ni eh lelehr Sesaria e ahpw douluhllahng Serusalem oh rahnmwahwih tohn mwomwohdiso; eri, e ahpw douluhllahng Andiok.  
\v 23 Eri, mwurin eh mihmihkier wasao ahnsou kis, e ahpw mwesel. Ih eri kotehla sapwen Kalesia oh Prikia, kakehlakala irail koaros me pwoson akan.   
\s1 Apolos nan Episos oh Korint  
\p
\v 24 Mehn Suhs emen ede Apolos, me ipwidier nan Aleksandria, ahpw kohdo Episos. Ih ohl emen me kadek kapahrek, oh e pil loalokongki Pwuhk Sarawi.  
\v 25 E sukuhlkiher duwen Ahl en Kaun-o; eri, e kin pwerisek koasoia oh padahkiwei pwungen mour en Sises ni peren. Ahpw e wehwehkihte papidais en Sohn.  
\v 26 Apolos ahpw tapihada eimah padapadahk nan sinakoke en mehn Suhs kan. Ni ahnsou me Persila oh Akwila rongada eh padahk kan, ira ahpw kahrelahng nan imwara oh kawehwehiong ni oaritik duwen pwungen Ahl en Koht.  
\v 27 Apolos eri lemehda en kolahng Akaia. Eri, me pwoson kan me mi Episos ahpw sewese ni arail ntinglahng me pwoson kan nan Akaia, koangngoangehkin irail en kasamwo Apolos wasao. Ni ahnsou me e lel wasao e ahpw wiahda sawas laud ehu ong irail ako me pwosonlahr pwehki kalahngan en Koht.  
\v 28 Pwehki eh akamai kehlail, e powehdi mehn Suhs akan nan akupwung sansal akan, kadekadehde sang nan Pwuhk Sarawi me Sises, iei Mesaia.   
\c 19  
\s1 Pohl nan Episos  
\p
\v 1 Eri, ni Apolos eh mihmihte Korint, Pohl ahpw wia eh seiloak nan werengen wehio oh lellahng nan Episos. E ahpw diarada ekei tohnpadahk wasao,  
\v 2 oh idek rehrail, “Ia duwe, kumwail aleier Ngehn Sarawi ni ahnsou me kumwail pwosonlahr?”  
\p Re ahpw sapengki, “Se saikinte mwahn rong ma mie Ngehn Sarawi.”   
\p
\v 3 Pohl eri kalelapak, “A soangen papidais da me kumwail ale?”  
\p Re ahpw sapengki, “Papidais en Sohn.”   
\p
\v 4 Pohl eri nda, “Papidais en Sohn ong irail kante me pahn koluhla; oh Sohn pil padahkihong aramas en Israel kan me irail uhdahn pahn pwoson mehmen me pahn kohdo mwuri, met wehwehki Sises.” \x - \xo 19.4 \xt Mad. 3.11; Mark 1.4, 7-8; Luk 3.4, 16; Sohn 1.26-27.\x*   
\p
\v 5 Ni arail rong padahk wet, re ahpw papidaisla ni mwaren Kaun Sises.  
\v 6 Pohl eri pwil peh kan pohrail, Ngehn Sarawi eri ketido pohrail; irail ahpw lokaiahki soangen lokaia tohrohr kei oh pil koasoia mahsen en Koht.  
\v 7 Irail koaros ohl ehk riemen.   
\p
\v 8 Pohl ahpw kohla nan sinakoke en mehn Suhs akan oh erein sounpwong siluh e pil eimah padapadahk ong aramas akan wasao, akupwung ong irail oh songosong koangngoangehkin irail en kamehlele duwen Wehin Koht.  
\v 9 Ahpw ekei irail me inenen keptakai oh sohte men pwoson; re ahpw kin kauwe duwen Ahl en Kaun-o mwohn pokono koaros. Pohl eri mweselsang irail oh wahda tohnpadahk ko. Eri, rahn koaros e kin padapadahk nan imwen kapahrek en Tiranus.  
\v 10 Met wiawihkiher erein sounpar riau. Ihme kahrehda aramas koaros me kousoan nan sapwen Eisia, mehn Suhs oh pil mehn liki kan, rongada mahsen en Kaun-o.   
\s1 Nein Skepa Pwutak kan  
\p
\v 11 Eri, Pohl ahpw kin wiahda manaman kapwuriamwei tohrohr kei sang ni roson en Koht.  
\v 12 Pil limwinpwudo oh likoun perehre kan me e kin doadoahngki, ni ar kin wisiklahng rehn me soumwahu kan, arail soumwahu kan kin mwahukihla, oh ngehn saut akan pil kin pedoisang rehrail.  
\v 13 Eri, ekei mehn Suhs akan me kin seiseiloakseli oh kin kausasang ngehn saut akan, re pil song en doadoahngki mwaren Kaun Sises nin soangen doadoahk wet. Irail eri ndaiong ngehn saut akan, “Ke uhdahn pahn pedoikihsang ni mwaren Sises me Pohl kin padapadahngki.”  
\v 14 Pirien isimen, nein Samworo Lapalap en mehn Suhs emen, me ede Skepa, iei irail me kin wia doadoahk wet.   
\p
\v 15 Ahpw ngehn sauto ndaiong irail, “I ese Sises, oh I pil ese Pohl; a ihs kumwail?”   
\p
\v 16 Eri, ohl me ngehn sauto tiadahr powe inenen pelianda irail oh poweiraildi. Irail koaros eri ohla oh tangasang ni imwen ohlo, oh arail likou kan pil teipeseng.  
\v 17 Eri, mehn Suhs koaros, oh pil mehn liki kan, me kousoan Episos, re ahpw rongada duwen met. Irail koaros ahpw masakada; oh koaros inenen waunekihla mehlel mwaren Kaun Sises.  
\v 18 Me tohto sang me pwosonlahr akan pwarodo, wehkada ni sansal oh kasalehda dahme irail wiahda.  
\v 19 Pil me tohto sang irail kan me kin wunahni re kihpene neirail pwuhk kan oh isikala mwohn masarail koaros. Irail ahpw kapatapene uwen pweinen pwuhk me isihslahr ako; eri, e pahrekiong pweinen tohndoadoahk men ong rahn limanen.  
\v 20 Ni soangen manaman wet mahsen en Kaun-o ahpw inenen kekeirda kehlail oh lolohkseli.   
\s1 Moromor nan Episos  
\p
\v 21 Mwurin mepwukat, Pohl ahpw koasoanehdi en seiloaklahng Masedonia oh Akaia oh douluhllahng Serusalem. E ahpw nda, “Mwurin ei pahn kohla wasao, I uhdahn pahn pil kilang Rom.”  
\v 22 E ahpw kadarala Timoty oh Erastus nan Masedonia, ira riemenet me kin sewesewese. Pohl eri mihmihki nan wehin Eisia erein ahnsou kis.   
\p
\v 23 Iei ahnsowo me pingiping laud ehu wiawi nan Episos pwehki Ahl en Kaun-o.  
\v 24 Mie sounsukmete men, me ede Demihtrius, me kin wiahkihda silper mwomwen imwen kaudok en koht lih Artemis, oh e kin netinetki. Eh pesineso ahpw kahrehda mwohni laud ong nah tohndoadoahk kan.  
\v 25 Eri, e ahpw ekerpene ienge ko iangahki koaros me kin iang wia soangen doadoahko oh ndaiong irail, “Ohl akan, kumwail ese me atail pai kin kohsang ni doadoahk wet.  
\v 26 Pein kumwail kak kilang oh rong dahme aramas menet Pohl kin wiewia. E kin koasoia me koht akan me kin wiawihkihda pehn aramas kaidehn mwahn koht ekei, oh e inenen pweida ni eh koangngoangehki aramas tohto met, nan Episos oh pil kereniong nan wehin Eisia pwon.  
\v 27 Eri, met me keper, ma atail doadoahk wet pahn adsuwedla. Kaidehn ihte met, ahpw pil inenen keper pwe imwen kaudok en koht lih Artemis pahn wiemwahlla oh pahn mwomwla—koht lih me aramas koaros kin pwongih nan Eisia oh pil nan sampah pwon!”   
\p
\v 28 Eri, ni pokono ar rong koasoi pwukat, irail inenen lingeringerda mehlel oh tapihada weriwer, ndinda, “Meid lapalap Artemis en Episos!”  
\v 29 Mwoarongo ahpw kohpeseng nan kahnimwo pwon. Pwihnen moromoro ahpw koledi Kaius oh Aristarkus, ira mehn Masedonia me iang Pohl seiseiloak, oh re tangahkiniralahng nan wasahn poudiahl mwadong ehu.  
\v 30 Pein Pohl men kohla mwohn pokono, ahpw me pwoson akan sohte mweidohng.  
\v 31 Pil ekei aramas lapalap en wasao me kompoakepahniki Pohl, re ahpw ileklahng oh peki en dehr kasalehda pein ih nan wasahn poudiahl mwadongo.  
\v 32 Ni ahnsowo tohn mihtingo inenen pingida, ekei aramas weriwerki ehu soahng, a ekei ehu soahng, pwehki me tohto nanpwungarail sohte mwahn ese dahme irail pokonkipene.  
\v 33 Ekei aramas koasoia me Aleksander me pwukoahki, pwehki mehn Suhs ko ar sikendahla en kohdahla mwohn pokono. Aleksander eri oaloallahng irail pwe en song kawehwehiong irail mehkot.  
\v 34 Ahpw ni ahnsou me re esehda me ih pil mehn Suhs men, irail koaros ahpw wiahkinteieu weriwerki erein awa riau, ndinda, “Meid lapalap Artemis en Episos!”   
\p
\v 35 Ni sounnting en kahnimwo eh kameleileidi pokono, e ahpw nda, “Ohlen Episos kan! Kumwail koaros ese me kahnimw en Episos wet, iei wasa me imwen kaudok en Artemis kin mi ie, oh iangahki takai sarawi me pwupwudihdo sang nanleng. \fig |alt="HK-31G Koht lih Artemis" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 19.35" \fig*  
\v 36 Sohte emen me kak kalikamwe soahng pwukat. Eri, kumwail meleilei oh dehr wia soahng ehu me sapwung.  
\v 37 Kumwail kahredohr ohl pwukat ni ara sohte pirapa imwen kaudok kan de nda soahng suwed ehu duwen atail koht liho.  
\v 38 Eri, ma Demihtrius oh nah tohndoadoahk kan men kedipa emen, eri, mie aramas lapalap oh pil rahnen kopwung, kadipadip kan kak wiawi wasao.  
\v 39 Ahpw ma mie mehkot me laudsang me kumwail anahne, met pahn kak koasoandi nan mihting en tohn wasaht.  
\v 40 Pwe mwurin me wiawiher rahnwet, e keper pwe kitail dehr dipkihda me kitail wiadahr moromor ehu. Sohte kahrepen pingiping wet, oh kitail sohte pahn kak koasoia ehu kahrepe mwahu ong met.”  
\v 41 Mwurin eh koasoia mepwukat, e ahpw kadarpeseng pokono.   
\c 20  
\s1 Mwesellahng Masedonia oh Akaia  
\p
\v 1 Pingiping lao meleileidier, Pohl ahpw ekerpene me pwoson kan, oh wiahiong irail koasoi en kakehlahda nan kapehdirail kan oh rahnmwahwihirailla. E ahpw mwesellahng Masedonia.  
\v 2 E kotehla sahpw akan oh koangngoangehki aramas akan padahk tohtohie. Mwuri, e ahpw kohdo Akaia,  
\v 3 oh koukousoanki wasao sounpwong siluh. E kaukaunop en sereklahng Siria, ahpw diarada me mehn Suhs ako men salihedi; ih eri koasoanehdi en pwuralahng Masedonia ahpw kolahng Siria.  
\v 4 Sopater, nein Pirus, mehn Peria, ahpw iangada, iangahki Aristarkus oh Sekundus, mehn Desalonika; Kaius mehn Derpe, Dikikus oh Tropimus sang wehin Eisia; oh pil iangahki Timoty.  
\v 5 Irail pwukat koaros ahpw tiengla oh awiawih kiht nan Troas.  
\v 6 Se sereksang Pilipai mwurin Sarawien Pilawa Sohte Doal Ihs; oh mwurin rahn limau se ahpw iangirailda nan Troas, wasa me se mihmihki erein wihk ehu.   
\s1 Kaimwiseklahn en Pohl eh Pwarek Troas  
\p
\v 7 Ni rahn keieu en wihko, se ahpw pokonpene pwehn pilitikihpeseng pilawa. Pohl ahpw koasoiong aramas akan, e koasoakoasoi lao lel ni lukepen pwong, pwehki eh pahn mweselsang irail mandahn rahno.  
\v 8 Lamp tohto mi nan perehn poweo, wasa se pokopokon ie.  
\v 9 Mwahnakapw emen me ede Eutikus wie mwomwohd ni wenihmwtok ehu; oh ni en Pohl eh wie koasoakoasoi, Eutikus ahpw men meirla oh meir kelikla, oh pwupwudihsang nan poasoake kesiluh pwupw nanpwel. Irail pwekada, e melahr.  
\v 10 Pohl eri kohdihla oh lukupoardiong powe oh pwoalehdi, ahpw nda, “Kumwail dehr nsensuwed, pwe e momourte.”  
\v 11 Ih eri pwuradahla poweo, pilitikihpeseng pilawao oh tungoale. Pohl ahpw koasoakoasoi ong irail ahnsou reirei, lao lel nimenseng. Eri, mwuhr, e ahpw mweselsang irail.  
\v 12 Irail ahpw kahrehla mwahnakapw menet ni eh mourdahr; irail eri nsenamwahula mehlel.   
\s1 Sang Troas ohng Mailihdus  
\p
\v 13 Se ahpw tienglahng nin sohpo oh sereklahng Assos, wasa se pahn ale Pohl ie. E ndaiong kiht se en wia met pwehki eh pahn sapallahng wasao.  
\v 14 Ni ahnsou me se tuhwong nan Assos, se iang Pohl douluhllahng Mitilihne.  
\v 15 Se mweselsang wasao oh lel Kios mandahn rahno. Mwurin rahn ehu se ahpw lel Samos, oh mwurin rahno se ahpw lel Mailihdus.  
\v 16 Pohl ahpw koasoanehdi en daulih Episos, pwe e sohte men kasohlapahla eh ahnsou nan wehin Eisia. E inenen karuwaruhki en lel Serusalem, ma e kak, mwohn rahnen Pendekos.   
\s1 En Pohl eh Kamwurimwuriong me Mah kan en Episos  
\p
\v 17 Pohl eri ileklahng me mah kan en mwomwohdisohn Episos sang Mailihdus, oh peki irail en tuhwong.  
\v 18 Ni ahnsou me re leledohng reh, e ahpw ndaiong irail, “Kumwail eseier duwen ei mihmi rehmwail, sang ni tepin rahn me I pwarodohng kumwail nan wehin Eisia.  
\v 19 Eri, nin duwen ladun Kaun-o men I kin wia ei doadoahk ni karakarahk oh sengiseng, pwehki ahnsou apwal akan me lelohng ie sang ni en mehn Suhs akan ar kin uhwong ie.  
\v 20 Kumwail ese me I sohte kin ekihsang kumwail mehkot me I dehdehki me pahn sewesei kumwail ni ei padahk oh panawih kumwail nan wasahn kapokon kan oh nan imwamwail kan.  
\v 21 I panawih mehn Suhs kan oh pil mehn liki kan, pwe irail en weksang diparail kan, oh wekidekiong Koht oh pil pwoson mwaren Kaun Sises.  
\v 22 Eri, met nin duwen ei peikiong Ngehn Sarawi, I pahn kolahng Serusalem, ahpw I sehse dahme pahn wiawihong ie wasao.  
\v 23 Ihte me I ese: nan kahnimw koaros me I kohla ie Ngehn Sarawi kin kasalehiong ie me selidi oh kahpwal kin awiawih ie.  
\v 24 I sohte katapaniki ei mour; ihte I men kapwaiada pweisei doadoahk me Kaun Sises ketikihong ie, me iei I en kalohkiseli Rongamwahu duwen kalahngan en Koht. \x - \xo 20.24 \xt 2 Tim. 4.7.\x*   
\p
\v 25 “I kalohkiseli nanpwungamwail koaros oh padapadahkihong kumwail duwen Wehin Koht. Eri met, I ese me sohte emen kumwail pahn kak pwurehng kilang ie.  
\v 26 Eri, I kehkehlingkihong kumwail rahnwet, pwe ma mehmen kumwail salongala, I sohte pahn pwukoahki,  
\v 27 pwehki I sohte ekihsang kumwail ei kasalehiong kumwail unsek en kupwur en Koht.  
\v 28 Eri, kumwail mwasamwasahn pein kumwail oh pil sihpw akan koaros me Ngehn Sarawi ketikihong kumwail en apwahpwalih. Kumwail en wia silepen mwomwohdisohn Koht, me e ketin sapwellimanikilahr pwehki ntahn sapwellime Iehros.  
\v 29 I ese me mwurin ei pahn mwesel kidien wel kan pahn kohdo nanpwungamwail oh re sohte pahn mweidohng pelin sihpwo en pitila.  
\v 30 Pil mie ekei aramas me pahn pwarada sang nanpwungamwail me pahn pitiheki me pwoson akan lokaia likamw, pwe re en idawehnirailla.  
\v 31 Eri, kumwail mwasamwasahn, oh tamataman me I sengisengkin kumwail nipwong nin rahn, ni ei padapadahki emenemen kumwail erein sounpar siluh.   
\p
\v 32 “Eri met, I likiong kumwail nin limen Koht oh kalahngan en sapwellime mahseno, iei ih me kak ketin kaukumwailda oh ketikihong kumwail kapai kan me e ketin nekinekid ong sapwellime aramas koaros.  
\v 33 I sohte kin noahroke nein emen silper de kohl de likou.  
\v 34 Kumwail ese me I kin doadoahngki pehi kat, oh koadoahkihada mehkoaros me iengei kan oh pein ngehi kin anahne.  
\v 35 Ih duwen ei kasalehiongkumwailehr ni soahng koaros me kitail en doadoahk kehlail oh sewese me luwet akan. Kitail en pil tamataman sapwellimen Kaun Sises mahsen me pein ih ketin mahsanih, ‘Kihwei kaperen sang ale.’”   
\p
\v 36 Ni ahnsou me Pohl kaimwisekala eh koasoi, irail koaros iang ih kelehpwikihdi oh kapakap.  
\v 37 Irail koaros ahpw pwoalehdi Pohl, sengiseng oh metik.  
\v 38 Re ahpw inenen nsensuwedkihla koasoio me dene irail sohte pahn pil pwurehng kilang. Irail eri likidkitalahng nin sohpo.   
\c 21  
\s1 Pohl Kohla Serusalem  
\p
\v 1 Eri, se ahpw rahnmwahwihirailla oh mwesel. Mwurin at serek kohkohla, se ahpw lel Kos, oh mandahn rahno se lel Rohdes; oh sang wasao se ahpw douluhllahng Patara.  
\v 2 Se ahpw diarada wasao sohp pwoat me pahn kolahng Penisia, kiht eri iangada.  
\v 3 Se senserek kohla se lao kilangada Saiprus, kiht eri sereklahng palieir en Saiprus oh douluhllahng Siria. Se ahpw peidi ni oaroahr en Dair, wasa me sohpo pahn kihsang ie kanenge.  
\v 4 Se tuhwong ekei me pwoson wasao, oh se mihmihki rehrail erein wihk ehu. Sang ni kaweid en Ngehn Sarawi, re ahpw padahkihong Pohl en dehr kohla Serusalem.  
\v 5 Ni eh lel ahnsoun at mwesel, se ahpw mweselsang irail. Irail koaros, iangahki arail pwoud kan oh neirail seri kan, ahpw pil iangkitada sang nan kahnimwo. Kiht koaros ahpw kelehpwikihdi pohn oaroahro oh kapakap.  
\v 6 Kiht eri rahnmwahwih emenemen irail oh karadahng pohn sohpo; re ahpw pwurala ni imwarail kan.   
\p
\v 7 Se usehlahte at seiloak, seiloaksang Dair kolahng Tolemeis, wasa me se rahnmwahwih riat me pwoson akan oh mihmih rehrail rahn ehu.  
\v 8 Mandahn rahno se ahpw mwesel oh lel Sesaria. Wasao se ahpw kohla ni imwen Pilip me kin iang kalohki rongamwahu; kiht eri koukousoan reh. Iei ih emen kisehn ohl isimen me pilipildahr en iang wia sounsawas nan Serusalem. \x - \xo 21.8 \xt Wie. 6.5; 8.5.\x*  
\v 9 Mie nah serepein kiripw pahmen, me kin padapadahngkiseli mahsen en Koht.  
\v 10 Ni at mihmihkiher wasao erein rahn ekei; soukohp emen, ede Akapwus, ahpw kohdo sang Sudia. \x - \xo 21.10 \xt Wie. 11.28.\x*  
\v 11 E kohdo reht, oh ale en Pohl eh katengo, e ahpw pein pirekipene neh oh peh kan, oh nda, “Iet me Ngehn Sarawi mahsanih: Iet duwen me mehn Suhs akan pahn wiahiong aramas me ahneki kateng wet nan Serusalem; oh re pil pahn pangala rehn mehn liki kan.”   
\p
\v 12 Eri, ni at rongehr met, kiht, oh irail kan me mi wasao, ahpw peki rehn Pohl en dehr kohla Serusalem.  
\v 13 Pohl ahpw sapengki, “Dahme kumwail sengisengki oh kauwehkilahr mohngiongi? I onopadahr, kaidehn ongete en selidi nan Serusalem, ahpw ong mehla, pwehki Kaun Sises.”   
\p
\v 14 Eri, pwehki at sohte kak wia mehkot en wekidala eh lamalam, se ahpw nda, “Eri, kupwur en Kaun-o en pweida.”   
\p
\v 15 Mwurin at koukousoankiher wasao erein ahnsou kis, se ahpw kaunopada at kepwe kan oh mwesellahng Serusalem.  
\v 16 Ekei tohnpadahk en Sesaria pil iangkitada, oh kahreikitalahng ni ihmw ehu, wasa me se pahn kousoan ie, imwen ohl emen me adaneki Neison, mehn Saiprus; ohl menet pwosonlahr sangete nin tapio.   
\s1 Pohl Tuhwong Seims  
\p
\v 17 Ni ahnsou me se lelohng nan Serusalem, riat me pwosonlahr ko inenen kasamwo kiht mwahu mehlel.  
\v 18 Mandahn rahno Pohl ahpw iangkitada pwe en kolahng tuhwong Seims, oh irail me mah kan en mwomwohdiso pil iang mi wasao.  
\v 19 Pohl eri rahnmwahwih irail oh koasoiaiong irail soahng koaros me Koht ketin wiahier nanpwungen mehn liki kan ni eh wie doadoahk rehrail.  
\v 20 Ni ar rong, irail koaros ahpw kapinga Koht. Irail eri ndaiong Pohl, “Riat Pohl, se men komwi en wehwehki met: mehn Suhs tohto me pwosonlahr, oh irail koaros inenen poadidiong Kosonnedo.  
\v 21 Irail rongehr me komw kin padapadahkihong mehn Suhs kan me koukousoan nan en mehn liki kan ar wehi en kesehla Kosonned en Moses, oh pil koasoiaiong irail re en dehr sirkumsaisihala neirail seri kan de pil idawehn tiahk kan en mehn Suhs.  
\v 22 Irail uhdahn pahn rong me komwi leledohr. Eri, dahme pahn wiawi?  
\v 23 Komw wia dahme se pahn ndaiong komwi. Ohl pahmen mihmih met me wiadahr inou ehu. \x - \xo 21.23 \xt Nempe 6.13-21.\x*  
\v 24 Eri, komw pahn iangirailla wia kasarawien kamwakel, oh pwainla pweinarail kan. Eri, re ahpw pahn kak koakoahsang pitenmoangarail kan.\f f \fr 21.24 \fk KOAKOAHSANG PITENMOANGARAIL KAN: \ft Tehk 18.18.\f* Eri, ni mwekid wet aramas koaros pahn esehki me soahng kan me irail rongehr duwen komwi me likamw, pwe pein komwi kin idawehn tiahk en Kosonned en Moses.  
\v 25 A duwen mehn liki me pwosonlahr akan, se kadaralahngirailehr kisinlikou kis oh koasoiaiong irail me se koasoanedier duwen arail sohte pahn kang mwenge me kin meirong ong dikedik en eni kan, de nta, de mahn me mwopwula, oh duwen arail pahn kanahieng pein irail sang nenek.” \x - \xo 21.25 \xt Wie. 15.29.\x*   
\p
\v 26 Pohl eri kahrehda ohl ako, oh pweidi songada e ahpw iang irail wiahda kasarawien kamwakel. E ahpw pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh pakairki duwen arail ahnsoun kamwakel en imwisekla mwurin rahn ekei, oh ni ahnsowo en emenemen meirong ahpw pahn wiawi.   
\s1 Pohl Kolkoldi nan Tehnpas Sarawio  
\p
\v 27 Eri, rahn isuh en kamwakelo eh kereniongehr imwisekla, ekei mehn Suhs akan sang wehin Eisia ahpw kilangada Pohl nan Tehnpas Sarawio. Re ahpw kamwoarongehda pokono pwon oh koledi Pohl.  
\v 28 Irail eri weriwerki, “Ohlen Israel kan! Kumwail sewesei kiht! Iei ohl menet me kin kohseli wasa koaros oh kin kaukauwe mehn Israel oh Kosonned en Moses, oh pil Tehnpas Sarawi wet. Oh met e pil kahrehlong ekei mehn liki nan Tehnpas Sarawi oh kasaminehkilahr wasa sarawi wet!”  
\v 29 (Irail nda met pwehki ar kilang Tropimus mehn Episos eh ieiang Pohl nan kahnimwo, oh re ahpw kihkihong me Pohl kahrehlong nan Tehnpas Sarawio.) \x - \xo 21.29 \xt Wie. 20.4.\x*   
\p
\v 30 Pingiping laud ahpw kipehdi nan kahnimwo pwon, oh aramas akan ahpw tangpene oh koledi Pohl oh wuruhdekihieisang nan Tehnpas Sarawio. Ni ahnsowohte re ahpw ritingedi wenihmwen Tehnpas Sarawio.  
\v 31 Pwihno ahpw songosong en kemehla Pohl; oh ni ahnsowo pakair ahpw kolahng kaunen sounpei en Rom me dene moromor wiewiawi nan Serusalem pwon.  
\v 32 Ni ahnsowohte kaunen sounpeio ahpw kahrehda opiser kei oh sounpei kei, oh mwadangdilahng pokono. Ni aramas ako ar kilangada ohlo, iangahki sounpei kan, re ahpw tokedihsang keme Pohl.  
\v 33 Kaunen sounpeio eri kohla rehn Pohl oh koledi, oh ruwese en selkihdi selmete riapwoat. E ahpw idek, “Ihs ohl menet, oh dahme e wiadahr?”  
\v 34 Eri, ekei nan pokono weriwerki ehu soahng, a ekei ehu soahng. Me inenen ping me kahrehiong kaunen sounpeio eh sohte kak dehdehki dahme wiawihero. Ih eri ndaiong nah sounpei ko re en kahrelahng Pohl nan kelen sounpeio.  
\v 35 Irail eri kahrelahng Pohl ni kehndake ko, oh sounpei ko ahpw wahda Pohl,  
\v 36 pwehki pwihnen moromoro ar pwakipwakih oh weriwerki, “En kamakamala!”   
\s1 Pohl Pein Doare Ih  
\p
\v 37 Ni ar kereniongehr pedolong nan kelen sounpeio, Pohl ahpw ndaiong kaunen sounpeio, “E kak mweiong ie I en koasoiong komwi?”  
\p Kaunen sounpeio ahpw idek, “Ke ese lokaiahn Krihs?  
\v 38 Eri, kaidehn kowe ohlen Isipo, me tapihada mwekid en moromor ehu oh kaundahr sounkam aramas pahkid nan sapwtehno?”   
\p
\v 39 Pohl ahpw sapengki, “Ngehi mehn Suhs, I ipwidi nan Tarsus en Silisia, uhdahn towe mehlel en kahnimw kesempwalo. Menlau mweidohng ie I en koasoi ong aramas pwukat.”   
\p
\v 40 Kaunen sounpeio ahpw mweidohng. Pohl eri kesihnenda pohn kehndake ko oh oaloallahng aramas ako; oh ni ar meleileidier, e ahpw koasoia ong irail ni mahsen en Ipru:   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 “Riei ko, semei ko, kumwail rongie ni ei pahn kawehwehda duwen pein ngehi mwohmwail!”  
\v 2 Ni arail rong eh lokolokaia ong irail ni mahsen en Ipru, re ahpw nennenla mehlel. Pohl eri uselahte:   
\p
\v 3 “Ngehi mehn Suhs men, me ipwidi nan Tarsus en Silisia, ahpw kekeirda nan Serusalem oh wiahier nein Kameliel tohnsukuhl. I aleier peneu kehlail nan Kosonned en samatail kahlap ako, oh uhdahn poadidiong Koht duwehte kumwail koaros me mi met rahnwet. \x - \xo 22.3 \xt Wie. 5.34-39.\x*  
\v 4 I kalokehier irail akan me idawehn Ahl pwoatet, oh kemeirailla. I salihdier ohl akan oh pil lih akan, oh keseiraillong nan imweteng. \x - \xo 22.4 \xt Wie. 8.3; 26.9-11.\x*  
\v 5 Eri, Samworo Lapalap oh Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo pwon kak kadehdehda me ei koasoi kat me mehlel. I aleier kisinlikou kei me ntingdahr ong riatail mehn Suhs kan nan Damaskus. Eri, I ahpw kohla wasao pwe I en salihekihdi aramas pwukat selmete oh kahreiraildohng Serusalem pwe re en kalokolok.”   
\s1 Pohl Koasoia duwen Eh Wekila  
\r (Pil tehk Wie. 9.1-19; 26.12-18)  
\p
\v 6 “Eri, ni ei seiseiloak oh karanih Damaskus, mwein nin souwas, marain ehu ahpw dakeriehda sang nanleng oh kapiliepene.  
\v 7 I ahpw pwupwudiong nan pwehl oh rongada ngihl ehu me mahsanih, ‘Sohl, Sohl, dahme ke kin kalokalokehkin ie?”  
\v 8 Ngehi eri patohwan, ‘Ihs komwi, Maing ei Kaun?’ Ngihlo ahpw sapeng ie mahsanih, ‘Ngehi Sises mehn Nasaret me ke kin kalokaloke.’  
\v 9 Eri, ohl ako me iang ie pil iang kilang maraino, ahpw re sohte rong kapitien me mahsendohng ieo.  
\v 10 I ahpw patohwan idek, ‘A dahme I pahn wia, Maing ei Kaun?” Eri, Kaun-o ahpw mahsanihong ie, ‘Uhda oh kohwei Damaskus, pwe ke pahn ese wasao soahng koaros me Koht ketin koasoanediong uhk ke en wia.’  
\v 11 Ngehi eri maskunla pwehki lingaling en maraino. Eri, irail me iang ie ko ahpw koledi pehiet oh kahluwaielahng Damaskus.   
\p
\v 12 “Eri, mie ohl emen me adaneki Ananaias, ohl sarawi men me kin poadidi oh peikiong atail Kosonned, ohl me kin keniken mehlel rehn mehn Suhs akan koaros me koukousoan Damaskus.  
\v 13 E ahpw kohdo rehi oh kesihnenda limwahi oh nda, ‘Riei Sohl, komw pwurehng kilangada wasa!’ Eri, ni ahnsowohte I ahpw kilangada wasa oh kak kilang ohlo.  
\v 14 E pil nda, ‘Koht en samatail kahlap ako ketin piluhkada pwe ke en esehla kupwure, oh ke en kilang sapwellime Ladu pwung, oh ke en rong kapitie.  
\v 15 Pwe ke pahn wiahla sapwellime sounkadehde pwe ke en koasoia ong aramas koaros dahme ke kilangehr oh rongehr.  
\v 16 Eri met, dahme ke awiawih? Uhda oh papidaisla pwe dipomw kan en wideudsang ni omw pahn likweriong mware.’   
\s1 Malipilip ong Pohl pwe en Padahkohng mehn Liki kan  
\p
\v 17 “Eri, I ahpw pwuralahng Serusalem, oh ni ei wie kapakap nan Tehnpas Sarawio, I ahpw kilangada kaudiahl ehu.  
\v 18 Nan kaudiahlo I kilang Kaun-o ni eh mahsanih, ‘Mwadangewei sang Serusalem, pwehki aramas en wasaht sohte pahn kamehlele omw kadehde ie.’  
\v 19 I ahpw patohwan, ‘Maing ei Kaun, irail inenen eseier duwen ei kohla nan sinakoke kan oh koledi oh keme irail kan me pwoson komwi.  
\v 20 Oh ni ahnsou me sapwellimomwi sounkadehde Stipen kamakamala, pein ngehi pil iang mi wasao, oh pwungki eh kamakamalao oh apwahpwalih en irail kan me kemehlao ar likoun liki kan.’ \x - \xo 22.20 \xt Wie. 7.58.\x*  
\v 21 Kaun-o ahpw mahsanihong ie, ‘Kohweite, pwe I pahn kadaruhkalahng wasa doh, rehn mehn liki kan.’”   
\p
\v 22 Aramas ako ahpw wie rongorong Pohl e lao wia koasoia pwoatet; irail eri tapihada weriwer, ndinda, “En pekeusweisang met! En kamakamala! E sohte warohng en momour!”  
\v 23 Irail eri wie weriwer oh oaloalki ar likou kan, oh kesekesedahng pwelpar nan wehwe.  
\v 24 Eri, kaunen sounpei en Rom ahpw padahkihong nah sounpei ko re en kahrelahng Pohl nan arail kelen sounpei. E pil ndaiong irail re en wokih, pwe en kak wehwehkihla kahrepen en mehn Suhs akan ar weriwer oh pelipelian. \fig |alt="HK-15F Wasahn iroir en kelen sounpei" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 22.24" \fig*  
\v 25 Eri, ni arail salihedi pwe en wowoki, Pohl ahpw ndaiong me lapalap emen me kesikesihnen wasao, “Me pwung kumwail en wokih towe mehlel en Rom men, me saikinte pakadeingkihda dihp ehu?”   
\p
\v 26 Eri, ni opisero eh rong met, e ahpw kohla rehn kaunen sounpeio oh patohwanohng, “Dahme komw wiewia? Pwe ohlo tohn wehin Rom mehlel men!”   
\p
\v 27 Kaunen sounpeio eri kohla rehn Pohl oh idek reh, “Ndaiong ie mahs, ma mehlel kowe tohn wehin Rom mehlel men?”  
\p Pohl ahpw sapengki, “Ei.”   
\p
\v 28 Kaunen sounpeio ahpw nda, “Ngehi, I wialahr tohn wehin Rom mehlel men ni ei pwainkihda uwen mwohni laud ehu.”  
\p Pohl ahpw sapeng, nda, “Ahpw ngehi sang ni ei ipwidi.”   
\p
\v 29 Ni ahnsowo ohl ako me pahn kapeidek Pohl ahpw kohkohlahsang. Eri, kaunen sounpeio ahpw masepwehkada ni eh wehwehkidahr me Pohl uhdahn towe mehlel men en wehin Rom me selkidier selmete.   
\s1 Pohl Mwohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalap  
\p
\v 30 Kaunen sounpeio ahpw men ese ni mehlel dahme mehn Suhs ako kedipahki Pohl. Eri, pweidi songada, e ahpw ruwese selmete ko en sapwedekda, oh e pil kapokonepene samworo lapalap ako oh pil Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo pwon. Ih eri kahrehla Pohl oh kasihnenihada mwohrail koaros.   
\c 23  
\p
\v 1 Pohl eri kakiledi Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo oh nda, “Riei ko, mohngiongi me inenen mwakelekel nin duwen ei mour unsek mwohn silangin Koht leledohng rahnwet.”  
\v 2 Samworo Lapalap Ananaias ahpw padahkihong irail kan me kesikesihnen mpen Pohl re en pohr ewe.  
\v 3 Pohl eri ndaiong, “Koht uhdahn pahn dupukohng komwi, mwalaun komwi liksansalamwahu! Komwi ketidiong wasahn kopwung pwe en kadeik ie nin duwen Kosonnedo, a komwi ahpw kauwehla Kosonnedo ni omwi mahsanih irail pwukat en pohr ie!” \x - \xo 23.3 \xt Mad. 23.27-28.\x*   
\p
\v 4 Ohl akan me mi mpen Pohl eri ndaiong, “Ke inenen lahlahwe sapwellimen Koht Samworo Lapalap!”   
\p
\v 5 Pohl ahpw sapengkin irail, “Riei ko, I sohte ese me ih Samworo Lapalapo. Pwe Pwuhk Sarawi mahsanih, ‘Ke sohte pahn kauwe kaunen noumw aramas akan.’” \x - \xo 23.5 \xt Eks. 22.28.\x*   
\p
\v 6 Ni Pohl eh kilang me ekei tohn pokono kisehn Sadusi oh ekei kisehn Parisi, e ahpw kalaudehla ngile ong Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, nda, “Riei ko, ngehi Parisi men, pil nein Parisi men. I pakadeikdahr wasakiset pwehki ei koapworopworki me melahr kan pahn pil pwurehng iasadahng mour!” \x - \xo 23.6 \xt Wie. 26.5; Pil 3.5.\x*   
\p
\v 7 Eri, ni ahnsou me e nda met, Parisi ko oh Sadusi ko ahpw tapihada akamaipene nanpwungarail; re ahpw liaktohrohrpeseng.  
\v 8 (Pwe Sadusi kan re kin koasoia me aramas akan sohte pahn kak iasada sang mehla, oh pil sohte tohnleng, de pil ngehn—ahpw Parisi kan kamehlele soahng siluh pwukat koaros.) \x - \xo 23.8 \xt Mad. 22.23; Mark 12.18; Luk 20.27.\x*  
\v 9 Eri, weriwer ahpw lalaudla, oh ekei sounpadahk en Kosonnedo me kisehn pwihn en Parisi kan ahpw uhda oh koasoia ni kehlail, “Se sohte diar mehkot me sapwung rehn ohl menet. Mwein ngehn ehu de tohnleng men me mahseniong.”   
\p
\v 10 Akamaio inenen lalaudla mehlel, oh kaunen sounpeio ahpw masakada re de dapengpeseng Pohl. E ahpw ndaiong nah sounpei ko re en kohdilahng nan pokono oh kihieisang Pohl rehrail, oh kahrelahng nan arail kelen sounpeio.   
\p
\v 11 Nipwongo, Kaun-o ahpw ket limwahn Pohl oh mahsanihong, “Pohl, ke dehr masak! Duwen omw eimah kadehdeiedahr nan Serusalem; eri, ke uhdahn pahn pil wia duwehte met nan Rom.”   
\s1 Pwihn Ehu Men Kemehla Pohl  
\p
\v 12 Ni eh rahnpeseng, mehn Suhs ako ahpw tuhpene oh wiahda koasoandi ehu. Irail inoukihda me irail sohte pahn kang de nim mehkot, irail lao pahn kemehla Pohl.  
\v 13 Me tohto sang pehk me inoukidahr koasoandi wet.  
\v 14 Irail eri kohla rehn samworo lapalap ako oh rehn me mah kan oh ndaiong irail, “Se inoukidahr ni kehlail me se sohte pahn kang de nim mehkot lao se kemehla Pohl.  
\v 15 Eri, kumwail iang Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo oh ileklahng kaunen sounpei en Romo pwe en kahredohng kumwail Pohl, kumwail mwomwehda me kumwail men ese ni mehlel sang reh soahng kei. Ahpw se pahn onopada se en kemehla mwohn eh pahn leledo wasaht.”   
\p
\v 16 Eri, wahwahn Pohl pwutak emen ahpw rongada duwen koasoandi wet, e ahpw kohla oh pedolong nan kelen sounpei ko oh ndaiong Pohl duwen met.  
\v 17 Pohl eri ekerodo emen opiser ako oh ndaiong, “Komw kahrehla mwahnakapw menet rehn kaunen sounpeio, pwe mie mehkot me e men koasoiaiong.”  
\v 18 Opisero eri kahrehda pwutako, oh kahrelahng rehn kaunen sounpeio, oh ndaiong, “Pohl me selidiero eker ie oh peki I en kahredohng komwi mwahnakapw menet, pwe dene mie mehkot me e men patohwanohng komwi.”   
\p
\v 19 Kaunen sounpeio eri ale pehn pwutako oh kelehpwkihla, a ahpw idek reh, “Dahme ke pahn koasoiaiong ie?”   
\p
\v 20 Mwahnakapwo ahpw nda, “Mehn Suhs akan pwungkipenehr me lakapw re pahn peki komwi en kahredilahng Pohl rehn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo, re pahn mwomwehda me Pwihn Lapalapo anahne ale ekei kadehde sansal duwen ih.  
\v 21 Ahpw komw dehr dukiong irail, pwe tohtohsang ohl pehk me pahn rukuruk oh awiawih Pohl. Eri, irail koaros inoukidahr me re sohte pahn kang de nim mehkot lao re kemehla Pohl. Met re kaunopadahr pwe re en wia soahng wet, oh re awiawih dahme komw pahn koasoanehdi.”   
\p
\v 22 Kaunen sounpeio ahpw nda, “Ke dehpa koasoiaiong emen duwen me ke koasoiaiong ie.” E ahpw kadarala mwahnakapwo.   
\s1 Pohl Pekederlahng Mwohn Kepina Peliks  
\p
\v 23 Kaunen sounpeio eri ekerodo riemen nah opiser ko oh ndaiong ira, “Kumwa kaunopada sounpei riepwiki pwe re en kohla Sesaria, iangahki isiakan soundake oahs, oh riepwiki ohlen kesik ketieu, oh onopada pwe re en mwesel kulok duwau pwohnget.  
\v 24 Kumwa pil kaunopada ekei oahs pwe Pohl en dake, kanahieng apwahpwalih lao lel rehn Kepina Peliks.”  
\v 25 Kaunen sounpeio pil ntingihada kisinlikou kis me koasoia:   
\pi1
\v 26 “Sang ngehi Klaudius Lisias, ong Kepina Peliks: Kaselehlie Maing.  
\v 27 Mehn Suhs akan koledier ohl menet oh kereniong re en kemehla. Eri, I esehda me ohl menet uhdahn towe mehlel en wehin Rom. Ihme kahrehda pein ngehi oh ei tungoal sounpei kan ahpw kohla oh kapitala sang mehn Suhs kan.  
\v 28 I anahne ese dahme re kedipahki; eri, I ahpw kahredilahng rehn arail Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo.  
\v 29 Eri, met I diarada me e sohte wiahda mehkot me pahn kahrehiong mehla de selidi; ahpw kadip me re kedipahki ohl menet pidada duwen arail Kosonned.  
\v 30 Oh ni ei esedahr me mehn Suhs akan wiadahr koasoandi ehu me uhwong, I ahpw koasoanehdi I en kadarowohng rehmwi ohl menet. I patohwanohng irail re en wia ar kadip mwohmwi.”   
\p
\v 31 Sounpei ko eri kapwaiada me re en wia; oh re kahrehla Pohl lel Antipatris nipwongohte.  
\v 32 Mandahn rahno sounpei ko me sapal ahpw pwuralahng arail wasa, a irail me dake oahs ahpw iangada Pohl.  
\v 33 Re ahpw kahrelahng nan Sesaria oh kihong rehn Kepinao iangahki kisinlikowo sang kaunen sounpeio.  
\v 34 Kepinao ahpw wadek kisinlikowo oh idek rehn Pohl mehnia sahpw me e kohdo sang ie. Ni eh diarada me ih mehn Silisia,  
\v 35 e ahpw mahsanih, “I pahn rong uhk ni ahnsou me irail akan me kedipaiuk pahn leledo.” Ih eri mahsanih irail en apwahpwalih oh sinsile Pohl nan tehnpesen Erod mahso.   
\c 24  
\s1 Mehn Suhs akan Kedipa Pohl  
\p
\v 1 Mwurin rahn limau, Samworo Lapalap Ananaias ahpw kohla Sesaria iangahki me mah kei en mehn Suhs kan oh sounkawehwe kosonned en Rom men me adaneki Tertulus. Irail pwukat ahpw pwarodo mwohn Kepina Peliks oh wia arail kadip akan me uhwong Pohl.  
\v 2 Pohl eri likwerlong; Tertulus ahpw tapihada kedipa Pohl nin duwe met:  
\p “Maing Peliks, sapwellimomwi koahiek en kaweid me kihongkitehr meleilei ahnsou reirei, oh soangen wekdekla kei me anahnepe mie nin duwen kamwahupen at wehi wet pil wiawiher.  
\v 3 Se inenen kapingkalahngkihong komwi duwen ire pwukat ahnsou koaros oh wasa koaros.  
\v 4 I sohte men kasohlapahkihla omwi ahnsou. Eri soh, I peki komwi en ketin kapaidoke at pato ni oaralap.  
\v 5 Se diarada ohl menet me keper oh kedirepw, e tapihadahr moromor kei nanpwungen mehn Suhs akan nan sampah pwon, oh e pil wiahier sounkaweid en pwihnen Nasarihn kan.  
\v 6 E pil songehr en kasaminehla Tehnpas Sarawio. Eri, se ahpw koledi. [Se men kadeikada nin duwen at Kosonned,  
\v 7 ahpw kaunen sounpei Lisias patohdo oh adihasang kiht.  
\v 8 Eri, Lisias ahpw patohwanohng irail me kedipa ohl menet re en patohdo rehmwi.] Ma komw pahn kapeidek ohl menet, pein komwi pahn ketin diarada sang reh soahng kan me se kedipahki.”  
\v 9 Eri, mehn Suhs akan pil iang kadip wet oh koasoia me mepwukat me mehlel.   
\s1 En Pohl eh Doarehla Pein Ih Mwohn Peliks  
\p
\v 10 Kepinao eri oaloallahng Pohl en kadehdehda pein ih. Pohl eri patohwan,  
\p “I wehwehki me komwi wiahier sounkopwung en wehi erein pahr tohtohie. Eri, ihme kahrehda I pil perenki I en doare pein ngehi mwohmwi.  
\v 11 Duwen omwi kak pein mwahngih, e saikinte rahn eisek riau dou pohn ei patohdalahr Serusalem pwe I en wia ei kaudok.  
\v 12 Mehn Suhs ako sohte mwahn kilangiehda ei akamaiong emen nan Tehnpas Sarawio. Re pil sohte kilang ei kamwkamwoaronga aramas akan, nan arail sinakoke kan de wasa kis nan kahnimwo.  
\v 13 Oh irail pil sohte kak wia kadehdepen kadip akan me irail kedipahkin ie.  
\v 14 I kasalehiong komwi met: I kin kaudokiong Koht en samat kahlap ako ni ei kin ideidawehn Ahlo me irail koasoia dene me likamw. I pil kamehlele soahng koaros me ntingdier nan Kosonned en Moses oh pil nan pwuken soukohp akan.  
\v 15 I koapworopworki Koht, duwen me pein ohl pwukat kin koapworopworki, me aramas koaros, me mwahu oh suwed, pahn iasada sang mehla.  
\v 16 Oh I kin wia uwen ei kak ahnsou koaros I en ahneki mohngiong mwakelekel ehu mwohn Koht oh aramas akan.   
\p
\v 17 “Eri, mwurin ei kohsang Serusalem nan erein sounpar kei, I pil pwuralahng wasao walahng pein ei aramas akan mwohni, oh pwe I en pil wia ei meirong kan. \x - \xo 24.17 \xt Wie. 21.17-28.\x*  
\v 18 Iei ih ahnsou me I wiewia mepwukat me irail diar ie nan Tehnpas Sarawio, mwurin ei kanekelahr kasarawien kamwakel. Sohte pokon ehu me iang ie, oh pil sohte pingiping ehu mie.  
\v 19 Ahpw mehn Suhs kei sang Eisia iang mi wasao; pein irail en patohdo mwohmwi oh wia arail kadip akan, ma mie mehkot rehrail me uhwong ie.  
\v 20 De mweidohng ohl pwukat me miher met re en patohwanda dihp dahnge me irail diar me I dipkidahr ni ahnsou me I mi mwohn Tohn Mwoalen Kopwung Lapalapo.  
\v 21 Ahpw ihte me I wia ni ahnsou me I miher mwohrail; I nda, ‘Kumwail kadeikiedahr rahnwet pwehki ei kamehlele me melahr akan pahn iasadahng mour.’” \x - \xo 24.21 \xt Wie. 23.6.\x*   
\p
\v 22 Eri, Peliks me wehwehkidahr mwahu duwen Ahlo ahpw kanekehla karongorongo. E ahpw mahsanihong irail, “I pahn koasoanehdi amwail ire wet, ni ahnsou me kaunen sounpei Lisias pahn lao pwarodo.”  
\v 23 E ahpw koasoia me silepe me sinsile Pohl en sinsilehte, ahpw re pahn mweidohng ekis saledek oh mweidohng kompoakepah kan en apwalih oh kihong dahme e pahn anahne.   
\s1 Pohl Mwohn Peliks oh Drusila  
\p
\v 24 Eri, mwurin rahn ekei Peliks ahpw pwarodo iangahki eh pwoud Drusila. Liho mehn Suhs men. E ahpw ileklahng Pohl en kohdo, pwe en karonge eh koasoakoasoia duwen pwoson Sises Krais.  
\v 25 Ahpw ni en Pohl eh usehlahte koasoakoasoia duwen aramas me mour mwakelekel, oh duwen aramas ar pahn powehdi pein arail ineng suwed, oh pil duwen Rahnen Kadeik me pahn kohdo, Peliks eri lehnda oh mahsanih, “Eri, ke kakehr mwesel ahnsou wet. I nek pil pwurehng eker uhk ni ei pahn pisekla.”  
\v 26 E ahpw kupwukupwure me Pohl pahn kihong mwohni; ihme e kin kalap ekerkihdo oh koasoikihong.   
\p
\v 27 Eri, mwurin sounpar riau, Porsius Pestus uhd wiliandi Peliks oh wiahla kepina. Peliks men masamasala rehn mehn Suhs akan, ihme kahrehda Pohl mihmihkihte nan imweteng.   
\c 25  
\s1 Pohl Peki Kopwung Sapahl Rehn Sihsar  
\p
\v 1 Eri, rahn siluh mwurin en Pestus eh leledohr nan sahpwo, e ahpw kohsang Sesaria oh kohdalahng Serusalem.  
\v 2 Wasao samworo lapalap akan oh kaunen mehn Suhs akan ahpw kedipa Pohl reh. Irail ahpw peki rehn Pestus  
\v 3 en kapwaiong irail nsenarail pwe en kadarodohng Pohl Serusalem, pwe irail kaunopadahr pwihn ehu pwe re en kemehla nanialo.  
\v 4 Pestus ahpw sapeng irail, mahsanih, “Pohl wie sensel nan imweteng en Sesaria, oh pein ngehi pahn pil pwuralahng wasao ni ahnsou keren.  
\v 5 Eri, amwail kaun akan en iangiehda kolahng Sesaria oh kedipa Pohl wasao, ma e wiahda mehkot sapwung.”   
\p
\v 6 Eri, Pestus koukousoankiher rehrail ele rahn waluh de eisek, oh mwuri e ahpw douluhllahng Sesaria. Mahndahn rahno e ahpw ketidiong nan mwoalen kopwung, oh mahsanih Pohl en pakahrdo.  
\v 7 Ni ahnsou me Pohl leledo, mehn Suhs akan me kohsang Serusalem ahpw kapilpene oh kedipahki kedip toutou kei me pein irail sohte kak kadehdehda duwe.  
\v 8 Ahpw Pohl pein doarehla pein ih, oh koasoia, “I sohte wia mehkot me uhwong Kosonned en mehn Suhs akan, de Tehnpas Sarawio, de Sihsar en Rom.”   
\p
\v 9 Pestus anahne en keniken rehn mehn Suhs akan, ihme kahrehda e idek rehn Pohl, “Ke pwungki ke en kolahng Serusalem oh kadeik mwohi wasao ong ni iren kadip pwukat?”   
\p
\v 10 Pohl ahpw patohwan, “I mihmi mwohn mwoalen kopwung en Sihsar, wasa me I uhdahn pahn pakadeida ie. I sohte mwahn wia sapwung ehu ong mehn Suhs akan, nin duwen omwi mwahngih.  
\v 11 Ma I kauwehla kosonned ehu, de wiahda mehkot me pahn kahrehiong ie I en ale kalokolok en kamala, I sohte peki I en pitsang. Ahpw ma arail kadip kan me irail kedipahkin ie me likamw, eri, sohte emen me kak pangielahng rehrail. Eri, I peki kopwung sapahl rehn Sihsar.”   
\p
\v 12 Eri, mwurin Pestus eh wie lamalam ong nah sounkaweid kan, e ahpw sapengki, “Ke peki kopwung sapahl rehn Sihsar; eri, ke pahn kohla reh.”   
\s1 Pohl Mwohn Akripa oh Pernis  
\p
\v 13 Eri, mwurin rahn ekei Nanmwarki Akripa oh Pernis ira ahpw ketidohng Sesaria pwe ira en tuhwong oh kasamwo Pestus.  
\v 14 Mwurin ara ketiketier wasao erein rahn ekei, Pestus ahpw kawehwehiong nanmwarkio duwen kadip akan me uhwong Pohl. E ahpw patohwan, “Mie ohl selidi men me Peliks pwilikihdiong met.  
\v 15 Eri, ni ahnsou me I pwaralahng Serusalem, samworo lapalap en mehn Suhs akan, oh me mah kan ahpw kedipa oh peki I en kemehla.  
\v 16 I ahpw ndaiong irail me mehn Rom kan sohte kin epwehnki pangala aramas emen me kedipidipkihda dihp toutou ehu mwohn eh saikinte tuhwong me kedipa kan nan wasahn kopwung, oh pahn ahneki ahnsoun doare pein ih sang kadip akan me uhwong.  
\v 17 Eri, ni ahnsou me irail koaros pwarodohr wasaht, I sohte kasohlapahla ahnsou; I ahpw mwohndiong nan mwoalen kopwung oh ileklahng ohlo en pakahrdo.  
\v 18 Irail kan me kedipa ahpw uhda mwohi, ahpw re sohte kedipahki soangen dihp suwed kan me I kihkihong me irail pahn wia.  
\v 19 Ahpw ihte me irail wia, re akamaikihong duwen pein arail palien lamalam, oh pil duwen ohl emen me melahr me adaneki Sises, me Pohl koasoia me e wie momourte.  
\v 20 I sohte kak koasoanehdi ia duwen ei pahn kak ale ire dehde ehu ong ire pwukat. I ahpw idek rehn Pohl, ma e pahn pwungki en kolahng Serusalem oh kadeik wasao nin duwen kadip pwukat.  
\v 21 Ahpw Pohl peki en senselte, oh I en kadaralahng rehn Sihsar, pwe nanmwarki lapalapo en koasoanehdi eh ire. Eri, I koasoanehdi en senselte I lao pahn kak kadaralahng rehn Sihsar.”   
\p
\v 22 Akripa ahpw mahsanihong Pestus, “Pein ngehi men rong ohl menet.”  
\p Pestus ahpw patohwan sapengki, “Komw pahn karonge lakapw.”   
\p
\v 23 Eri, mandahn rahno Akripa oh Pernis ahpw ketila ni lapalahn kasamw oh wahu oh ketilong wasahn kopwung iangahki me lapalap en sounpei kan oh kaun akan en kahnimwo. Pestus eri ileklahng Pohl; Pohl eri pakahrdo.  
\v 24 Pestus eri patohwan, “Maing, Nanmwarki Akripa, oh koaros me iang kiht patopato wasaht, kumwail patohwan ohl menet, me mehn Suhs akan me pato met, oh pil nan Serusalem, kedipa rehi. Irail weriwerki en kamala.  
\v 25 Ahpw I sohte kak diarada mehkot reh me en kamakamkihla. Eri, pwehki pein ih pil peki kopwung sapahl rehn Sihsar, eri, I koasoanehdi me I pahn ntingkilahng Sihsar.  
\v 26 Ahpw sohte sapwung ehu me I diar reh me I pahn ntingkilahng Sihsar. Eri, iet ih mwohmwi, maing Nanmwarki Akripa. Eri, mwurin ei pahn raparapahki duwen eh ire kan, I kakehr kilelehdi mehkot oh pakairkilahng Sihsar.  
\v 27 Pwe me pahn sapwung ong ie ma I kadarala aramas selidi men ni eh sohte dehde kadip akan me uhwong.”   
\c 26  
\s1 Pohl Doare Pein Ih Mwohn Akripa  
\p
\v 1 Eri, Akripa ahpw mahsanihong Pohl, “Ke mweimweiongehr koasoia duwen pein kowe.” Pohl eri kapahwei peh oh doare pein ih nin duwen met:   
\p
\v 2 Maing Nanmwarki Akripa, I inenen paiamwahu rahnwet pwehki ei kak doareiehsang mehkoaros me mehn Suhs akan kedipahkin ie.  
\v 3 Met me inenen mehlel, pwehki komw mwahngih mwahu duwen tiahk en mehn Suhs akan oh pil arail wiewia kan. Eri, I peki rehmwi komwi en kanengamah oh ketin karonge ie.   
\p
\v 4 “Mehn Suhs akan koaros kin wehwehki duwen mwomwen ei mour sang ni ei pwulopwul. Irail pil ese mwomwen ei mour nin tapio, pwe I kin koukousoan nan ei tungoal kahnimw, oh pil nan Serusalem.  
\v 5 Irail pil wehwehki sang nin tapio, ma irail men kadehde, me sang mahs ngehi emen kisehn pwihnen Parisi me keieu poadidiong at palien lamalam. \x - \xo 26.5 \xt Wie. 23.6; Pil 3.5.\x*  
\v 6 Eri, met I pakadeikdahr pwehki ei koapworopworki inou me Koht ketin wiahiongehr samat kahlap ako—  
\v 7 iei inou wetohte me at kadaudok eisek riauo koaros kin koapworopworki en ale, ni arail kaudok ong Koht ni rahn nipwong. Eri, koapworopwor wet, maing nanmwarki, me I dipkidahr rehn mehn Suhs akan.  
\v 8 Eri, dahme kahrehda kumwail mehn Suhs akan sohte kak kamehlelehki me Koht kin ketin kaiasada me melahr akan? \x - \xo 26.8 \xt 2 Mak. 7.9.\x*   
\p
\v 9 “Pein ngehi medemedewe me I pahn wia soahng koaros ni uwen ei kak pwe I en uhwong mwaren Sises mehn Nasaret. \x - \xo 26.9 \xt Wie. 8.3; 22.4-5.\x*  
\v 10 Iei met me I wiahier nan Serusalem, I ahpw ale manaman sang rehn samworo lapalap akan oh salihedi sapwellimen Koht aramas tohtohie; oh ni arail pengpenglahn kamala, I pil inenen iang pwungki mehlel.  
\v 11 Pak tohto I kaloke irail nan en mehn Suhs kan ar sinakoke kan, oh song pwe re en kahmahmkihla arail pwoson. I inenen lingeringerkin irail; ihme kahrehda I pil kohkilahr nan kahnimw en wehin liki kan pwe I en kaloke irail.”   
\s1 Pohl Koasoiahda duwen Eh Wekila  
\r (Pil tehk Wie. 9.1-19; 22.6-16)  
\p
\v 12 “Iei kahrepe wet me I pil kohkilahng Damaskus sang ni manaman oh kehkehlik sang rehn samworo lapalap akan.  
\v 13 Eri, pohn ahlo nin souwas, maing nanmwarki, I ahpw kilangada marain ehu me lingaling sang ketipin, me dakodo sang nanleng ahpw kapiliepene oh pil ohl akan me iang ie seiseiloak.  
\v 14 Kiht koaros eri pwupwudiong nanpwel, oh I ahpw rong ngihl ehu me peidohng ie ni mahsen en Ipru, ‘Sohl, Sohl, dahme ke kalokalokehkin ie? Ni omw wiewia men, ke pein kauwehkinuhkala, rasehng kouwol emen me kin pahd kisin tuhke keng me soundakepe kin wokihki.’  
\v 15 I ahpw idek, ‘Ihs komwi, Maing ei Kaun?’ Kaun-o eri mahsanih, ‘Ngehi Sises me ke kin kalokaloke.  
\v 16 Uhda, pwe I pwarohng uhk pwe I en piluhkada pwe ke en wiahla ei ladu. Ke pahn koasoiaiong meteikan dahme ke kilang rehi rahnwet, oh pil dahme I pahn kasalehiong uhk ni ahnsou kohkohdo.  
\v 17 I pahn doareiukasang rehn aramas en Israel kan, oh pil sang mehn liki kan, me I pahn kadarowohng uhk rehrail.  
\v 18 Ke pahn kapehdpeseng masarail kan, oh kahreiraildo sang nan rotorot ong nan marain, oh pil sang nan manaman en Sehdan ong Koht; pwehki ni arail pwoson ie, diparail akan pahn lapwada oh re pahn pedolong nan dewerail rehn sapwellimen Koht me pilipildahr akan.’”   
\s1 Pohl Koasoiahda duwen Eh Doadoahk  
\p
\v 19 “Eri, maing Nanmwarki Akripa, I sohte kin kasohwe me I aleier sang nanleng.  
\v 20 Keieu, nan Damaskus oh nan Serusalem, oh pil nan kahnimw en Sudia pwon, oh nanpwungen mehn liki kan, I kapahrengkihong irail re en koluhla oh wiliakapwala; re en wekiong Koht, oh wia soahng kan me pahn kasalehda me re wiliakapwalahr. \x - \xo 26.20 \xt Wie. 9.20, 28-29.\x*  
\v 21 Iei kahrepe wet me mehn Suhs akan kolkiniehdi nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh song en kemeiehla.  
\v 22 Ahpw lel rahnwet Koht ketin sewese ie, oh met I patohier wasaht oh wia ei kadehdehiong kumwail koaros, me tikitik oh me lapalap akan. Eri, met me I patopatohwan, iei soahngohte me soukohp ako oh Moses pil mahsaniher me pahn wiawi:  
\v 23 me Mesaia uhdahn pahn lokolok oh ih me pahn tepin iasada sang mehla, pwe en kasalehda marain en komour ong mehn Suhs akan oh pil ong mehn liki kan.” \x - \xo 26.23 \xt 1 Kor. 15.20; b Ais. 42.6; 49.6.\x*   
\p
\v 24 Eri, ni en Pohl eh doandoare pein ih ni irair wet, Pestus ahpw wering, patohwan, “Pohl, ke iahkalahr! Omw sukuhl laud kahrehiong omw iahkalahr!”   
\p
\v 25 Pohl ahpw sapengki, “I sohte iahk, maing Pestus. Koasoi pwukat me I koasoia me mehlel oh maledek.  
\v 26 Maing Nanmwarki Akripa! I kak eimah patohieng komwi pwehki omwi mwahngih mepwukat. I koapworopworki me komw erekiher ire pwukat koaros, pwehki mepwukat sohte wiawi ni rir nan keimw ehu.  
\v 27 Maing Nanmwarki Akripa, komw sohte kamehlele soukohp ako? I patohwan ese me komwi ketin kamehlele!”   
\p
\v 28 Akripa eri mahsanihong Pohl, “Nan erein ahnsou mwotomwot kiset ke medemedewe me ke kak kahrehda ei soulengla?”   
\p
\v 29 Pohl eri patohwanohng, “Mehnda ma ahnsou mwotomwot de reirei, iet ei tungoal kapakap ong Koht: komwi oh pil irail pwukat me rongorong ie rahnwet, en duweiehla—ahpw kaidehn ni selmete pwukat.”   
\p
\v 30 Eri, nanmwarkio, kepinao, Pernis, oh pil meteikan koaros, re ahpw ketida;  
\v 31 oh mwurin ar mwesel re ahpw ndapene nanpwungarail, “Ohl menet sohte mwahn wiahda mehkot me pahn kahrehiong en kamala de selidi.”  
\v 32 Akripa eri mahsanihong Pestus, “Ohl menet kakete lapwada, ma e sohte peki kopwung sapahl rehn Sihsar.”   
\c 27  
\s1 Pohl Sereksang Rom  
\p
\v 1 Eri, ni eh koasoandier me se pahn sereklahng Itali, irail ahpw kihong Pohl oh pil ekei me seldier ko rehn Sulius, opiser men nan pwihnen sounpei en Rom me adaneki “Sapwellimen Sihsar Pwihn.”  
\v 2 Se ahpw karada pohn sohp pwoat sang Adramitium, me kaunopadahr en mwesellahng kahnimw kan me mi ni oaroahr kan en wehin Eisia; se ahpw mwesel. Aristarkus, mehn Masedonia men sang Desalonika, pil iang kiht.  
\v 3 Mandahn rahno se ahpw lel Saidon. Sulius me kadek ong Pohl, oh mweidohng en kohla oh tuhwong kompoakepah kan, pwe en ale sang rehrail dahme e anahne.  
\v 4 Se ahpw douluhlsang wasao, oh pwehki eh engsuwed se ahpw serek oh tang pahn mwetehn Saiprus.  
\v 5 Se kohtehla sehd me sallahng Silisia oh Pampilia oh lel Maira nan Lisia.  
\v 6 Wasao opisero ahpw diarada sohp pwoat sang Aleksandria me pahn seiloaklahng Itali; eri, e ahpw kidahng kiht powe.   
\p
\v 7 Se ahpw senserek wawai kohla erein rahn ekei, oh nan apwal laud se ahpw lel kahnimw Naidus. Pwehki eh engsuwed, kahrehda se sohte kak inenweite, se ahpw sereklahng wasa mwele kis likin deke Krihd, oh daulih imwinsapwen Salmone.  
\v 8 Eri, pwehki eh apwal, se ahpw peianla limwahn sahpwo oh lel wasa kis me adaneki Kepdau Mwahu, me sohte dohsang kahnimw Lasea.   
\p
\v 9 Eri, se mihmihki wasao ahnsou reirei, oh me keperiong kiht se en usehla at seiloako, pwehki ni ahnsowo eh daulihalahr Rahnen Tomw.\f g \fr 27.9 \fk RAHNEN TOMW: \ft Rahnen tomw kin wiawi ni imwin Septempe de ni tepin Oktohpe, ni ahnsowo kisinieng kin kehlail oh kin keper seiloak nan madau.\f* Pohl eri kaweidkin irail,  
\v 10 “Maing ko, I pehmadahr me atail seiloak sang met kohla pahn inenen keper mehlel; kepwe kan oh sohp wet pahn ohla, oh ekei kitail pahn mehla.”  
\v 11 Ahpw kaunen sounpeio inenen koapworopworki dahme kepin en sohpo, oh me wareneki sohpo nda, sang dahme Pohl nda.  
\v 12 Kepdauwo kaidehn kepdau mwahu ong sohp en peipei ie ni ahnsoun kopou. Ihme kahrehda pali tohtohn ohl ako pwungki se en mwesel oh song en lel Pihniks, ma e kak. Pihniks kepdau ehu nan Krihd, me sallahng palieir en palikapi oh paliepeng en palikapi en sahpwo, me re pahn kak peipei ie ni ahnsoun kopou.   
\s1 Melimel nan Madau  
\p
\v 13 Kisinieng tikitik ehu uhdo sang palieir, ohl ako ahpw kihkihong me re pahn kapwaiadahte ar koasoandio. Irail eri apihada peipwungo oh serek; re medemedewe me re pahn peianlahte oaroahr en Krihd ni uwen ar kak.  
\v 14 Ahpw mwurin ahnsou kis kisinieng kehlail ehu, me adaneki “Paliepeng en Palimese” ahpw ipido sang dekeo,  
\v 15 oh lelohng sohpo. Eri, pwehki at sohla kakohng kainenehiong sohpo nan kisiniengo, se ahpw mweidohng sohpo en iangala kisiniengo.  
\v 16 Se diar wasa mwele kis ni at tang palieir en kisin deke Kauda. Se ahpw doadoahk laudki at katengehdi pwohten pohn sohpo wasao pwe me apwal.  
\v 17 Irail eri pwekadahng pohn sohpo, oh salihedi teng. Irail masak re de loisang madepei pwoat me ekis dohsang oaroahr en Lipia. Eri, re ahpw lilidi oh mweidohng sohpo en peipeiseli.  
\v 18 Melimelo wie kekehlailte, oh mandahn rahno irail ahpw tapihada kesehsang kanengen sohpo,  
\v 19 oh ni kesiluhn rahn re uhd kesehsang dipwisoun sohpo.  
\v 20 Rahn tohto me se sohla kilang ketipin de usu kan, oh melimelo pil kekehlailte. Eri, se solahr koapworopworki me se pahn pitla.   
\p
\v 21 Eri, mwurin ohl ako ar sohla mwengehki ahnsou reirei, Pohl ahpw kesihnenda mwohrail oh nda, “Maing ko, ma kumwail rong iehte, oh sohte mweselsang Krihd, kitail sohte pahn lel soangen apwal oh luhs pwukat.  
\v 22 Ahpw met I peki rehmwail kumwail en koapworopwor! Pwe sohte emen kumwail pahn mehla; sohpette me pahn ohla.  
\v 23 Pwe pwohng, tohnleng en Koht me sapwellimanikin ie, oh me I kin kaudokiong, pwarodo rehi  
\v 24 oh mahsanih, ‘Pohl ke dehr masak; ke uhdahn pahn uh mwohn Sihsar. Oh Koht, sang ni sapwellime kalahngan, e ketikihong nan pehmw mouren irail koaros me iang uhk nan seiloak wet.’  
\v 25 Eri, maing ko, kumwail koapworopwor! Pwe I koapworopworki me mepwukat uhdahn pahn wiawi nin duwen me I rongehr.  
\v 26 Ahpw kitail pahn pwungidekdahng pohn oaroahr en deke ehu.”   
\p
\v 27 Ni kaeisek pahieun pwohng, melimel kehlail wet ahpw kapeikitalahng nan lepin sehd Mediderenien. Nin lukepen pwohng sehla ko ahpw mwelekihada me se kereniongehr sahpw ehu.  
\v 28 Irail eri pirehiong mehn katoutou ehu ni sahl apwoat oh kadaridi, oh re diarada me piht epwiki rieisek loalen wasao. Pil mwurin ahnsou kis re pil pwurehng wia soahngohte oh diarada me piht duweisek loalen wasao.  
\v 29 Irail masak pwe sohpo de seradahng pohn takai kan. Irail eri kadaridi peipwung pahieu sang sohpo oh kasikasik pwe wasa en rahnpeseng.  
\v 30 Sehla ko men tangasang sohpo, irail eri kadaridi pwoht pwoat nansedo oh mwomwmwomwe me re pahn pil kadaridi ekei peipwung sang mwohn sohpo.  
\v 31 Pohl ahpw ndaiong kaunen sounpeio, oh pil sounpei ko, “Ma sehla pwukat sohte pahn mihmihte pohn sohpet, kumwail sohte kak mourla.”  
\v 32 Sounpei ko eri lupukada sahl me poudaki pwohto—pwohto eri peilahsang ni sohpo.   
\p
\v 33 Ni eh kereniongehr rahnpeseng, Pohl ahpw peki rehrail irail en tungoalla: “Met kumwail awiawihkiher rahn eisek pahieu, oh nan erein rahn pwukat kumwail sohte sair kisin tungoal kis.  
\v 34 Eri, I peki kumwail en tungoale mehkot me kumwail anahne pwe kumwail en kak mour. Sohte mwahn apwoat pitenmoangamwail pahn pwupwusang.”  
\v 35 Mwurin en Pohl eh koasoia met, e ahpw ale kisin pilawa kis, kapingkihong Koht mwohrail koaros, pilitikihpeseng, oh tapihada sakan.  
\v 36 Irail eri pwatietda, oh emenemen irail pil iang tungoale mehkot.  
\v 37 Kiht koaros me riepwiki isiakan wenemen me mi pohn sohpo.  
\v 38 Eri, ni emenemen kiht eh medlahr, re kesehsang pohn sohpo edin pilawa kan pwe en kamarahda.   
\s1 Sohp Serada  
\p
\v 39 Eri, ni eh rahnpeseng, sehla ko sohte kak kasawihada mehnia sahpw mwo, re ahpw kilangada dahu pihk ehu me mi ni oaroahro. Irail eri koasoanehdi, ma e kak, re pahn pidengkilahng sohpo wasao.  
\v 40 Irail eri lupukada selin peipwung kan oh kesediong nansedo. Re ahpw lapwahda selin padil en ilihl kan. Irail ahpw apihada serek me mi mwohn sohpo, pwe kisinieng en wahlong sohpo ni oaroahr.  
\v 41 Sohpo ahpw serada pohn madepei pwoat; mwohn sohpo eri tengala, oh sohte kak mwekid, a mwurio ahpw maropkipene iloak kan.   
\p
\v 42 Eri, sounpei ko ahpw koasoanehdi me re pahn kemehla me selidi koaros, pwe re de papolong nan sahpw oh tangdoaui.  
\v 43 Ahpw kaunen sounpeio men kapitala Pohl; eri, e sohte mweidohng irail. Ahpw e padahkihong irail koaros me kak pap re en lusisang pohn sohpo, oh papolong nan sahpw;  
\v 44 oh me sehse pap re en dakehda dinapw akan de kisehn sohpo. Iei duwen me kiht koaros ahpw pitkilahng nan sahpw.   
\c 28  
\s1 Nan Malda  
\p
\v 1 Ni kiht koaros at pitlahr lel nan sahpw, se ahpw esehda me dekeo adaneki Malda.  
\v 2 Tohn deke wet me inenen kadek ong kiht. E ahpw tapihada keteu oh inenen kopou mehlel; re ahpw saunda kisiniei ehu oh kasamwo kiht koaros.  
\v 3 Pohl eri wesepene kapakap en tuwi kei; oh ni eh kihkihong tuwi ko nan kisiniei, sineik men ahpw pwedieisang nan kepentuwio pwehki karakaro, e ahpw ngalispene oh pidpene pehn Pohl.  
\v 4 Ni tohn dekeo ar kilangada sineiko eh wie mwotomwotou ni pehn Pohl, re ahpw ndapene nanpwungarail, “Ohl menet mwein sounkam aramas emen. Eri, e pitsangehr nan madau, ahpw e uhdahn pahn mehla.”  
\v 5 Pohl ahpw sipedalahng sineiko nan kisinieio sang ni peho, oh sohte mwahn mehkot ohla reh.  
\v 6 Irail ahpw awiawih ma e soh pahn mpwospeseng de pwupwudihte mehla. Ahpw mwurin arail awiawihkier ahnsou reirei oh sohte kilang mehkot kapwuriamwei me wiawihong Pohl, re ahpw wekidala arail lamalam oh nda, “Ih koht emen!”   
\p
\v 7 Mie pelien sahpw kei me sohte dohsang wasao, sapwen Puplius, kaunen dekeo. E ahpw kasamwo kiht oh apwalih kiht mwahu. Erein rahn siluh se koukousoanki reh.  
\v 8 En Puplius eh pahpao wonohnki soumwahu karakar oh mehntang. Pohl eri pedolong nan en ohlo eh pereo oh pwil peh ko powe oh kakehlahda.  
\v 9 Ni met eh wiawiher, me soumwahu koaros pohn dekeo ahpw kohdo rehn Pohl, e ahpw pil kamwahwihirailla.  
\v 10 Irail kisekisehkin kiht soahng tohto; oh ni at mwesel, re ahpw audehkihda sohpo dahme se anahne ong seiloako.   
\s1 Sang Malda ong Rom  
\p
\v 11 Eri, mwurin sounpwong siluh, se ahpw mwesel, iangada sohp pwoat sang Aleksandria, me adaneki “Koht Mpwer ko,” me mihmiher ni dekeo ni ahnsou kopou.  
\v 12 Se lel nan kahnimw Sirakus oh mihmihki wasao erein rahn siluh.  
\v 13 Se ahpw serek sang wasao oh kolahng nan kahnimw Reikium. Eri, mandahn rahno, kisinieng ahpw tapihada ipido sang palieir, oh nan erein rahn riau se ahpw lel nan kahnimw Puteoli.  
\v 14 Se ahpw tuhwong me pwoson ekei wasao me peki reht se en mihmi rehrail wihk ehu. Eri, mwurin mwo se ahpw lel Rom.  
\v 15 Me pwoson kan nan Rom rongada duwen kiht; re ahpw pwarodo lel wasahn netikihla wahntuhke en Appius oh Imwen Keiru Siluh ko pwe re en tuhwong kiht. Ni Pohl eh kilangirailda, e ahpw kapingkihong Koht oh eh koapworopwor ahpw laudla.   
\s1 Nan Rom  
\p
\v 16 Eri, ni at lelehr Rom, re ahpw mweidohng Pohl en kelekelehpw pahn epwelpen sounpei men. \fig |alt="HK-16C Pohn elen Rom" src="" size="col" ref="WIEWIA KAN 28.16" \fig*   
\p
\v 17 Eri, mwurin rahn siluh, Pohl ahpw ekerpene kaunen mehn Suhs kan ong ni mihting ehu. Oh ni arail pokonpenehr Pohl ahpw ndaiong irail, “Riei ko, I sohte mwahn wia mehkot me uhwong aramas en atail wehi de pil tiahk kan me kitail alehsangehr samatail kahlap ako; I ahpw selidi nan Serusalem oh pengpenglahng rehn mehn Rom kan.  
\v 18 Mehn Rom ahpw kapeidakih ie oh anahne en kasaledekihiehla pwehki re diarada me I sohte mwahn wiahda mehkot me pahn kahrehiong I en kamakamkihla.  
\v 19 Ahpw ni en mehn Suhs kan ar sapwungki koasoandi wet, I ahpw itoitehng I en peki kopwung sapahl rehn Sihsar, ahpw sohte mehn kadip ehu mie me I en uhkihong mehn Suhs akan. \x - \xo 28.19 \xt Wie. 25.11.\x*  
\v 20 Iei kahrepe wet me I men tuhkihong kumwail oh koasoiaiong kumwail, pwe I selikihdi selmete pwoatet pwehki ohlo me mehn Israel akan kin koapworopworki.”   
\p
\v 21 Irail eri ndaiong Pohl, “Se saikinte ale kisinlikou kis sang Sudia me koasoia duwen komwi, pil sohte riat emen me kohdo sang wasao me wahdo rongen komwi de pil mehkot me suwediong komwi.  
\v 22 Ahpw se men rong duwen omwi lamalam, pwehki se ese me wasa koaros aramas akan kin sansarsuwediong pwihn wet me komwi towedahr.”   
\p
\v 23 Irail eri kilelehiong Pohl rahn ehu, oh me tohtohie nanpwungarail me kohdo rahno wasa me Pohl koukousoan ie. Eri, sang nimenseng lel nipwong e kawekawehwehiong irail oh padapadahkihong irail duwen Wehin Koht. E song en kawekirailla ni eh kawehwehda ekei iren nan Kosonned en Moses oh nan pwuken soukohp ako.  
\v 24 Ekei irail kamehlele eh koasoi kan, a ekei sohte kamehlele.  
\v 25 Irail eri mwesel, oh sohte pwungpene nanpwungarail, mwurin Pohl eh nda, “Meid pwung me Ngehn Sarawi mahsanihong Aiseia pwe en patohwanohng samatail kahlap ako!  
\v 26 pwe e mahsanih,  
\q1 ‘Kohwei oh koasoiaiong aramas pwukat:  
\q1 Kumwail pahn rongorong ahpw sohte dehdehki;  
\q2 kumwail pahn kilikilang, ahpw sohte pahn kilang. \x - \xo 28.26 \xt Ais. 6.9-10 (LXX).\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Pwehki aramas pwukat keptakailahr;  
\q2 irail kaponelahr salengarail kan,  
\q2 oh irail perelahr masarail kan.  
\q1 Pwe ma soh, masarail kan pahn kilang,  
\q2 oh salengarail kan pahn rong;  
\q2 irail ahpw pahn wehwehki  
\q1 oh wekiong ie,  
\q2 oh I pahn kamwahwihirailla.  
\q1 Ih met mahsen en Koht.’”   
\p
\v 28 Eri, Pohl ahpw pil usehla koasoia, “Kumwail en ese me sapwellimen Koht mahsen en komour pekederlahngehr mehn liki kan. Re ahpw pahn rong.”  
\v 29 [Mwurin Pohl eh nda mepwukat, mehn Suhs akan ahpw mwesel, akahkamaipene kehlail nanpwungarail.]   
\p
\v 30 Eri, erein sounpar riau Pohl koukousoan wasa kis wasao oh pein iseise, oh e kin kasamwo koaros me kin pwarodo reh.  
\v 31 E ahpw padapadahkihong aramas akan duwen Wehin Koht; oh e kin eimah oh pil saledek ni eh kin kapahrengki duwen Kaun Sises Krais.   